NK131(do)001:1: // rgyal ba'i dbang po karma pa mi bskyod rdo rjes
NK131(do)001:2: gsang sngags rnying ma ba rnams la dri ba'i chab
NK131(do)001:3: shog gnang ba'i dris len lung dang rig pa'i 'brug
NK131(do)001:4: sgra zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK131(do)001:6: gang zhig zag med yon tan phung po srid dang
NK131(do)001:7: zhi ba'i sgro skur bral ba chos kun mnyam pa
NK131(do)001:8: chen po'i ngang / spros pa kun grol ci yang
NK131(do)001:9: mi dmigs rang babs ga nyugs ma ma skyes mi
NK131(do)001:10: gnas 'gags pa med pa'i bdag nyid can /
NK131(do)001:11: sna tshogs sgyu ma rang sar grol ba shes dang
NK131(do)001:12: shes bya gcig tu gyur pa bde chen ye shes
NK131(do)001:13: sgyu ma'i sku / rgyal ba khyab bdag 'khor lo'i
NK131(do)001:14: dbang phyug kun bzang mgon po bla ma'i tshogs la
NK131(do)001:15: rtag par dad pa'i phyag bagyi'o //
NK131(do)001:16: rang bzhin dbyings su thams cad gdod nas lhun gyis grub pa skye med ngang du ro gcig pa //
NK131(do)001:17: rang byung ye shes rtogs pa'i rgyud las rab tu grol ba mi 'gyur thig le'i ngang nyid las //
NK131(do)001:18: skye ba'i cho 'phrul sgyu ma'i rol pa mtha' yas sprul sku dpal ldan sangs rgyas pad+ma skyes //
NK131(do)001:19: 'ja' 'od sku ru mngon par byang chub rgyal ba kun dngos o rgyan bla ma de la 'dud //
NK131(do)001:20: gang gi zhing khams kha ba can du bde gshegs bstan pa spel slad du //
NK131(do)001:21: srid pa'i 'ching las nges par grol yang srid par 'jug pa 'di mdzad de //
NK131(do)001:22: mtha' yas sems can phan bde'i lam du rtag par gzhol mdzad thugs rje can //
NK131(do)001:23: spyan ras gzigs dbang srong btsan sgom po'i zhabs kyi pad mor phyag 'tshal lo //
NK131(do)001:24: rgya chen rab 'byams dkyil 'khor kun gyi gtso bo nyid de rgyal ba ma lus bskyed pa'i yab //
NK131(do)001:25: ye shes sgyu ma'i rol pa mtha' yas thabs mkhas snying rje'i cho 'phrul bkod pa rgya chen pos //
NK131(do)001:26: srid mtshor byings ba'i nyams thag 'gro la mu med dge ba'i lam mchog bzang po rtsol mdzad pa //
NK131(do)001:27: 'jam dbyangs gzhon nu mi yi tshul 'chang 'dzam gling
NK131(do)001:28: rgyal po khri srong lde'u btsan la phyag 'tshal lo
NK131(do)001:29: // bod yul mtha' 'khob mi shes mun pa'i smag rum 'dir //
NK131(do)001:30: chos kyi nyi ma rab tu gsal bas bde gshegs bstan pa snang mdzad cing //
NK131(do)001:31: phan bde'i pad tshal kun nas rab tu rgyas mdzad pa //
NK131(do)001:32: skyes mchog mtshungs med lo pan tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK131(do)001:33: rnam dag rgyal ba'i bstan pa rin po che //
NK131(do)001:34: rgya bod gnyis su bshad dang sgrub pa'i srol //
NK131(do)001:35: phan bde'i rgyun bzang da lta'i bar du yang //
NK131(do)001:36: legs par snang mod su zhig log par lta //
NK131(do)001:37: de lta'i gsang chen bla med theg pa'i mchog /
NK131(do)001:38: ye shes mngon sum ston pa'i a ti la //
NK131(do)001:39: snga phyi bdud ris rtsod pa mang byung kyang //
NK131(do)001:40: mun pa'i snang ba ji bzhin sgrib ma nus //
NK131(do)001:41: deng sang rgyal ba'i dbang po kar+m+aa pas //
NK131(do)001:42: ldems dgongs dri ba'i chab shog gnang ba la //
NK131(do)001:43: lugs ngan rmongs pa'i gnyid las bslong byed pa //
NK131(do)001:44: dris lan lung rigs 'brug sgra 'dir brjod bya //
NK131(do)001:45: spyir bstan pa rin po che 'di la theg dman nyan rang gnyis /
NK131(do)001:47: khyad par rnal 'byor gyi theg pa dang bcas pas /
NK131(do)001:48: thub pa'i gtsug lag mtha' dag bsdus par bstan la /
NK131(do)001:49: 'di dag tu ma 'dus pa'i rgyal ba'i bstan pa gzhan 'ga' yang ma mchis shing /
NK131(do)001:50: thub pa'i dbang pos skyes rabs phal cher bstan pa 'dul ba lung dang /
NK131(do)001:51: thugs bskyed tshul ston pa bskal ba bzang po dang /
NK131(do)001:52: mdzad pa bcu gnyis bye brag tu ston pa mngon
NK131(do)001:53: 'byung gi mdo la sogs pa mdo sde dang rgyud
NK131(do)001:54: sde mtha' dag las kyang thub pa'i rdzogs chen theg
NK131(do)001:55: pa'i chos 'khor bskor ces cung zad tsam yang mi
NK131(do)001:56: snang ba dang / khyad par 'phags pa'i yul na
NK131(do)001:57: rdzogs chen mi snang zhes lo chen rin bzang dang
NK131(do)001:59: rngog lo sogs phal mo che'i bstan bcos las byung
NK131(do)001:60: bas deng sang bod na gsang sngags 'gyur du grags
NK131(do)001:61: pa'i bka' ma mang po zhig dang /
NK131(do)001:62: gter gton gyis bton par grags pa'i chos lugs grangs
NK131(do)001:63: kyis mi lang ba shin tu mang ba cig 'dug
NK131(do)001:64: pas / snyigs ma rgya gar na yod pa'i gtan tshigs nges pa can smra rgyu ci yod /
NK131(do)001:66: thub pas dngos su ma gsungs pas chos ma yin pa dang /
NK131(do)001:67: rgya gar na med par 'dod pa de ltar na /
NK131(do)001:68: brtag pa gnyis pa la sogs pa dgyes pa rdo rje'i rgyud rnams kye rdo rjes gsungs te /
NK131(do)001:70: bdag gi 'khor lo khyod bshad na //
NK131(do)001:71: khyod kyi 'khor lo ji ltar legs zhes sogs rgyas par gsung shing /
NK131(do)001:72: de bzhin du bde mchog gi rgyud rnams 'khor lo sdom pas gsungs te /
NK131(do)001:74: phag mos gsol btab rdo rje can //
NK131(do)001:75: nyung ngu'i rgyud ni gsal bar mdzad //
NK131(do)001:78: ston pas sprul sku'i snang ba bsdus te /
NK131(do)001:79: dpal gsang ba 'dus pa'i dkyil 'khor sprul nas gsung ba dang /
NK131(do)001:80: lha mo bzhi'i zhus pa'i rgyud rdo rje sems dpas gsungs pa dang /
NK131(do)001:81: rnam snang sgyu 'phrul dra ba rnam snang gi gsung pa dang /
NK131(do)001:82: rtog pa bdun pa dang gsum pa 'jig byed kyi gsungs pa dang /
NK131(do)001:83: bde mchog gi rgyud 'ga' zhig dang de sogs bla
NK131(do)001:84: med kyi rgyud phal cher rang rang gi dkyil 'khor
NK131(do)001:85: gyi gtso bos gsungs shing thub pas dngos su ma
NK131(do)001:86: gsung na / de dag kyang chos ma yin dang rgya gar na med par 'gyur ram ci /
NK131(do)001:87: de dag ston pa'i dngos su ma gsungs kyang ston
NK131(do)001:88: pa dkyil 'khor gtso bo nyid du bzhengs nas gsungs
NK131(do)001:89: pa'i phyir don la mi 'gal lo snyam na /
NK131(do)001:91: ston pa nyid gdul bya dbang po rnon po don
NK131(do)001:92: gyi rjes su 'brongs pa rnams kyi phyir bcom ldan
NK131(do)001:94: gzhon nu dpa' bo stobs ldan dang /
NK131(do)001:95: ston pa bcu gnyis la sogs par bzhengs te gsungs pas na mi 'gal ba yin te /
NK131(do)001:97: thog tha med pa'i sems dpa' ni //
NK131(do)001:98: rdo rje sems dpa' dga' ba che //
NK131(do)001:99: kun tu bzang po kun bdag nyid //
NK131(do)001:100: rdo rje snyems tshul bdag po mchog /
NK131(do)001:101: bcom ldan 'das dpal mchog gi dang po'i skyes bu'o //
NK131(do)001:102: zhes gsungs pa'i tshul ltar ro //
NK131(do)001:103: de lta bas na rnying ma pa dag sprul sku'i bstan pa sde snod gsum /
NK131(do)001:104: logs sku'i bstan pa kri yog gsum /
NK131(do)001:105: chos sku'i bstan pa yo ga gsum zhes 'dod pa yin no //
NK131(do)001:106: yang sems can rnams kyi ji srid du 'jug pa'i
NK131(do)001:107: 'du shes ma zad kyi bar du 'dul byed theg
NK131(do)001:108: pa'i rnam grangs bsam gyis mi khyab pa de'i phyir
NK131(do)001:109: thub pas dngos su rdzogs chen theg pa gsungs pa
NK131(do)001:112: ji srid sems ni 'jug pa'i bar //
NK131(do)001:113: theg pa'i mtha' la thug pa med //
NK131(do)001:114: sems ni zhig par gyur pa na //
NK131(do)001:115: theg pa med cing 'gro ba'ang med //
NK131(do)001:117: mdo rje pad+ma dkar po las /
NK131(do)001:118: nga yi bstan pa'i theg pa dgu po dag /
NK131(do)001:119: sems can rnams kyi mthu dang mos par bshad //
NK131(do)001:120: 'di ltar thabs kyi mchog gi ye shes la //
NK131(do)001:121: rab tu bzung ba'i phyir na ngas bshad do //
NK131(do)001:123: mya ngan las 'das pa'i mdo las /
NK131(do)001:124: bstan bcos sam rig sngags sam gsang sngags gang ci
NK131(do)001:125: yang rung ba de dag thams cad ni rdzogs pa'i
NK131(do)001:126: sangs rgyas kyi gsungs yin par shes par gyis shig
NK131(do)001:128: bde mchog gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i rgyud las /
NK131(do)001:129: theg pa gsum dang bco brgyad de //
NK131(do)001:130: ji srid 'du shes yod kyi bar //
NK131(do)001:131: theg pa'i mtha' la thug pa med //
NK131(do)001:132: ces pa'i tshul mdo rgyud du mar gsungs shing /
NK131(do)001:133: dus kyi 'khor lo dang mtshan yang dag par brjod
NK131(do)001:134: pa la sogs pa gnyis su med pa'i rgyud sde
NK131(do)001:135: rnams ni rdzogs pa chen po dang grub mtha' khyad
NK131(do)001:137: de'i tshul rgyas par slob dpon pad+ma dang /
NK131(do)001:138: bi m+aa la gnyis kyi mtshan brjod kyi 'grel pa dang /
NK131(do)001:139: slob dpon pad+mas mdzad pa'i sbyor drug dang /
NK131(do)001:140: bdag gis byas pa'i lam rim mthar pa'i sgo gcig rnams su gsal lo //
NK131(do)001:141: lo ts+aa ba rin chen bzang pos sngags log sum
NK131(do)001:142: 'byin du gsang sngags sgra ji bzhin par spyod pa
NK131(do)001:144: rnying ma la dgag pa mdzad pa med do //
NK131(do)001:145: 'gos lo chen po lha btsas kyi 'byams yig che chung du rnying ma bkag kyang /
NK131(do)001:146: chos rnams bsgyur bar mdzad pa'i lo ts+aa ba so sos byas so zhes pa tsam las /
NK131(do)001:147: khungs thub pa'i rgyu mtshan 'god rgyu byung mi snang la /
NK131(do)001:148: rje nyid sku gzhon nu'i dus su zur la chos gsan par byon pas /
NK131(do)001:149: chos ma bslab par mnar so btang bas de'i lan
NK131(do)001:150: du mdzad pa'i lo rgyus snga rabs kyi bla ma
NK131(do)001:152: 'gos lo thams cad mkhyen pa gzhon nu dpal gyi deb sngon du yang lo rgyus de bshad do //
NK131(do)001:153: spyir na rje 'gos 'brog mi lo ts+aa ba'i gam
NK131(do)001:154: du byon dus su'ang chos 'ga' ma gnang pas thugs
NK131(do)001:155: mug ste rgya gar du gsung ba na'ang /
NK131(do)001:156: slob gnyer phul phyin cig ma byas na 'brog ldom
NK131(do)001:157: de la ngo tsha ba yod ces sogs rang gi
NK131(do)001:158: bla ma la skur ba gsung na de la yid
NK131(do)001:159: brtan du bzung bas ci zhig 'tshal /
NK131(do)001:160: rngog lo ts+aa ba legs pa'i shes rab ni rnying ma'i rgyud 'grel rnams 'chad bzhin pa ste /
NK131(do)001:161: jo bo chen po rjes kyang /
NK131(do)001:162: khyod kyi de khrom du bsgrags na gsang sgrogs su
NK131(do)001:163: 'gyur bas gsang nas bshad par rigs pa yin zhes
NK131(do)001:164: pa stsal / de'i dbon po lo ts+aa ba chen po blo ldan shes rab kyis ni /
NK131(do)001:165: bee ro tsa na nam mkha' dag dang mnyam //
NK131(do)001:166: ka cog rnam gnyis nyi zla zung gcig la //
NK131(do)001:167: rin chen bzang po tho rangs skar chen tsam //
NK131(do)001:168: kho bo de drung srin bu me khyer bzhin //
NK131(do)001:169: zhes snga 'gyur gyi lo ts+aa ba la sngags pa cher mdzad mod kyi /
NK131(do)001:170: rnying ma dgag pa med do //
NK131(do)001:171: rnying ma rgya gar du ji ltar yod pa yang /
NK131(do)001:172: slob dpon brgya byin sdong pos sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor gyi 'grel pa rgyud don rnam bshad las /
NK131(do)001:173: gsang sngags kyi rgyud mtha' dag sdu na /
NK131(do)001:175: mtshon byed yi ge'i rgyud do //
NK131(do)001:176: mtshon byed yi ge'i rgyud la /
NK131(do)001:181: de la bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga /
NK131(do)001:182: rdzogs pa a nu yo ga /
NK131(do)001:183: rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga gsum mo //
NK131(do)001:184: bskyed rdzogs rnam pa gsum du phye ste /
NK131(do)001:185: dang po rgyud kyi rnam grangs bco brgyad du gsungs pa las /
NK131(do)001:187: tan+t+ra chen po sde bco brgyad kyi thog ma gsum ni /
NK131(do)001:190: sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor rnams la thugs gsung sku'i rgyud zer /
NK131(do)001:191: mnyam sbyor gyi he ru ka'i dkyil 'khor yang dag yin la /
NK131(do)001:192: de dag gi bshad srol kyang da lta'i bar du ma nub cing /
NK131(do)001:193: pan chen thams cad mkhyen pa bu ston gyi rgyud sde spyi'i rnam bzhag tu /
NK131(do)001:194: rdo rje bzhad pa'i skor gyi le'u zhes tshan pa gcig tu mdzad pa'i /
NK131(do)001:195: rdo rje bzhad pa'i gsang ba 'dus pa'i 'grel par /
NK131(do)001:196: gsang ba snying po'i rgyud kyi lung mang du drangs /
NK131(do)001:197: 'dus pa phyi ma'i 'grel pa slob dpon bi shwa mi tras mdzad pa dang /
NK131(do)001:198: slob dpon brgya byin sdong pos mnyam sbyor gyi 'grel par yang gsang snying gi lung mang du drangs /
NK131(do)001:199: 'grel pa 'di rnams pan chen thams cad mkhyen pa
NK131(do)001:200: bu ston gyi bstan 'gyur dkar chag tu yang tshad
NK131(do)001:201: mar mdzad / jo bo rjes lam sgron gyi rang 'grel du /
NK131(do)001:202: gal te bya ba'i rgyud la sogs pa'i gsang sngags
NK131(do)001:203: kyi theg pa la spyod par 'dod pa yin na
NK131(do)001:204: slob dpon gyi dbang bskur ba bya ba bum pa'i
NK131(do)001:205: dbang thob par ma byas par smon pa dang 'jug
NK131(do)001:206: pa'i sems bskyed pa tsam la ltos par mi bya
NK131(do)001:207: ste / gsang sngags rang nyid len par 'byung ba'i phyir ro //
NK131(do)001:209: slob dpon mnyes par ma byas shing //
NK131(do)001:210: dbang rnams thob par ma byas na //
NK131(do)001:211: nyan pa la sogs brtson pa yang //
NK131(do)001:215: dbang bskur rjes gnang med par yang //
NK131(do)001:216: gsang sngags rang nyid len par byed //
NK131(do)001:218: zhes lung 'dren mdzad pa'i tshig 'di gnyis gsung ba snying po'i rgyud tshig yin no //
NK131(do)001:219: thar pa lo ts+aa bas gsang snying rgyud phyi ma la 'gyur mdzad /
NK131(do)001:220: bsam yas su gsang ba snying po'i rgya dpe kha
NK131(do)001:221: che pan chen gyi phyag tu byung ba rta ston
NK131(do)001:223: de nas sha gad lo ts+aa ba la byung ba bcom ldan ral gris blang ste 'gyur bcos mdzad /
NK131(do)001:224: gsang snying sgrub pa rgyan gyi me tog ces pa'i bstan bcos mdzad /
NK131(do)001:225: de dus sha gad lo ts+aa bas bcom ldan ral gri la bskur ba'i yi ge ni /
NK131(do)001:226: bsil ldan 'di na sde snod 'dzin rnams kyis //
NK131(do)001:227: nang na rgyu skar rgyal po gang ba ltar //
NK131(do)001:228: kun nas kun tu rab tu mdzes gyur pa //
NK131(do)001:229: mkhas chen bcom ldan ral gri rgyal gyur cig /
NK131(do)001:231: gsang ba snying po'i rgya dpe bris la bskur gsung ba /
NK131(do)001:232: dpe de ta la'i lo ma la yi ge wartu shin tu legs par bris pa /
NK131(do)001:233: snga dus su byon pas yi ge la la subs /
NK131(do)001:234: le'u dgu pa nas ta la'i byang bu gcig kyang chad /
NK131(do)001:235: mjug kyang ma rdzogs pa cig gda'/
NK131(do)001:236: 'on kyang le'u nyer gnyis pa rdzogs nas ma 'gyur ba'i le'u gnyis rdzogs su nye ba cig gda'/
NK131(do)001:237: des kyang ji tsam rdzogs ma 'tshal /
NK131(do)001:238: gnyis po 'di la 'bru thu ga bgyis na cung zad go'am snyam ste ma bgyis /
NK131(do)001:239: 'ga' zhig la cung zad bgyis pa 'di dag la'ang
NK131(do)001:240: nor ba mchis pas de rnams legs par 'chos pa
NK131(do)001:241: dang / 'di gnyis legs par bsgyur bar yang zhu /
NK131(do)001:242: gzhan mtshams sbyor ma byas pa dang /
NK131(do)001:243: tshigs bcad la shad ma bris pa rnams rgya dpe
NK131(do)001:244: la ji ltar 'dug pa bzhin bris pa lags so
NK131(do)001:246: rgyud kun snying po dpal ldan 'dus pa dang //
NK131(do)001:247: dbyer med rgyud chen 'di lta bu dang gzhan //
NK131(do)001:248: zab mo'i rgyud dang theg chen chos rnams dang //
NK131(do)001:249: mjal nas tshul bzhin sgrub pa byed par shog /
NK131(do)001:252: gnas gtsang steng gi 'og min nyams dga' bar //
NK131(do)001:253: kun bzang rdo rje sems dpas gsungs pa'i bka' //
NK131(do)001:254: rgyud rgyal gsang snying rgya dpe ma rnyed pas //
NK131(do)001:255: bod kyi byas zhes gangs ri'i khrod 'dir grags //
NK131(do)001:256: bcom ldan ral gris rgya dpe legs btsal nas //
NK131(do)001:257: gzhung 'di 'dzin pa'i sngags 'chang rnams la bstan //
NK131(do)001:258: pan chen bi shwa mi tra la sogs pa'i //
NK131(do)001:259: gzhung gi sgrub byed gsang snying sgrub par ltos //
NK131(do)001:260: rgya bod gnyis su mkhas par legs sbyangs pas //
NK131(do)001:261: dpe 'di ma rnyed yid bzhin rin chen 'dra //
NK131(do)001:262: sangs rgyas gsang ba bi shwa mi tra yi //
NK131(do)001:263: gsang snying rgyud dang mthun pa'i 'grel ba mdzad //
NK131(do)001:264: 'di gnyis spangs nas rang gar 'chad pa rnams //
NK131(do)001:265: shes rab 'chal ba'i rang bzhin bslus pa yin //
NK131(do)001:266: rma rin 'phyang drug dpyad gzhung ma mthong bas //
NK131(do)001:267: 'phyong drug gzhung mtshams shes pa med ces grags //
NK131(do)001:268: 'phyong drug shes par 'dod pa'i sngags 'chang rnams //
NK131(do)001:269: gzur gnas blo yi kho bo'i drung du byon //
NK131(do)001:270: zhes gsungs shing dar bar mdzad /
NK131(do)001:271: jo bo chen po rjes bsam yas su rgya dpe rnams gzigs pas /
NK131(do)001:272: jo bos sngar gzigs ma myong ba rgya dpe mang po 'dug pas /
NK131(do)001:273: gsang sngags 'di la mis shes pa med pa'i /
NK131(do)001:274: mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyis kyang nam mkhar gzhal yas
NK131(do)001:275: khang dpag tu med pa'i sgo phye nas rgyud sde
NK131(do)001:276: mang po bstan pa la'ang 'di rnams mi gda'/
NK131(do)001:277: theg pa chen po gsang sngags 'di la mtha' mngon
NK131(do)001:278: rgyu rang yod yod mi 'dra gsungs nas thugs rgyal
NK131(do)001:279: chag / bod kyi rgyal po la rjes su yi rangs pa mdzad nas /
NK131(do)001:280: bod kyi bstan pa dar dus de 'dra rgya gar du yang ma byung ngam gsungs shing /
NK131(do)001:281: rgya gar du me'i dgra lan gsum byung bas tshigs pa 'dra /
NK131(do)001:282: rgya gar na med pa'i dpe mang po 'di na snang gsungs nas btsal /
NK131(do)001:283: zhal bshus nas rgya gar la bskur bya ba dang /
NK131(do)001:284: slob dpon pad+mas nam mkha' la byon nas lha dang klu dang /
NK131(do)001:285: dpal sh+r+ai len+t+ra nas rgyud sde thams cad bsam yas
NK131(do)001:286: su spyan drangs pas rgya gar bas bod mang ba
NK131(do)001:287: yin gsung ba rnams jo bo'i rnam thar chen mor
NK131(do)001:288: snang ngo // de lta bu'i rgyud rnams ji ltar dar ba yang /
NK131(do)001:289: mdo sde gdams ngag 'bogs pa'i rgyal po las /
NK131(do)001:290: rgyu la mos pa rgyu'i chos kyi //
NK131(do)001:291: 'khor lo rab tu bskor byas nas //
NK131(do)001:292: rdo rje theg pa nye lam zhig /
NK131(do)001:295: rnying ma'i mdo dgongs pa lung ston las /
NK131(do)001:296: 'dzam gling shar lho'i phyogs mtshams su //
NK131(do)001:297: mi las skal ldan grags pa che //
NK131(do)001:298: rgyal po dza zhes bya ba la //
NK131(do)001:299: lag na rdo rjes ston par 'gyur //
NK131(do)001:302: dpal sdom pa'i rgyud phyi ma las /
NK131(do)001:303: nga ni 'di nas mi snang nas //
NK131(do)001:304: lo ni nyi shu rtsa brgyad na //
NK131(do)001:305: bstan pa'i snying po dam pa zhig /
NK131(do)001:306: lha gnas gsum du grags pa ste //
NK131(do)001:307: 'dzam gling shar lho'i phyogs mtshams na //
NK131(do)001:308: dpal zhes bya ba'i ri bo la //
NK131(do)001:309: thugs rje mthun pa'i byin rlabs kyi //
NK131(do)001:310: rgyal po rgyal po tsa yin na dza'i bshad pa mi rung ngo snyam na /
NK131(do)001:311: tsa dang dza gnyis sgra'i byings gcig ste dza di ral pa'i don la /
NK131(do)001:313: tsa t+au na ral pa la'i zhes so //
NK131(do)001:315: lag na rdo rjes snang bar byed //
NK131(do)001:316: mi las skal ldan dam pa rnams //
NK131(do)001:317: byang chub mchog tu grub 'gyur ba //
NK131(do)001:318: de la rtag tu gus par byos //
NK131(do)001:319: zhes mthun par gsung pa ltar /
NK131(do)001:320: rgyal po dza la babs nas rim par dar ba yin te /
NK131(do)001:321: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa tshul brgya lnga bcu pa'i 'grel pa las /
NK131(do)001:322: gsung rab 'di'i lo rgyus bshad na /
NK131(do)001:323: sngon sangs rgyas mi yul na lo brgyad cu bzhugs pa'i tshe /
NK131(do)001:324: sarba bud+d+ha sa ma yo ga dang /
NK131(do)001:325: gu h+ya sa ma dza la sogs pas 'dul zhing
NK131(do)001:326: theg pa de dag gi snod du gyur pa 'dzam
NK131(do)001:327: bu'i gling gi mi yul na med pas /
NK131(do)001:328: rgyal chen rigs bzhi dang sum cu rtsa gsum dang /
NK131(do)001:329: dga' ldan la sogs pa'i gnas rnams na lha rnams
NK131(do)001:330: dang bskal pa bzang po'i byang chub sems dpal la
NK131(do)001:331: sogs pa snod du gyur nas de'i tshe mdo sde
NK131(do)001:333: slad kyi sangs rgyas mya ngan las 'das pa'i 'og
NK131(do)001:334: tu za hor gyi rgyal po 'khor dang bcas pa
NK131(do)001:335: ngo mtshar du chos la dad pa dag cig 'dug
NK131(do)001:336: pa theg pa de'i 'dul skal du gyur cing snod
NK131(do)001:337: du gyur nas sarba bud+d+ha sa ma yo ga la
NK131(do)001:338: sogs pa mdo sde chen po bco brgyad phyag na
NK131(do)001:339: rdo rje'i byin gyis brlabs kyi za hor gyi yul
NK131(do)001:341: za hor gyi rgyal po in+d+ra b+h+au tis mdo sde dag bltas pa na brda' ma 'phrod nas /
NK131(do)001:342: sngon gyi las kyi dbang gi mngon par shes pa thob pas bltas pa na /
NK131(do)001:343: yul gyi dbus yul ma la ba na +aa tsar+ya
NK131(do)001:344: ku ku r+aa dza nyin bzhin khyi stong la chos
NK131(do)001:345: 'chad / mtshan bzhin khyi de dag la dam tshig gi longs spyod mdzad pa /
NK131(do)001:346: khyi'i slob dpon mdzad pa cig bzhugs pa de theg pa'i snod du gyur la /
NK131(do)001:347: bdag gi 'dul skal du gyur pa yang 'dra nas /
NK131(do)001:348: rgyal pos pho nya btang nas slob dpon gshegs su gsol ba dang /
NK131(do)001:349: slob dpon de yang sngon gyi las kyi dbang gi mngon par shes pa lnga dang ldan nas /
NK131(do)001:350: rgyal po de bdag gi 'dul du 'bab bam mi 'bab /
NK131(do)001:351: mdo sde de dag gi snod du gyur ram ma gyur brtags pa na /
NK131(do)001:353: bdag kyang mdo sde'i snod du yang gyur /
NK131(do)001:354: rgyal po'i the tshom yang sel bar 'gyur mod kyi /
NK131(do)001:355: 'on kyang mdo sde de dag sngar ma ltas na /
NK131(do)001:356: rgya la rgyal po'i the tshom dag ma sol bar
NK131(do)001:357: gyur na shin tu ma legs pas pho nyal slar
NK131(do)001:358: springs pa / mdo sde de dag kho bos sngar
NK131(do)001:359: bltar 'tshal gyi tshur skur cig ces springs pa dang
NK131(do)001:360: springs pa / / mdo sde de dag tshur gshegs te ltas pa na /
NK131(do)001:361: mgo mjug gar lta'i cha ma mchis te /
NK131(do)001:362: de nyid du lus brdabs te mgon med do //
NK131(do)001:363: skyabs med do zhes bos pa dang /
NK131(do)001:364: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' mngon par gshegs te khyod ci 'dod ces dris pa dang /
NK131(do)001:365: bdag mdo sde zab mo 'di bltas pa tsam gyi shes par 'dod ces gsol ba dang /
NK131(do)001:366: de bzhin gnang ngo gsung nas /
NK131(do)001:367: de nas sarba bud+d+ha sa ma yo ga la sogs
NK131(do)001:368: pa'i glegs bam rnams ma phye bar de dag gi
NK131(do)001:369: don mngon sum du yid la gsal bar gyur to
NK131(do)001:370: // de nas slob dpon de za hor gyi yul
NK131(do)001:371: du gshegs te rgyal po 'khor dang bcas pa la
NK131(do)001:373: dpal rdo rje sems dpas lung bstan te rgyal po
NK131(do)001:374: 'khor dang bcas pa rnams rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil
NK131(do)001:377: btsun mo dam pa bzhi yum gyi sar bkod /
NK131(do)001:378: blon po bzhi rigs bzhi'i sar bkod /
NK131(do)001:379: sras mo rnams nang gi lha mo'i sar bkod /
NK131(do)001:380: btsun mo phal pa rnams phyi'i lha mo'i sar bkod /
NK131(do)001:381: blon po phal pa rnams sgo srung bzhi dang bskal
NK131(do)001:382: pa bzang po'i byang chub sems dpa' ltar bkod pa
NK131(do)001:384: bdag cag 'khor dang bcas pa rig 'dzin gyi gnas su grub pa'i phyir na /
NK131(do)001:385: dam pa'i chos 'di mi nub par bya ba'i phyir
NK131(do)001:386: sras sha kra pu ti rgyal tshab tu dbang bskur
NK131(do)001:387: nas / +aa tsar+ya ku ku ras lung dang man
NK131(do)001:388: ngag bstan pa rgyal ba de la bstan nas bzhag
NK131(do)001:390: rgyal po 'khor dang bcas pa stong sa la gnas
NK131(do)001:391: pa'i byang chub sems dpa'i rig 'dzin du grub bo
NK131(do)001:392: // de'i sras sha kra pu tis de bzhin du
NK131(do)001:393: bsgom pa dang 'khor bdun brgya dang bcas pa yang
NK131(do)001:394: rig 'dzin gyi gnas su grub bo //
NK131(do)001:395: yang rgyal po sha kra pu tis /
NK131(do)001:397: sras mo go ma de b+ai la dpal dam pa'i
NK131(do)001:398: nang nas tshul brgya lnga bcu pa bkod de bshams
NK131(do)001:399: nas in+d+ra b+h+au ti'i lugs de sras mo yul dang
NK131(do)001:400: sa 'dzin du stsal ba de la bstan pas sras
NK131(do)001:401: mo de 'khor dang bcas pa brgya dang yang rig
NK131(do)001:403: de nas sras mo des rgyal bu la lung dang
NK131(do)001:404: man ngag bzhag pa las 'phel ba ni deng sang
NK131(do)001:406: zhes pa ltar rim gyis dar ba yin la /
NK131(do)001:407: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang bas lam rnam par bkod par yang /
NK131(do)001:408: de nas rdo rje gdan stengs kyi //
NK131(do)001:409: 'dzam gling shar lho'i phyogs mtshams su //
NK131(do)001:410: pho brang dam pa rin chen nang //
NK131(do)001:411: bkra shis dam pa'i khang pa ru //
NK131(do)001:412: ku ku r+aa dza in+d+ra b+h+au ti dang //
NK131(do)001:413: sing ha u pa ra dza dang //
NK131(do)001:414: sras mo go ma pa la sogs //
NK131(do)001:415: sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i dbang thob nas //
NK131(do)001:416: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor mngon sgrubs te //
NK131(do)001:417: rdo rje 'chang sar mngon du gshegs //
NK131(do)001:419: sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor gyi 'grel pa las kyang /
NK131(do)001:420: rgyal ba'i dgongs don yun ring gnas pa'i thabs //
NK131(do)001:421: sprul sku'i nyi mas 'dzam gling gsal mdzad nas //
NK131(do)001:422: sde snod gsum gyi 'jig rten 'dul ba'i dus //
NK131(do)001:423: blo dman 'phags pa'i lam la bkod byas kyang //
NK131(do)001:424: rang gi de nyid nges don gnas ma mthong //
NK131(do)001:425: ma 'ongs blo mchog grol bar bya ba'i phyir //
NK131(do)001:426: sprul pa'i byang chub sems dpa' blo gros mchog /
NK131(do)001:427: dgongs pa'i dbang gis rmongs pa 'dul ba'i tshul //
NK131(do)001:428: dkyil 'khor sprul pa'i 'khor lo rab snang mdzad //
NK131(do)001:429: mgon po rnams kyi rjes su bslabs byas te //
NK131(do)001:430: dpal ldan sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam sbyor gzhung //
NK131(do)001:431: gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor rim gyis sgrubs don gsal //
NK131(do)001:432: gdul bya dag pa'i tshogs rnams grol bar mdzad //
NK131(do)001:433: yun ring gsang ba'i theg pa gnas bya'i phyir //
NK131(do)001:434: sprul pa'i byang sems sme khrod rgyal po la //
NK131(do)001:435: gsang ba dam pa'i gdams ngag rab dkrol zhing //
NK131(do)001:436: rnal 'byor don phyir rab tu gdams par mdzad //
NK131(do)001:437: sprul pa'i sku 'das phyi ma'i dus shig tshe //
NK131(do)001:438: rgyal ba'i bka' gsang 'dzam gling gnas su shar //
NK131(do)001:439: rgyal po'i khab tu spyan drangs mchod byas shing //
NK131(do)001:440: dga' zhing gus bstod legs bltas brda ma mjal //
NK131(do)001:441: thugs rje'i 'brel shugs gsang sngags 'dzin par grags //
NK131(do)001:442: dam par bzung ste glegs bam 'dzin par zhus //
NK131(do)001:443: sgyu 'phrul thig le stong pa'i dkyil 'khor gzhung //
NK131(do)001:444: grub thob lhag pa'i lha yis lung bstan mdzad //
NK131(do)001:445: zhes 'byung zhing rgyas par mdzad pa yin la /
NK131(do)001:446: sprul pa'i sku dga' rab rdo rjes /
NK131(do)001:447: rdo rje sems dpa' la dngos su gsan nas /
NK131(do)001:451: pan+di ta dz+ny+aa na s+au tra /
NK131(do)001:452: pan chen bi m+aa la mi tra rnams kyi sems
NK131(do)001:453: klong man ngag gi sde gsum rgyas par mdzad cing
NK131(do)001:454: / sgyu 'phrul gsang ba snying po'i skor rnams ni slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang bas dar bar mdzad /
NK131(do)001:455: gsang ba snying po'i 'grel pa dang /
NK131(do)001:456: sgyu 'phrul lam rim la sogs pa'i bstan bcos kyang mang du brtsams so //
NK131(do)001:457: yang dze ta ri'i slob ma /
NK131(do)001:458: 'jam pa'i dbyangs kyi rjes su bzung ba'i slob dpon
NK131(do)001:459: sgeg pa'i rdo rjes gsang ba snying po la tik+ka
NK131(do)001:460: mdzad cing dar bar mdzad do //
NK131(do)001:461: yang kar+m+aa pa rang nyid kyi lugs la yang rdzogs chen rgya gar du yod pa 'grub ste /
NK131(do)001:463: rdo rje sems dpa'i sprul pa dga' rab rdo rje
NK131(do)001:464: la rdzogs pa chen po klong chen rab 'byams sogs
NK131(do)001:465: nyan pa'i tshe rang byung rdo rje bdag kyang tog
NK131(do)001:466: tse rnal 'byor dbang phyug bya bar gyur nas rdzogs
NK131(do)001:467: pa chen po'i sgra don thams cad rtogs pa gcig
NK131(do)001:470: rgyal po dza'i rjes slob dpon pad+ma bod du ma byon pa'i snga rol tsam na /
NK131(do)001:471: rgya gar du bdag kyang gsang sngags rnying ma thams
NK131(do)001:472: cad ston shes pa'i sngags kyi rnal 'byor pa zhig
NK131(do)001:473: tu gyur nas mtshan yang ye shes rdo rje 'bar
NK131(do)001:475: de dag gis ni sngags kyi rgyud rnams sprul pa'i
NK131(do)001:476: skus dngos su gsung dgos pa'i nges pa med pa'i
NK131(do)001:477: tshul dang / thub pas rdzogs pa chen po la
NK131(do)001:478: sogs pa theg pa rim pa dgu yang gsungs pa'i
NK131(do)001:479: tshul dang / tshul dang / rnying ma rgya gar
NK131(do)001:480: du ji ltar byung zhing dar ba'i tshul bstan pa
NK131(do)001:481: tshul dang / tshul dang / yin no // yang /
NK131(do)001:482: rnying ma'i rgyud kyi skabs na /
NK131(do)001:483: spyir gsar ma'i rgyud mtha' dag ni rgyud kyi dngos
NK131(do)001:484: po bcu tshang ba 'phags yul kun tu cher grags
NK131(do)001:485: shing deng sang gi bar du gnas pa /
NK131(do)001:486: bod yul 'dir sngar yang 'gyur zhing phyis kyang 'gyur ba /
NK131(do)001:487: skad gsar bcad dang brda rnying gi khyad tsam ma
NK131(do)001:488: gtogs 'gyur zur phran tshegs gcig mi gcig las phal
NK131(do)001:489: cher gcig thog gcig 'bab pa 'ba' zhig 'gyur 'dug
NK131(do)001:490: pa la / rnying ma'i rgyud 'di dag gleng gzhi
NK131(do)001:491: gleng blang nas rgyud rdzogs par bstan pa'i bar gyi
NK131(do)001:492: dngos po bcu tshang bar bstan pa nyung bar 'dug
NK131(do)001:493: pa la / pas / rgyud mtshan nyid pa yin
NK131(do)001:494: na rgyud kyi dngos po bcu tshang dgos pa la
NK131(do)001:495: pa la / pas / / 'di dag ma tshang
NK131(do)001:496: na thang rgyud du 'gro ba'i shes byed rnam dag
NK131(do)001:499: spyir gsang sngags kyi rgyud sde sems can rnams kyi
NK131(do)001:500: blo'i rim pa dang chos kyi dbyings kyi rjes su
NK131(do)001:501: byed pas mtha' dang grangs dang tshad bzung bar dka'
NK131(do)001:502: mod kyi / mdo tsam smos na /
NK131(do)001:504: rgyud ni rgyun chags zhes bya ste //
NK131(do)001:505: khor ba rgyud du 'dod pa yin //
NK131(do)001:506: rgyu rgyud 'jag ma'i srin bu nas sangs rgyas kyi bar du rgyun chags su gnas pa yin la /
NK131(do)001:507: gsang ba 'dus pa phyi ma las /
NK131(do)001:508: rang bzhin rnam dag rgyu yin te //
NK131(do)001:509: gzhi ni thabs zhes bya ba yin //
NK131(do)001:511: gsum gyi rgyud don bsdus pa'o //
NK131(do)001:513: rgyu'i rgyud sems can thams cad kyi rgyud la dkar po'i sa bon dang ldan pa dang /
NK131(do)001:514: thabs kyi rgyud nyams su len pa'i lam dang /
NK131(do)001:515: 'bras bu'i rgyud sku gsum ye shes lnga dang ldan
NK131(do)001:516: pa'i bdag nyid mngon du gyur pa ste gsum dang
NK131(do)001:517: / mngon brjod bla ma'i 'grel pa las /
NK131(do)001:518: rgyud ni gnyis te rtsa ba dang yan lag gi'o //
NK131(do)001:521: brjod bya don gyi rgyud kyi ngo bo ni gang
NK131(do)001:522: la gnyis med kyi ye shes snang bar nus pa
NK131(do)001:523: yin la / rjod byed tshig gi rgyud kyi ngo
NK131(do)001:524: bo ni gang la gnyis med kyi ye shes snang
NK131(do)001:525: bar nus pa'i man ngag yin no //
NK131(do)001:526: zhes pa ltar na yang gnyis dang /
NK131(do)001:527: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang bas kyang gnyis su phye la /
NK131(do)001:528: mdor na rgyu'i rgyud la yul yul can dang rgyu 'bras gnyis yod pas /
NK131(do)001:529: de'i dri ma sbyong byed du bskyed rdzogs gnyis ston
NK131(do)001:530: pa'i thabs la rjod byed tshig gi rgyud du btags
NK131(do)001:531: pa yin mod / zhi rgyas la sogs pa'i las
NK131(do)001:532: rab 'byams sgrub pa gtso bor bton pa'i rgyud rnams
NK131(do)001:533: la ni dngos po bcu tshang dgos pa yang ma
NK131(do)001:534: pa yin mod / yin zhing / bskyed rdzogs kyi
NK131(do)001:535: lam phyin ci ma log par ston pa'i rgyud rnams
NK131(do)001:536: la dngos po bcu dang ldan dgos te /
NK131(do)001:537: lta ba dang dkyil 'khor dang dbang dang dam tshig
NK131(do)001:538: dang sgrub pa dang phrin las dang sngags dang phyag
NK131(do)001:539: rgya dang ting nge 'dzin dang mchod pa ste bcu'am
NK131(do)001:540: / gzhan nas bshad pa yang rung ste 'di'i rgyud rnams la yod cing /
NK131(do)001:541: 'ga' zhig la med kyang skyon med pa yin te /
NK131(do)001:546: sngags btu'i rgyud la sogs pa bya spyod phal cher la ma tshang /
NK131(do)001:547: chos spyod mngon par rtogs pa'i rgyud dang /
NK131(do)001:548: 'jig rten gsum rgyal gyi rtog pa la sogs pa yo ga 'ga' zhig la ma tshang la /
NK131(do)001:549: bla med kyi dum bu phal che ba la med do //
NK131(do)001:550: de lta bas na gsar ma ba'i rgyud rnams la
NK131(do)001:551: yang dngos po bcu tshang ba dang ma tshang ba
NK131(do)001:553: rgyud gcig la dngos po bcu ka tshang dgos pa'i nges pa med do //
NK131(do)001:555: gsar ma'i rgyud rnams ni rgya gar shar nub u
NK131(do)001:556: rgyan la sogs 'phags yul kun na deng sang gi
NK131(do)001:557: bar du dar rgud med par gnas la /
NK131(do)001:558: bod kyi lo ts+aa ba snga phyi mang du byon pa dag gi 'gyur bcos byas shing /
NK131(do)001:559: dper na kye rdor gcig pu la yang 'gyur byed snga phyi bdun tsam byung 'dug pa la /
NK131(do)001:560: rnying ma'i rgyud 'di la khri srong lde btsan gyi gong du yang ma 'gyur /
NK131(do)001:561: de dus las kyang 'gyur ba'i lo rgyus gtan tshig khungs thub mi snang bas /
NK131(do)001:562: tshul 'di la khungs thub mi snang bas /
NK131(do)001:563: tshul 'di la dpag na rnying ma rgya gar na med pa yang 'thad pa 'dra zhing /
NK131(do)001:564: rigs pa des na de dus bod ni bon gyi
NK131(do)001:565: dbang byas pas bon gyi bstan pa shin tu dar
NK131(do)001:566: la / 'gro ba mtha' dag kyang bon la ngo mtshar du 'dzin pa gzigs /
NK131(do)001:567: lo ts+aa ba rnams kyi gsang sngags bon gyi lugs su bshad de /
NK131(do)001:570: sbyor sgrol gyi lag len mdzad pa la ming rdzogs
NK131(do)001:571: chen dang rnying mar grags pa tsam las rgya gar
NK131(do)001:573: mkhas pa dag gi gsung las kyang 'thad la 'di la ci smra /
NK131(do)001:575: gsar ma'i rgyud rnams 'phags yul kun na deng sang
NK131(do)001:576: gi bar du dar rgud med par gnas shes gsung
NK131(do)001:577: pa yang ha cang thal ba yin te /
NK131(do)001:578: dus 'khor rtsa rgyud 'grel pa stong phrag drug cu
NK131(do)001:579: pa dang bcas pa slob dpon tsi lu pa'i slob
NK131(do)001:580: mas ka ta ka'i rgyal po'i yul du dmag byung
NK131(do)001:581: ba dang dong du sbas pa /
NK131(do)001:582: phyis bton pas ma tshang ba dang /
NK131(do)001:583: tsi lu ba la 'bri bar zhus pas /
NK131(do)001:584: mkha' 'gro mas sbas pa yin pas mi rung gsung nas ma gnang /
NK131(do)001:586: rtsa rgyud kyi dum bu thar los bsgyur ba dang /
NK131(do)001:587: 'grel chen stong phrag drug cu rtsa bzhi pa'i dum
NK131(do)001:588: bu pan chen b+h+au mi sh+r+ais bsnams pa pan chen
NK131(do)001:589: thams cad mkhyen pa bu'i 'gyur las mi snang bas
NK131(do)001:590: / dus 'khor rtsa rgyud 'grel pa dang bcas pa
NK131(do)001:591: yang nub nas da lta dum bu las med cing
NK131(do)001:592: / / de bzhin du rgyud sde rin po che
NK131(do)001:593: rnams la dar rgud 'phel 'grib byung tshul chos 'byung
NK131(do)001:594: rnams las bshad pas smos ma dgos /
NK131(do)001:595: chos rgyal khri srong lde'u btsan gyi dus su lo
NK131(do)001:596: ts+aa ba rnams kyi gsang sngags bon gyi lugs su
NK131(do)001:598: nyid rang gi 'dir gsungs mod gzhan du lo rgyus khungs ma gang na yang ma bshad /
NK131(do)001:599: bon gyi lo rgyus rnams su yang /
NK131(do)001:600: de dus bon snub nas chos dar bar byas so zhes pa kho na 'byung /
NK131(do)001:601: de'i gong du lha'i tho tho ri'i ring la chos kyi da bu brnyes zer kyang /
NK131(do)001:602: nam mkha' nas spangs bskongs phyag rgya ba sogs babs
NK131(do)001:603: pa la chos dang bon gang yin ngo ma shes
NK131(do)001:604: par mtshan gnyan po gsang bar btags nas mchod pa
NK131(do)001:606: de nas gdung rabs lnga nas chos rgyal srong btsan sgam po byon /
NK131(do)001:607: 'di spyan ras gzigs dngos yin pas /
NK131(do)001:608: snying rje pad+ma dkar po dang /
NK131(do)001:609: za ma tog bkod pa la sogs pa thugs rje chen po'i mdo'i skor dang /
NK131(do)001:611: zhal gdams kyi skor la sogs pa mang du gsungs /
NK131(do)001:614: chos skyong lha mgon gyi sgrub skor sogs gsang sngags
NK131(do)001:615: mang du gsungs pas yer ba'i brag gcig pu la
NK131(do)001:616: 'od lus grub pa'i grub thob brgyad cu byung /
NK131(do)001:617: mtha' 'dul yang 'dul la sogs pa'i gtsug lag khang du bzhengs /
NK131(do)001:618: thon mis yi ge blang nas mdo sde dkon mchog sprin bsgyur /
NK131(do)001:619: glang khams pa go chas yum rgyas pa bsgyur /
NK131(do)001:620: de nas mes ag tshom gyi bar du gsang sngags
NK131(do)001:621: kyi sgrub pa gsang ste spyod pa mang po byung
NK131(do)001:622: / byis pa yan chad kyi yi ge drug pa
NK131(do)001:623: 'don cing thugs rje chen po la yi dam du
NK131(do)001:624: / byed / zhi khro'i sgrub thabs dang /
NK131(do)001:625: gshin rje gshed kyi sgrub thabs chos rgyal gyi mdzad
NK131(do)001:626: pa deng sang yang snang bas gsang sngags rnying ma
NK131(do)001:627: ni chos rgyal khri srong lde'u btsan gyi gong du
NK131(do)001:629: phyis su yang ma 'gyur ba ma yin te /
NK131(do)001:630: 'brog mi lo ts+aa bas dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyi zor mdos bsgyur /
NK131(do)001:631: 'gos lo ts+aa ba khug pa lha btsas kyi rgyal
NK131(do)001:632: po sprin gyi shugs can la gsan te gshin rje
NK131(do)001:633: gshed 'joms byed dang 'char ka'i skor la /
NK131(do)001:635: de dag gi 'grel pa sgrub thabs /
NK131(do)001:637: pan+di ta ga ya d+ha ri'i zhal khrigs sogs tshang bar bsgyur /
NK131(do)001:638: gzhan yang gshin rje kha thun rgyud sgrub skor las
NK131(do)001:639: tshogs dang bcas pa 'gos kyi bsgyur nas rang gi
NK131(do)001:640: slob ma rdog lba ba can la sogs pa nas
NK131(do)001:641: brgyud pa deng sang du yod cing /
NK131(do)001:642: slob dpon pad+ma nas brgyud pa'i phyag na rdo rje
NK131(do)001:643: gos sngon can gyi rgyud sgrub thabs rgya gar phyag
NK131(do)001:645: yang dag me gcig thod gcig gi skor pan chen sh+aakya sh+ri dang khro bu lo ts+aa bas bsgyur /
NK131(do)001:646: thar pa lo ts+aa ba nyi ma rgyal mtshan gyi
NK131(do)001:647: phur pa'i sgrub skor dang man ngag kha yar bsgyur
NK131(do)001:648: / glo bo lo ts+aa ba shes rab rin chen
NK131(do)001:649: gyi rdo rje phur pa'i drag po sgrol dbang yongs
NK131(do)001:651: sa skya pan+di tas phur pa tsa dum gyi rgyud la bsgyur bcos mdzad /
NK131(do)001:652: bcom ldan ral gris gsang snying la 'gyur bcos dang sngar ma 'gyur pa'i le'u gnyis bsgyur /
NK131(do)001:653: gsang snying rgyud phyi ma thar pa lo ts+aa bas bsgyur /
NK131(do)001:654: slob dpon pad+mas pan chen nags rin la gnang ba'i
NK131(do)001:655: tshe sgrub pan chen de nyid dang chos 'khor lo
NK131(do)001:656: ts+aa bas bsgyur / lha mo spu gri'i rgyud dang
NK131(do)001:657: rag sha'i rgyud dzo gi kan tsi n+aa tha'i dpe
NK131(do)001:658: las mkhyen rtse lo ts+aa bas bsgyur ba sogs mang
NK131(do)001:659: ts+aa bas bsgyur / zhing / grub chen u rgyan pa'i gsung las kyang /
NK131(do)001:660: bal po na rnying ma'i rgya dpe mang du 'dug pa la /
NK131(do)001:661: ngas bod kyi sngags pa rnams la khyed rang tsho mang yul du 'deng /
NK131(do)001:662: ngas rnying ma'i pan+di ta dang rgya dpe tshur dkug /
NK131(do)001:663: lo ts+aa ba ngas byas te bsgyur byas pa la /
NK131(do)001:664: bod kyi sngags pa rnams bu smad gso bas g.yengs te ma 'grub /
NK131(do)001:665: da dung 'gyur mang du bya rgyu 'dug pa la /
NK131(do)001:667: rnying ma bdag gis gsar ma'i skyes bu dam pa
NK131(do)001:668: rnams kyi phyag srol ltar rgya ba la du bgrod
NK131(do)001:669: nas thos bsam gyi rgyud sbyangs te rgyud rnams gsar
NK131(do)001:671: 'gyur bcos sogs byas na byed rgyu med pa ma yin mod kyang /
NK131(do)001:672: sngags 'chang gong ma rnams rang rang gi pha chos
NK131(do)001:673: gtso bor bton nas bshad pa dang sgrub pa kho
NK131(do)001:674: na la nan tan mdzad pas lo ts+aa bar grags
NK131(do)001:675: pa cher ma byung ba yin gyi rgya gar nas
NK131(do)001:676: chos kyi dpe cha snyed pa ma yin no //
NK131(do)001:677: mdos gtor la sogs pa 'di dag bon dang 'dres snyam par yang mi bsam ste /
NK131(do)001:678: slob dpon d+hi ri warmasa mdzad pa'i gtsug tor gdugs dkar gyi mdos dang /
NK131(do)001:679: bram ze mchog sred kyi mdzad pa'i lha mo dang mgon po'i mdos dang /
NK131(do)001:680: 'gro bzang snying po dang spyod mdzad chos kyi rdo
NK131(do)001:681: rjes mdzad pa'i rnam thos sras kyi mdo la sogs
NK131(do)001:682: pa sngags gsar ma la yang mang du yod pas
NK131(do)001:685: rgya gar na yod na khri srong lde'u btsan gyi gong du yang 'gyur dgos la /
NK131(do)001:687: de dus na yang rgyud re re la lo pan
NK131(do)001:688: re le'u btsan gyi gong du yang 'gyur dgos la
NK131(do)001:690: de dus na yang rgyud re re la lo pan re res 'gyur byed byas la /
NK131(do)001:691: rgyud gcig la 'gyur byed kyi lo pan nang mthun
NK131(do)001:692: par byung ba bshad pa mi 'dug pas 'di dag
NK131(do)001:693: lo pan tha dad kyi brtsams rgyud yin nges su
NK131(do)001:694: snang na brtsoms rgyud ma yin pa'i lung rig gi
NK131(do)001:695: sgrub byed smra rgyu ci yod /
NK131(do)001:697: de ni ha shang sun phyung ba'i rjes su rgyal po'i bkas bcad de /
NK131(do)001:698: lta ba klu sgrub kyi lugs /
NK131(do)001:700: rgyud sde 'og ma gsum la bsten par gnang /
NK131(do)001:701: bla med kyi rgyud sde rnams re zhig 'gog pa'i
NK131(do)001:702: zol gyi gsang nas bsgyur zhing spyod pa yin te
NK131(do)001:703: / de'i rgyu mtshan gyi 'phang thang ma dang ldan dkar ma la sogs pa'i dkar chag tu /
NK131(do)001:706: dges rdor la sogs pa'i rgyud rnams kyang ma thebs pa yin la /
NK131(do)001:707: rgyud gcig la lo pan nang mthun ma byung ba brtsoms rgyud yin pa'i gtam tshig tu 'jog na /
NK131(do)001:708: kha che zla mgon gyi dri med 'od kyi ye shes le'u /
NK131(do)001:711: jo bo chen po'i rang 'gyur 'ga' zhig /
NK131(do)001:714: bi b+h+au ti tsan+d+ra la sogs pa'i rang 'gyur mang po dang /
NK131(do)001:716: dbang mdor bstan gyi dka' 'grel sum brgya drug cu pa /
NK131(do)001:717: de'i dka' 'grel yid bzang rtse bas bsgyur ba /
NK131(do)001:718: spang los bshad sbyar mi g.yo snang ba /
NK131(do)001:719: rdo rje snying po rgyun gyi rgyud /
NK131(do)001:721: gsang ba rgyan gyi rgyud gsum su ga ta sh+r+ai dang /
NK131(do)001:723: kun mkhyen bus gshed dmar gyi rgyud gsum la sogs pa mang po dang /
NK131(do)001:724: kri ya sa muts+tsha pan+di ta many+dzu sh+r+ai dang /
NK131(do)001:725: sa bzang lo ts+aa ba ma ti sa bsgyur ba sogs /
NK131(do)001:726: de dus las sngar yang ma 'gyur /
NK131(do)001:728: lo pan nang mthun par ma byung ba mang na /
NK131(do)001:729: de dag kyang brtsams rgyud du 'dod dam ci /
NK131(do)001:730: chos nyid kyi bden pa gzigs pa'i lo ts+aa ba
NK131(do)001:731: chen po de dag gi chos log dang rgyud brtsams
NK131(do)001:732: so zhes sgrog pa yang 'phags pa la bskur ba
NK131(do)001:735: dus phyis rma rin chen mchog gi gsang ba snying po brtsams so zhes pa dang /
NK131(do)001:737: rma ban rin chen mchog ces pas //
NK131(do)001:738: gsang ba snying po'i rgyud brtsams pas //
NK131(do)001:739: rgyal pos gsan nas btsal ba'i tshe //
NK131(do)001:740: lo grangs bcu gnyis gab ces grags //
NK131(do)001:743: tan+t+ra chen po sde bco brgyad du grags pa 'di rnams chos log dri ma can yin no //
NK131(do)001:744: zhes sogs kyi tshig la bstan pa tsam yin gyi
NK131(do)001:745: khungs thub pa'i rgyu mtshan gzhan ci yang med de
NK131(do)001:746: / rma rin chen mchog gi bod du gsang ba snying po'i rgyud brtsams pa yin na /
NK131(do)001:747: de'i sngon du rgya gar du slob dpon sna tshogs
NK131(do)001:748: bshes gnyen gyi mdzad pa'i gsang 'dus kyi 'grel par
NK131(do)001:749: gsang ba snying po'i rgyud kyi lung 'dren 'ong don
NK131(do)001:751: tan+d+ra chen po sde bco brgyad po bod du brtsams pa'i chos log dri ma can yin na /
NK131(do)001:752: sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor gyi rgya 'grel du de la
NK131(do)001:753: skyed rdzogs rnam pa gsum du phye ste dang po
NK131(do)001:754: rgyud kyi rnam grangs bco brgyad du gsungs pa las
NK131(do)001:755: / zhes pa rnying ma la grags pa dang khyad par med pa dang /
NK131(do)001:756: gzhan thams cad kyang 'di dang 'dra na ci'i phyir
NK131(do)001:757: khyed rnams la brtsoms rgyud yin pa'i gtan tshigs yod
NK131(do)001:758: na gsal bar bstan dgos so zhes gsol ba lags
NK131(do)001:759: / yang rgyud de dag brtsams rgyud ma yin pa'i sgrub byed smra na yang /
NK131(do)001:760: rgyud rang gi ngo bos kyang rgyud kyi mtshan nyid mi ldan te /
NK131(do)001:761: rgyud yin na thams cad mkhyen pa sangs rgyas kyi gsung yin pas /
NK131(do)001:765: ma 'brel ba'i skyon sogs 'byung mi srid la /
NK131(do)001:766: khyod kyi rgyud kyi don de nyid kyi gzhung don
NK131(do)001:767: legs par brtags na skyon de dag ldan pa kho
NK131(do)001:768: na 'dug kyang yi ge mang por 'gro phyir re
NK131(do)001:770: brda' tsam mtshon na klad don mtshan gyi skabs na yang /
NK131(do)001:771: kun 'dus rig pa'i mdo zhes bya ba'i rgyud /
NK131(do)001:773: dur khrod khu byug rol pa'i mdo zhes bya ba'i rgyud /
NK131(do)001:774: ces sogs 'gal dang ma 'brel ba'i skyon can gyi ming chags pa dang /
NK131(do)001:775: gter mar grags pa'i rgyud 'ga' zhig na /
NK131(do)001:776: man ngag snying gi dgongs pa rgyal ba'i bka' zhes bya ba'i rgyud /
NK131(do)001:777: ces rgyal ba'i bka' min zhes gleng dogs kyi mtha' 'gegs pa'i tshig ming la bkod pa dang /
NK131(do)001:778: der ma zad rgyud rnams mtha' drug tshul bzhis rgyas btab pa'i don /
NK131(do)001:779: rgya bod mkhas pa'i 'grel de dag gi rnam par dbye ba byas pa na /
NK131(do)001:780: smin par byed pa dbang nas grol bar byed pa
NK131(do)001:781: dbang don nyams su blang ba'i gdams pa'i bar lam
NK131(do)001:782: cha lag dang bcas pa rdzogs par ston pa zhig
NK131(do)001:783: rgyud rnam dag gi mtshan nyid yin pa la /
NK131(do)001:784: rnying ma'i rgyud der dkyil chog gyer chog sogs kyang
NK131(do)001:785: rgyud nyid kyi ston pa'i gsal gsal mor byed pa
NK131(do)001:786: zhig las rgyud rnam dag gi rnam pa 'dra ba
NK131(do)001:787: yang lta smos kyang ci dgos te /
NK131(do)001:788: gang zag mkhas pas brtsoms pa'i tshig sbyor tsam yang mi snang ba'i phyir dang /
NK131(do)001:789: rgyud gzhan rnams kyi gzhung gi rdzogs tshig tu zhes
NK131(do)001:790: bya ba'i rgyud rdzogs so zhes bshad 'ong ba la
NK131(do)001:791: / rnying ma la lar zhes bya ba 'khor ba ma stong gi bar du ma rdzogs so //
NK131(do)001:792: zhes rnal 'byor pa lta ba la rgyab g.yar te
NK131(do)001:793: rtsing chos su smra ba khyad chos su 'ong re
NK131(do)001:794: bkod pa log skyon can gyi tshig sbyor 'di dag
NK131(do)001:795: lung rig gi lam du gzhal ba na rgyud kyi
NK131(do)001:796: mtshan nyid gtan nas med pas brtsams rgyud du rig
NK131(do)001:797: par bya'o // 'di dag byung ba'i dus kyang 'ga'
NK131(do)001:798: zhig ni gong du bstan pa ltar khri srong gi
NK131(do)001:800: phal cher ni dar mas bstan pa snubs rjes mi drug la sogs pa mthar 'khyar ba na /
NK131(do)001:801: dbus gtsang 'dir rab tu byung ba ni med /
NK131(do)001:802: khyim pa'i cha byad kyi sngags pa rnams bde bar
NK131(do)001:803: rgyu ste de dag gi nyin re bzhin kha zer
NK131(do)001:804: ba na yang / de ring nyi ma ring bar snang /
NK131(do)001:805: jo mo chang zhig gnang dang /
NK131(do)001:806: pha jos rgyud zhig rtsoms pa lags zer bar grags pas dus der brtsoms pa yin no //
NK131(do)001:808: 'di'i rgyud rnams phur pa la sogs pa phyogs ma h+aa yo gar gtogs pa rnams dang /
NK131(do)001:811: gsang ba man ngag gi sde gsum ste bzhir snang ba las /
NK131(do)001:814: klong sder gtogs pa rnams ni tshig zab la 'brel
NK131(do)001:815: chags pa sdeb sbyor legs par gsungs pas na don
NK131(do)001:816: bzang po tshig 'bru bzang bo sha stag yod pas
NK131(do)001:817: mi legs pa'i skyon gang yang med /
NK131(do)001:818: man ngag gi sde rnams ni ston pas go bde
NK131(do)001:819: ba man ngag gi tshul du bshad pas rgyud nyid
NK131(do)001:820: thos pa'am bltas pa kho nas don bde blag tu
NK131(do)001:822: de dag gi dgongs 'grel mkhan po u rgyan chen po dang /
NK131(do)001:824: bee ro tsa na la sogs pa mkhas pa 'gran
NK131(do)001:825: zla ma mchis pa rnams kyi kyang sdeb sbyor spangs
NK131(do)001:826: te lhug pa go bde ba nyid du bkral ba
NK131(do)001:828: pan chen bi m+aa la'i mtshan mtshan brjod kyi 'grel pa las /
NK131(do)001:829: chos skad dbyings la ma bsten bod kyi mis //
NK131(do)001:830: go ba bde phyir so so'i skad kyi bkrol //
NK131(do)001:831: de phyir mkhas pas tshig skyon gdags mi rigs //
NK131(do)001:832: 'on kyang rgyal ba'i lung la skur 'debs na //
NK131(do)001:833: bdag 'dra'i gzhung la ci phyir smad mi rigs //
NK131(do)001:835: gzhan yang tshig sdeb sbyor legs mi legs dang sgra bzang ngan la brton par ma gzungs te /
NK131(do)001:836: bde mchog stod 'grel don la brton par bya yi
NK131(do)001:837: tshig la brton par bya ba ma yin pa dang
NK131(do)001:838: / nges don la brton par bya yi drang don la brton par bya ba ma yin pa dang /
NK131(do)001:839: ye shes la brton par bya yi rnam shes la brton par bya ba ma yin pa dang /
NK131(do)001:840: chos la brton par bya yi gang zag la brton par bya ba ma yin pa'o //
NK131(do)001:842: tshig 'bru la rab tu brton pa ni theg pa
NK131(do)001:843: gang du yang bcom ldan 'das kyi ma gsungs so
NK131(do)001:846: kun mkhyen lam don gnyer ba rnams la sgra dang sgra min rnam dpyod chen po med /
NK131(do)001:847: sna tshogs yul skad ngan pa yis kyang chen po rnams kyi lam la rtag tu 'jug /
NK131(do)001:848: sems can rnams kyi mos pa'i sems kyi dbang gi thams cad mkhyen pa'i gsung mchog la /
NK131(do)001:849: brda' sprod pa la lha klus bkod pa'i sgra sogs rtsod pa don gnyer rnams kyi de las gzhan /
NK131(do)001:850: sgra nyams pa dang yul gyi skad las kyang /
NK131(do)001:851: rnal 'byor ldan pas don ni 'dzin byed de //
NK131(do)001:852: chu la 'o ma nges par zhugs pa de //
NK131(do)001:853: ngang pas rab tu phyung nas 'thung bar byed //
NK131(do)001:854: don dam de nyid yul la rtag tu ni //
NK131(do)001:855: chen po rnam dag tshig la brton pa min //
NK131(do)001:856: yul gyi ming rnams kyi ni don shes na //
NK131(do)001:857: bstan bcos sgra dag gis ni ci zhig bya //
NK131(do)001:858: gang zhig zur chag sgra dang sgrar gyur pa //
NK131(do)001:859: brjod pa de nyid ye shes ma yin zhing //
NK131(do)001:860: gang zhig 'gro ba dag la nyi tshe ba //
NK131(do)001:861: de ni thams cad mkhyen pa'i gsung ma yin //
NK131(do)001:864: 'gal ba dang ma 'brel ba dang bzlos pa dang
NK131(do)001:865: ma tshang ba sogs med pas sangs rgyas kyi bka'
NK131(do)001:867: de lta na snyan ngag dang sdeb sbyor la sogs pa'i bstan bcos dang /
NK131(do)001:868: tshangs pa dang khyab 'jug dang dbang phyug la sogs
NK131(do)001:869: pas byas pa'i mu stegs byed kyi gzhung rnams dang
NK131(do)001:870: / sgra tshad la mkhas pa'i mu stegs rnams kyi
NK131(do)001:871: byas pa'i bstan bcos rnams tshig bzang zhing 'gal ba
NK131(do)001:872: dang ma 'brel ba la sogs pa'i skyon gang yang
NK131(do)001:873: / med pas / de dag thams cad mkhyen pa sangs rgyas kyi gsung du 'dod pa lags sam /
NK131(do)001:875: sgra bzang po smra ba rnams kyi sgra bzang po
NK131(do)001:876: la zhen pa spangs pa'i slad du don la brton
NK131(do)001:877: pa nyid la brten pa nas tshigs su bcad pa
NK131(do)001:878: kha cig sgra nyams pa dang /
NK131(do)001:879: kha cig gcod mtshams nyams pa dang /
NK131(do)001:880: kha cig tu rnam dbye med pa'i tshig dang /
NK131(do)001:881: kha cig dbyangs dang gsal byed phyis pa dang /
NK131(do)001:882: kha cig tu ring po la thung ngu dang /
NK131(do)001:883: thung ngu la ring po dang /
NK131(do)001:884: kha cig tu lnga pa'i don la bdun pa dang /
NK131(do)001:885: bzhi pa'i don la drug pa dang /
NK131(do)001:886: gzhan gyi tshig la bdag nyid kyi tshig dang /
NK131(do)001:887: bdag nyid kyi tshig la gzhan gyi tshig dang /
NK131(do)001:888: kha cig tu gcig gi tshig la mang po'i tshig dang /
NK131(do)001:889: mang po la gcig gi tshig dang /
NK131(do)001:890: kha cig tu pho'i rtags can la ma ning gi rtags dang /
NK131(do)001:891: ma ning la mo'i rtags dang /
NK131(do)001:892: kha cig tu rkan las byung ba la so dang spyi bo las byung ba dang /
NK131(do)001:893: kha cig tu spyi bo las byung ba la so dang rkan las byung ba ste /
NK131(do)001:894: gzhan yang rjes su rtogs par bya'o //
NK131(do)001:896: sgra bzang po'i mngon pa'i nga rgyal nyams par bya
NK131(do)001:897: ba'i slad du bdag gi don la brton pa nyid
NK131(do)001:898: la brten te bri bar bya'o //
NK131(do)001:899: zhes gsungs pas sgra skyon dang 'gal skyon dang ma
NK131(do)001:900: 'grel ba sogs byung yang don la skyon dang ldan
NK131(do)001:902: mdo zhes bya ba'i rgyud ces pa /
NK131(do)001:903: gsang sngags ni mdo sde'i snod du bshad pa yin te /
NK131(do)001:905: gsang sngags mdo sde'i tshul du bshad kyi nyon //
NK131(do)001:908: mdo sde 'di ni legs par bshad //
NK131(do)001:911: rgyud do cog gi rtsa ba ste /
NK131(do)001:913: mdo sde 'di yi gzi brjid kyi //
NK131(do)001:914: zhes pa la sogs pa mang du gsung zhing /
NK131(do)001:915: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang bas kyang //
NK131(do)001:916: rgyud chen de'i don rnams kun //
NK131(do)001:917: mdor bsdus zab mor ston pas na //
NK131(do)001:918: mdo sder bde bar gshegs pas gsungs //
NK131(do)001:919: zhes rgyud sde rnams shin tu rgyas pa'i sder bshad cing mdo sde'i snod du 'dus par bzhed cing /
NK131(do)001:921: de la gsang sngags ni gsung rabs yan lag bcu
NK131(do)001:922: gnyis las gang zhe na zab mo'i don bsdus te
NK131(do)001:925: gang ltar yang gsang sngags rnams mdo'i sder bshad do //
NK131(do)001:926: man ngag snying gi dgongs pa rgyal ba'i bka' zhes bya ba'i rgyud kyi mtshan ni /
NK131(do)001:927: mtha' 'geg pa'i tshig ma yin te /
NK131(do)001:928: chos thams cad don la mtshan du gsol ba'i phyir yin no //
NK131(do)001:929: de yang sngon jo bo chen po rjes byang chub
NK131(do)001:930: lam sgron mdzad pa'i tshe khyed bod la mtshan gyi
NK131(do)001:931: 'dogs lugs ji lta bu yod gsung /
NK131(do)001:933: don la mtshan du gsol ba dang /
NK131(do)001:934: dpe la mtshan du gsol ba dang /
NK131(do)001:935: yul dang zhu ba po la mtshan du gsol ba la sogs pa du ma bdog zhus pas /
NK131(do)001:937: bod na rgya gar na med pa'i gtam mang po 'dug gsung ste /
NK131(do)001:938: rol snyed ma phrogs pa dang /
NK131(do)001:939: gnod sbyin mkhar ba bsad pa'i gtam brgyud gsungs nas /
NK131(do)001:940: chos thams cad don la mtshan du gsol ba yin zhes gsungs pa nyid kyi shes so //
NK131(do)001:941: smin grol gyi lam cha lag dang bcas pa ni
NK131(do)001:942: 'di pa'i rgyud dang gdams pa rnams na zab la
NK131(do)001:943: rgya che zhing myur ba las kyang ches myur ba
NK131(do)001:944: lo dang zla ba'i cha shas kyi sangs rgyas kyi
NK131(do)001:945: sa la sbyor nus pa yod do //
NK131(do)001:946: zhes bya ba'i rgyud ma rdzogs so zhes zhi khro dgongs pa rang grol du 'byung ba yang /
NK131(do)001:947: 'di nyid chos kyi sku dang longs spyod rdzogs pa'i
NK131(do)001:948: sku'i bstan pa yin pas ston pa mya ngan las
NK131(do)001:950: de'i bstan pa yang 'og min la sogs pa rnams
NK131(do)001:951: su rtag pa rgyun gyi khor mor gnas pas chos
NK131(do)001:952: kyi rdzogs mtha' mi mngon pa la dgongs pa yin
NK131(do)001:953: no // lugs 'di ni gsar ma'i shing rta chen po rnams la yang grags te /
NK131(do)001:954: slob dpon rgyal ba bzang pos mdzad pa'i bde mchog gi 'grel pa las /
NK131(do)001:955: 'dir ni bcom ldan 'das mi gnas pa'i mya ngan
NK131(do)001:956: las 'das pa brnyes pas rtag par bzhugs nas chos
NK131(do)001:957: ston pas de'i phyir chos kyi rdzogs pa'i mtha' nam
NK131(do)001:958: yang mngon pa ma yin no //
NK131(do)001:960: 'o na khyed rang chos sku'i bstan par 'dod pa'i
NK131(do)001:961: rgyud bcu bdun la sogs pa rnams su zhes bya
NK131(do)001:962: ba'i rgyud rdzogs so zhes 'byung ba ci snyam na
NK131(do)001:963: / de ni sdud pa po dang /
NK131(do)001:964: lo pan rnams kyi spyi dang mthun par bshad pa yin gyi /
NK131(do)001:965: don la zab mo'i chos la rdzogs mtha' mngon par 'dod pa ma yin no //
NK131(do)001:966: khyim pa'i cha byad kyi sngags pa rnams nyi ma
NK131(do)001:967: ring ba nas chang re 'thungs nas rgyud brtsoms zhes
NK131(do)001:969: de'i dus su rgyal po dar mas bstan pa snubs
NK131(do)001:970: nas 'chad rtsod brtsom pa la sogs pa'i ming tsam
NK131(do)001:972: de bas na pan chen yid bzang rtse pas /
NK131(do)001:973: spyir na dar mas bstan pa bsnubs nas lo bdun
NK131(do)001:974: cu lhag cig gi bar na dbus gtsang du rab
NK131(do)001:976: rnying ma ba'i sngags 'chang mang du yod pa rnams
NK131(do)001:977: kyi yul so sor sgrub pa khyad par can gyi
NK131(do)001:979: khyim pa rnams kyang de dag la dad cing bum
NK131(do)001:980: dbang tsam re blang nas zas gos la sogs pas
NK131(do)001:981: mnyes par byas / klu mes la sogs pa'i dbus
NK131(do)001:982: gtsang gi mi drug gam brgyad du grags pa rnams
NK131(do)001:983: byon pa'i tshe yul dang yul ljongs rnams su dge
NK131(do)001:985: sngon bsgyur ba'i bka' dang bstan bcos la ma nyams par longs spyod du chog pa byung /
NK131(do)001:986: zhes gsungs pa ltar don la gnas pa yin la /
NK131(do)001:987: grub chen u rgyan pas chag lo ts+aa ba nga rang gi dbang zhus pa'i bla ma yin kyang /
NK131(do)001:988: rnying ma'i mdo dgongs pa 'dus pa bod kyi sngags rgan rnams kyi brtsams zhes gsungs ba mi 'thad /
NK131(do)001:989: de yin na nged rang rnams kyis kyang brtsams dang
NK131(do)001:990: sangs rgyas kyi gsung la yang de bas lhag pa
NK131(do)001:992: 'dir grub mtha' dang lta dgongs mthos pa la thugs su mi shong ba mi 'tshal te /
NK131(do)001:993: theg pa rnams kyi mtho dman lha dgongs kyi phye ba yin pas na slob dpon zhi ba'i lhas /
NK131(do)001:994: rnal 'byor pa yang blo khyad kyi //
NK131(do)001:995: gong ma gong ma rnams kyi gnod //
NK131(do)001:997: gzhan yang 'phags pa shes rab khri pa las /
NK131(do)001:998: chos 'di ni theg pa la gsar du zhugs pa dang /
NK131(do)001:999: nyan thos dang rang sangs rgyas kyi rigs can rnams kyi mdun du brjod par mi bya'o //
NK131(do)001:1001: skrag cing sngangs la spu zing byed pas shes rab
NK131(do)001:1002: kyi pha rol du phyin pa 'di nyid spong bar
NK131(do)001:1005: dbu ma rin chen phreng ba las /
NK131(do)001:1006: nges par legs pa'i chos rnams kyang //
NK131(do)001:1007: phra zhing zab par snang bas na //
NK131(do)001:1008: byis pa thos pa mi ldan la //
NK131(do)001:1009: skrag par byed par rgyal bas gsungs //
NK131(do)001:1011: gzhan yang dge slong khrims nyams pa las dregs par skyes pa pe har dang /
NK131(do)001:1012: ban d+he dkon gnyer las mtha' log pa las dregs par skyes pa rdor legs dang /
NK131(do)001:1013: gang zag sa thob pa las mtha' log pa khyab
NK131(do)001:1014: 'jug sogs yul gru tha dad kyi lha 'dre dregs
NK131(do)001:1015: pa can rnams la yang rgyud re 'ong bar snang
NK131(do)001:1016: ba 'di / spyir na rgyud kyi skad don tan+t+ra ste /
NK131(do)001:1019: ma tshang ba med pa sogs la 'jug na /
NK131(do)001:1020: dregs pa can 'di dag las mtha' ma log pa'i
NK131(do)001:1021: gong du ni de dag gi rgyud 'ong don med
NK131(do)001:1022: la / des na rgyud chags kyi don ma tshang /
NK131(do)001:1023: dbang dang lha sgrub rgyun chags su ston pa mi 'dug pas 'brel ba'i don ma tshang /
NK131(do)001:1024: rgyud de dag nas gang zag gcig 'tshang rgya pa'i
NK131(do)001:1025: lam cha lag rdzogs par mi ston pas ma tshang
NK131(do)001:1026: ba med pa'i don ma tshang /
NK131(do)001:1027: des na gtan tshig gsum gyi rgyud min par rig par bya ste /
NK131(do)001:1028: rdzas sngags la rten pa'i lha 'dre'i sgrub thabs yin par rig par bya'o //
NK131(do)001:1033: khams pa phra mo sogs kyi phan bya gnod bya'i rgyud mang po dang /
NK131(do)001:1034: rtsis dang sman gyi rgyud 'dug pa dag mtshungs te /
NK131(do)001:1035: don la rgyud ma yin te bstan bcos yin no //
NK131(do)001:1036: yang rgyud mtshan nyid pa yin na de dag gi sgrub byed gsal bar smra bar byos shig /
NK131(do)001:1038: dregs pa can 'di dag la rgyud 'ong ba'i rgyu
NK131(do)001:1039: mtshan ni slob dpon sangs rgyas gnyis pa pad+ma 'byung
NK131(do)001:1040: gnas kyis / dregs pa can 'di dag sangs rgyas
NK131(do)001:1041: kyis kyang brid cing dam la btags pa las sgrol
NK131(do)001:1043: pho rgyud mo rgyud 'jig rten gyi mthu chen 'di
NK131(do)001:1044: rnams 'dul ba'i don du dpal chen po khros nas
NK131(do)001:1045: sku gtum pa'i cha byad du bstan te /
NK131(do)001:1046: pho tshogs 'dul ba'i don du gshin rje gshed por bstan /
NK131(do)001:1047: mo tshogs 'dul ba'i don du che mchog tu bstan /
NK131(do)001:1048: klu 'dul ba la dpal rta mgrin du bstan /
NK131(do)001:1049: de las kyang stobs can gsum du bstan /
NK131(do)001:1050: pho tshogs 'dul ba'i don du 'jig pa'i stobs can du bstan /
NK131(do)001:1051: mo tshogs 'dul ba'i don du brjid pa'i stobs can du bstan /
NK131(do)001:1052: klu 'dul ba'i phyir du gyad kyi stobs can du bstan /
NK131(do)001:1053: mthun pa'i rdzas kyi brid nas dam la btags /
NK131(do)001:1054: sha khrag srog dbugs la dbang byed par bskos nas
NK131(do)001:1055: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa bsrung ba'i rnal 'byor pa
NK131(do)001:1056: rnams kyi srung mar bzhag go //
NK131(do)001:1059: thabs mkhas pas brid cing dbang du bsdus pa tsam las thabs gzhan gyi ma thul ba yin pas /
NK131(do)001:1060: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i lha rnams kyi rgyud ltar
NK131(do)001:1061: dbang bzhi dang sbyang gzhi sbyong byed la sogs pa
NK131(do)001:1062: smin grol gyi lam ston pa'i rgyud med kyang 'di
NK131(do)001:1063: dag tu zhi rgyas dbang drag las sogs pa phrin
NK131(do)001:1064: las sna tshogs sgrub pa'i thabs las rgyal mchog gi
NK131(do)001:1065: rim pa du ma gsungs pas na rgyud kyi bye
NK131(do)001:1066: brag yin no // de la 'dir rgyun chags dang /
NK131(do)001:1068: ma tshang ba med pa'i don gsum ka tshang ste /
NK131(do)001:1069: lo chen rin chen bzang po'i rgyud sde spyi rnam las /
NK131(do)001:1070: ci'i phyir 'di la rgyud ces bya zhe na /
NK131(do)001:1071: rgyud la legs sbyar gyi sgra las /
NK131(do)001:1074: ni ran tan+t+ra zhes 'brel zhing breng chags pas na rgyud de /
NK131(do)001:1075: de yang gzhi sems can gyi dus /
NK131(do)001:1077: 'bras bu sangs rgyas kyi dus gsum gyi sems rgyud 'brel bas na rgyud do //
NK131(do)001:1078: de la sgyu 'phrul dra ba las /
NK131(do)001:1079: rgyud ces bya ba 'brel ba'i don //
NK131(do)001:1080: don ni rnam pa gsum yin te //
NK131(do)001:1084: yang na sems rgyud gsum 'brel shing breng chags pa
NK131(do)001:1085: de yang ma tshang ba med par phun sum tshogs
NK131(do)001:1086: pa'i tshul gyi bde blag tu sgrub par nus pa'i
NK131(do)001:1087: brjod bya dang brjod byed du 'brel ba la bya
NK131(do)001:1088: ste / dpal dam tshig gsum bkod pa'i rgyud las /
NK131(do)001:1089: 'brel dang ma tshang med pa dang //
NK131(do)001:1090: phun sum tshogs pas rgyud ces bya //
NK131(do)001:1094: sa la k+sha tan+t+ra zhes rang gi mtshan nyid 'dzin pas na rgyud de /
NK131(do)001:1095: zhes gsungs pa rnams tshang ba'i phyir dang /
NK131(do)001:1097: rgyud ni rgyun chags zhes bya ste //
NK131(do)001:1099: zhes pas rgyun chags kyi don ni gzhi sems can gyi dus yin pas tshang /
NK131(do)001:1100: sems des 'khor 'das thams cad la khyab pas 'brel pa'i don tshang /
NK131(do)001:1101: sems de la chos thams cad rdzogs pas ma tshang ba med pa'i don tshang ba yin te /
NK131(do)001:1103: rin chen sems las phyir gyur pa //
NK131(do)001:1104: sangs rgyas med cing sems can med //
NK131(do)001:1106: de bas na 'di dag gi rgyud la mtshan nyid mi ldan pa med pa yin la /
NK131(do)001:1107: sngags gsar ma la yang 'di dag dang mtshungs pa'i 'jig rten pa dag gi rgyud yod de /
NK131(do)001:1108: 'jig rten gsum las rnam par rgyal ba'i rtog par /
NK131(do)001:1109: kyo ba tang gi sgrub pa dang /
NK131(do)001:1118: ci bgyi ma la sogs pa 'jig rten pa'i lha mang po'i sgrub thabs gsungs shing /
NK131(do)001:1119: bde mchog rdo rje mkha' 'gro'i rgyud kyi le'u bcu dgu par /
NK131(do)001:1122: 'byung po thams cad kyi sgrub thabs rnams yod pas khyad par med pa yin no //
NK131(do)001:1123: dregs pa so so'i rgyud dang man ngag las dregs
NK131(do)001:1124: pa'i srog dbang zhes bka' gtad rjes gnang la dbang
NK131(do)001:1125: du btags pa rnying ma ba dag mdzad pa dang
NK131(do)001:1126: mthun par / gsar ma la yang yod pa yin te /
NK131(do)001:1128: phyag na rdo rje gzi byin gyi //
NK131(do)001:1129: dkyil 'khor du ni dbang bskur ba //
NK131(do)001:1130: de ni rdo rje'i rigs gcig gi //
NK131(do)001:1132: ma mo gnod sbyin drag pa yi //
NK131(do)001:1133: dkyil 'khor gang dag ci bshad pa //
NK131(do)001:1134: thams cad de dag kun kyang ni //
NK131(do)001:1135: dogs pa med par bri bar bya //
NK131(do)001:1137: yang rdor legs la sogs pa 'di dag lha 'dre rang rgyud par bzung bar yang mi rigs te /
NK131(do)001:1138: 'byung po 'ga' zhig rang rang gi gzugs kyi 'dul ba'i slad du /
NK131(do)001:1139: sangs rgyas thabs mkhas pas de dag gi tshul bzung ba yod de /
NK131(do)001:1140: rdor legs rta mgrin yin par thams cad mkhyen pa rang byung rdo rjes /
NK131(do)001:1141: dam can skyes bu chen po ging gi bdag /
NK131(do)001:1142: dpal ldan dregs pa rta mgrin thugs las sprul //
NK131(do)001:1144: pe har gur gyi mgon po dang thugs rgyud gcig ste /
NK131(do)001:1145: sde brgyad spyi 'dul phyir rgyal po'i tshul bstan /
NK131(do)001:1146: de'i 'khor rnams kyang pu tra ming sring ru 'dren sde bzhi sogs kyang khyad par med /
NK131(do)001:1147: mgon po legs ldan nag po sa thob pa'i byang
NK131(do)001:1148: chub sems dpa' yang dkar po nag po'i tshul gyi
NK131(do)001:1150: khyab 'jug ni bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad dang rdo rje 'chang gi sprul par bshad /
NK131(do)001:1151: rnam sras kyi sras su bshad pa sogs kyi rgyu mtshan gyis na /
NK131(do)001:1152: sangs rgyas kyi rnam par 'phrul pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa la phyogs re bar mi bsam ste /
NK131(do)001:1155: res 'ga' bgegs chen gdon mdzad cing //
NK131(do)001:1156: skye dang ri bo thams cad do //
NK131(do)001:1159: gang du snang nas kyang sems can gyi don mdzad do //
NK131(do)001:1160: zhes gsungs pa'i don khongs su chud par bya'o //
NK131(do)001:1161: yang 'di dag sangs rgyas kyi rnam par sprul pa ma yin kyang /
NK131(do)001:1162: rdo rje 'chang chen po la dngos su dbang thob pa yang yin la /
NK131(do)001:1163: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa'i srung ma yin pas rgyud
NK131(do)001:1164: dang sgrub thabs 'byung ba mi 'gal ba yin no
NK131(do)001:1165: // khams pa phra mo la sogs pa'i rgyud rnams dang mtshungs pa ma yin te /
NK131(do)001:1166: de dag ni rgyud kyi ming tsam du zad la /
NK131(do)001:1167: 'dir ni mtshan nyid rnams legs par tshang ba'i phyir ro //
NK131(do)001:1168: yang rgyud de dag las 'byung ba'i smin byed dbang gi skabs na /
NK131(do)001:1169: spyir dbang gi lag len 'khrul par bstan pa /
NK131(do)001:1170: bye brag tu sgrub chen gyi lag len 'khrul bar bstan pa /
NK131(do)001:1171: slob dpon la bdag 'jug med pas lag len 'khrul bar bstan pa /
NK131(do)001:1172: dbang bskur dngos kyi lag len 'khrul par bstan pa /
NK131(do)001:1173: zhar la bzlas pa'i sngags sogs ma dag par bstan pa'o //
NK131(do)001:1174: dbang po spyir rnying ma'i dbang gi lag len 'khrul te /
NK131(do)001:1175: gsang sngags gsar ma ltar na slob dpon gyi mtshan nyid sngags sogs dag pa /
NK131(do)001:1176: slob ma'i mtshan nyid snod dang ldan zhing lan gsum gsol ba btab pa /
NK131(do)001:1177: de yang grangs nges pa can /
NK131(do)001:1178: gnas kyi mtshan nyid dben zhing gtsang ba /
NK131(do)001:1179: cho ga'i mtshan nyid sbyor dngos rjes gsum tshangs shing ma 'khrul ba zhig dgos par gsung pa la /
NK131(do)001:1180: rnying ma 'dir bsnyen sogs dag par byed pa'i nges pa'ang mi 'dug cing /
NK131(do)001:1181: de bas rang gi ma thob pa'i dbang gzhan la bskur ba'ang 'ga' zhig snang /
NK131(do)001:1182: slob ma'i skabs su mi 'du tshogs che ba gtso
NK131(do)001:1183: bor 'dzin pa las snod la brtag dpyad mi byed
NK131(do)001:1185: dag kyang slob mas gsol ba mi 'debs te /
NK131(do)001:1186: bla ma rang gi ngos bsrung bar byas te dbang
NK131(do)001:1187: bskur ci thub byed pas dpon slob kyi 'brel pa
NK131(do)001:1188: ma dag / gnas ni skye bo gang 'du'i gnas su bskur bas gnas ma dag /
NK131(do)001:1189: cho ga'i ngo bo ma dag pa ni 'og tu ston te /
NK131(do)001:1190: des na spyir gzhung lugs dang 'ga' ba lta smos kyang ci dgos /
NK131(do)001:1191: rang lugs kyi phun sum tshogs pa lnga dgos par
NK131(do)001:1192: bshad pa dang yang dngos su 'gal bas spyir dbang
NK131(do)001:1194: yang dgos sgrub chen gyi lag len 'khrul te /
NK131(do)001:1195: gsar ma ltar na dpal gsang ba 'dus pa las
NK131(do)001:1196: bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi bshad pa dang mthun par
NK131(do)001:1197: mi snang la / de dang mthun dgos kyi nges pa med na'ang /
NK131(do)001:1198: rnying ma rang lugs kyi bsnyen dbang /
NK131(do)001:1201: sgrub chen bzhi bshad 'dug pa'i de dag gi rnam
NK131(do)001:1202: par dbye ba e dgos zhes dris na 'di la
NK131(do)001:1203: ci smra / kho bos rnying ma rang lugs kyi gzhung lugs la brtags pa na /
NK131(do)001:1204: bsnyen dbang ma song bar sgrub pa la mi dbang /
NK131(do)001:1205: sgrub pa ma byas par sgrub chen la mi dbang bar bshad 'dug pa la /
NK131(do)001:1206: deng sang bsnyen sgrub gang yang med pa'i skye bo
NK131(do)001:1207: rang ga zhig dang lhan cig tu sgrub chen byas
NK131(do)001:1208: pas sgrub chen gyi lag len ma dag /
NK131(do)001:1209: yang rnying ma ba rang gi bdag 'jug ma byas
NK131(do)001:1210: par dbang bskur bas slob dpon gyi las ma dag
NK131(do)001:1211: ste rgyud gzhan dang 'gal ba lta ci smos te
NK131(do)001:1212: / khyed rang gi rta mchog rol chen dang /
NK131(do)001:1213: sgyu 'phrul la sogs gzhung lugs phal che ba'i nang
NK131(do)001:1214: na bdag 'jug dgos par bstan pa 'dug pas so
NK131(do)001:1216: chu sogs 'dod pa gang zhig la chu ster 'dod
NK131(do)001:1217: na rang la chu sogs yod pa zhig dgos la
NK131(do)001:1218: / yod pa de blang pa la ltos dgos par mtshungs pas so //
NK131(do)001:1219: yang dkyil 'khor sgrub pa'i dus na rdo rje rgyal
NK131(do)001:1220: tshab kyi ming btags pa zhig la gzhung phrin gyer
NK131(do)001:1222: slob dpon rang dkyil 'khor las dben pa'i lkog tu
NK131(do)001:1223: gyur pa zhig tu gnas nas dkyil 'khor sgrub blo
NK131(do)001:1225: dbang bskur dngos kyi skabs su dbang rdzas rgyal tshab kyi thogs te dbang bskur ba yod 'dug pas /
NK131(do)001:1226: dbang de slob dpon las thob par 'gyur ram rgyal
NK131(do)001:1227: tshab las thob par 'gyur zhes dri na 'di la
NK131(do)001:1228: ci smra / de la dbang dngos su thob dgos
NK131(do)001:1229: na ni dbang rdzas kyang slob dpon gtad pa cig
NK131(do)001:1230: ci smra / cis kyang dgos / brgyud de thob pas rung na ni /
NK131(do)001:1231: slob dpon gyi rgyal tshab dang /
NK131(do)001:1232: rgyal tshab kyis rang la brgyud pas rgyal tshab de dbang gi brgyud pa la nges par gzhug dgos /
NK131(do)001:1233: des na dbang gi lag len rgyal tshab la bcol
NK131(do)001:1234: ba'ang ma dag pa chen po ste rtsod med kyi
NK131(do)001:1235: gzhung dang mkhas pa'i lag len las mi 'byung bas
NK131(do)001:1236: so // yang rnying ma gyer bsgom gyi khyad par
NK131(do)001:1237: 'phags zer nas rang rang gi las byang du grags
NK131(do)001:1239: dbyangs dang bcas te grub pa na bdag 'dun bum
NK131(do)001:1240: gsum gyi sgrub mchod dus gcig la grub zer bas
NK131(do)001:1241: / 'di yang thabs bskyed rim pa la rtsings pa'i gtam ste /
NK131(do)001:1242: de tsam gyis bskyed rims 'byongs pa la phra mo'i rnal 'byor 'byongs dgos par gsungs la /
NK131(do)001:1244: med pas ni bdag nyid dkyil 'khor 'khor lo gsal
NK131(do)001:1245: ba'i mngon rtogs bsgom tshe mdun bskyed gnyis gsal bar
NK131(do)001:1246: mi 'gyur la / de ma gsal na dkyil 'khor
NK131(do)001:1247: dang bum pa sgrub mchod mtshan nyid pa mi 'ong
NK131(do)001:1248: mi 'gyur la / bas / 'di dag las byang
NK131(do)001:1249: gcig gi tha dad du sgrub pa'i gnad ci yod
NK131(do)001:1250: ces dri na 'di la ci smra /
NK131(do)001:1251: yang las byang gcig gi bzlas par sleb pa na /
NK131(do)001:1252: ming 'dzab tu grags pa sngar gyi dkyil 'khor du
NK131(do)001:1253: ma zhugs pa'i skye bo rnams dang lhan cig tu
NK131(do)001:1254: snying po 'dzab dbyangs su gyer ba zhig 'dug pa
NK131(do)001:1255: 'di pan grub kyi dgongs pa yin nam ma yin
NK131(do)001:1256: / khyed rang gi thugs kyi dam tshig bcu bshad
NK131(do)001:1257: pa'i skabs na lha dang sngags gsang bar bshad pas
NK131(do)001:1259: de bzlas pa byed pa la dbang phyin chad sngags dbang ngag la bskur ba dang /
NK131(do)001:1260: gsang dbang la dgos pa ci yod ces dri na 'di la smra /
NK131(do)001:1261: yang bzlas pa'i skabs na u rgyan gyi thugs sngags yin zer ba zhig snang ba /
NK131(do)001:1262: gzhan rnams legs sbyar sang kri ta'i skad du 'dug pa la /
NK131(do)001:1264: thod pa'i skad dod ka p+aa la dang /
NK131(do)001:1265: phreng ba'i skad dod m+aa le zhes thob rgyu bod du bzhag pa'i dgos pa ci /
NK131(do)001:1266: mkhas pa 'ga' zhig gi smra mdo na /
NK131(do)001:1267: bod yul rmongs pa'i chos lugs 'di //
NK131(do)001:1268: sngags sgra rgya min bod min bklags //
NK131(do)001:1269: gsungs pa 'di lta bu la gsungs pa nges par ma dag pa chen po yin /
NK131(do)001:1270: rtsal rtsal mang po sngags dang gsang mtshan la yod pa 'di bon lugs la grags shing /
NK131(do)001:1271: tshad ldan gyi gzhung lugs na mi snang bas rnying
NK131(do)001:1272: ma bon dang 'dres shes de yang bden nges kyi
NK131(do)001:1274: des na rgya skad bod skad 'dres pa'i sngags de
NK131(do)001:1275: lta bu rnying ma la shin tu mang bar 'dug
NK131(do)001:1276: pas / skyon med kyi sngags su 'gro ba'i 'thad pa gtan tshig ci mchis /
NK131(do)001:1277: zhes gsungs pa la brjod par bya'o //
NK131(do)001:1278: de la 'dir rgyud gsang ba snying po las /
NK131(do)001:1279: slob dpon mnyes par ma byas shing //
NK131(do)001:1280: dbang rnams thob par ma byas na //
NK131(do)001:1281: nyan pa la sogs 'dod pa rnams //
NK131(do)001:1284: kun tu bzang po thugs kyi me long las /
NK131(do)001:1285: gsang sngags dbang la ma brten 'grub par ga la 'gyur //
NK131(do)001:1286: dper na gnyan pa lag skya med pa bzhin //
NK131(do)001:1287: pha rol sgrod par ga la 'gyur //
NK131(do)001:1292: nyams su ting nge 'dzin gyi blangs /
NK131(do)001:1294: dam tshig la gzhi gnas pa dang drug gi chos
NK131(do)001:1295: kyi gnad 'gag thams cad bsdus pa yin pas nges
NK131(do)001:1296: par du dbang bskur ba nyid dgos shing /
NK131(do)001:1297: de la bsnyen sogs dag pa la yang /
NK131(do)001:1298: drang don du bskyed rims pa'i bsnyen pa dang /
NK131(do)001:1299: nges don du rdzogs rim gyi bsnyen pa gnyis /
NK131(do)001:1300: dang po ni lha rang rang gi grangs dang dus dang rtags kyi bsnyen pa gsum yin la /
NK131(do)001:1301: dbang bskur ba la ni de tsam dgos pa ma bshad de /
NK131(do)001:1303: thams cad mkhyen pa'i lam shes pas //
NK131(do)001:1304: sngon du bsnyen pa'i tshogs bsag cing //
NK131(do)001:1305: bgegs ni rnam par nyams byed bya //
NK131(do)001:1306: bsnyen pa med pas dngos grub med //
NK131(do)001:1307: de phyir rim gnyis de nyid rigs //
NK131(do)001:1308: dben par yang dag gnas nas ni //
NK131(do)001:1309: lha yi 'khor lo bsgom par bya //
NK131(do)001:1310: skyo na de yi gsang sngags bzlas //
NK131(do)001:1312: yang na rang gi lhag lha'i 'bum //
NK131(do)001:1313: dkyil 'khor pa yi khri yin te //
NK131(do)001:1314: 'di ni sngon du bsnyen par brjod //
NK131(do)001:1316: kho bo cag gi rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor gyi phreng
NK131(do)001:1317: bar ni dbang po rnon po'i blo ngor byas te
NK131(do)001:1318: dkyil lha bsgom pa'i rim pa dang /
NK131(do)001:1319: snying po bsdus pa brjod pa ni nges par bsgom par bya'o //
NK131(do)001:1321: rdzogs phreng las gsungs pa'i don ni rdzogs rim la
NK131(do)001:1322: dril ba'i rtags bcu rdzogs te rgyun du goms par
NK131(do)001:1323: byas nas / 'od gsal las zung 'jug gi skur
NK131(do)001:1324: bzhengs pa'i tshul gyi gang bsgom par bya ba'i rten
NK131(do)001:1325: dang brten par bcas pa'i dkyil 'khor rigs bdag dang
NK131(do)001:1326: bcas pa gsal bar sgoms nas dkyil 'khor so so'i
NK131(do)001:1327: gtso bo'i snying po dang las thams cad pa'i sngags
NK131(do)001:1329: so so'i gtso bo'i snying po 'bum phrag re dang
NK131(do)001:1330: las thams cad pa'i khri bzlas pas rung bar bshad
NK131(do)001:1331: / yang na rang gi lhag lha'i 'bum zhes pa'i don /
NK131(do)001:1332: rang gi yi dam gsang 'dus yin na de'i bsnyen pa 'bum bzla /
NK131(do)001:1333: de nas bde mchog sogs su bsgyur nas de dang
NK131(do)001:1334: de'i gtso bo'i sngags khri phrag re bzlas pas bsnyen
NK131(do)001:1335: pa 'gro zhing / de ltar bsnyen pa byas nas
NK131(do)001:1336: skad cig gi dkyil 'khor gyi lha'i rnam pa thams
NK131(do)001:1337: cad rdzogs par spro ba dang bsdu bar nus pas
NK131(do)001:1338: slob ma bsdus te dbang bskur bar bya bar slob
NK131(do)001:1340: jo bo chen po rjes rgyud sde lam khyer du ni /
NK131(do)001:1341: rang dgyes rdor du bsgoms nas mdun du gsang ba 'dus pa'i dkyil 'khor bris nas dbang bskur btub /
NK131(do)001:1342: ces gsungs pa dang mthun par /
NK131(do)001:1343: rnying ma ba dag bde gshegs gcig sgrubs rgyal ba kun gyi ngang /
NK131(do)001:1345: rgyal ba thams cad dgongs pa gcig pa'i ngos nas
NK131(do)001:1346: lha gcig gi bsnyen tshad song na lha thams cad
NK131(do)001:1347: kyi bsnyen tshad song bar don gyi thob pa yin
NK131(do)001:1348: zhing / de ltar ma yin na /
NK131(do)001:1350: zhi khro bka' brgyad la sogs pa rnams kyi bsnyen
NK131(do)001:1351: tshad mi tshe gcig la 'gro bar dka' bas na
NK131(do)001:1352: / slob dpon chen pos kyang de go chod par gsungs so //
NK131(do)001:1353: gnyis pa nges don du rdzogs rim gyi bsnyen pa ni /
NK131(do)001:1354: sor bsam gyi stong gzugs dang rdzogs chen gyi 'od
NK131(do)001:1355: gsal don gcig pas de la nges pa'i don gyi
NK131(do)001:1357: sangs rgyas thams cad pa'i bsnyen pa yang 'di yin /
NK131(do)001:1358: de nas srog rtsol gyi srog gzugs dbu ma'i nang
NK131(do)001:1359: du 'gro 'ong byed pa'i rdo rje'i bzlas pa zla
NK131(do)001:1360: ba gcig la drug 'bum rdzogs na dkyil 'khor gyi
NK131(do)001:1361: lha yod do cog gi grangs bsnyen thams cad thems
NK131(do)001:1362: pa yin te / gnyis med rnam rgyal gyi lung rim lngar drangs pa las /
NK131(do)001:1363: 'bum phrag drug kyang bzlas nas su //
NK131(do)001:1364: rdo rje sems dpar phyag byas na //
NK131(do)001:1366: zhes pas des las chen brgyad sogs sgrub pa dang
NK131(do)001:1367: rdo rje slob dpon la dbang ba'i bsnyen pa thems
NK131(do)001:1368: pa yin zhes chag los bshad la /
NK131(do)001:1370: 'dir sngags kyi bzlas pa zhes pa ni srog sdoms pa ste /
NK131(do)001:1371: sogs pa'i sgras dbyung ba dang dgang ba dang bum
NK131(do)001:1372: pa can gyi sbyor ba ni rtag tu bsnyen pa'o
NK131(do)001:1373: // de yi lha mchog ster bar 'gyur te /
NK131(do)001:1374: srog ma sdoms par ngag tu brjod pas ni ma yin no //
NK131(do)001:1376: 'dzin pas skye shi'i las zad rjes dran gyi sgrub pa po stong /
NK131(do)001:1377: gzugs kyi lhar song ba la rdzogs rim gyi lha grub pa zer /
NK131(do)001:1378: de nas ting nge 'dzin gyi las la sbyar bas
NK131(do)001:1379: tshe 'di nyid la mchog gi dngos grub brnyes pa
NK131(do)001:1380: yin / 'di dang rnying ma'i chos nyid zad pa'i snang ba gcig des na +aar+ya de w+aas /
NK131(do)001:1381: dngos gcig dngos po kun gyi rang bzhin te //
NK131(do)001:1382: dngos kun dngos po gcig gi rang bzhin nyid //
NK131(do)001:1383: gang gi dngos gcig de bzhin nyid mthong ba //
NK131(do)001:1384: de yi dngos po kun gyi de nyid mthong //
NK131(do)001:1386: 'jam dpal gyi mtshan yang dag par brjod pa las /
NK131(do)001:1388: dngos po kun gyi rang bzhin mchog /
NK131(do)001:1389: dngos po kun gyi rang bzhin 'dzin //
NK131(do)001:1390: skye med chos te sna tshogs don //
NK131(do)001:1391: ces pas sangs rgyas thams cad dgongs pa dang /
NK131(do)001:1394: ngo bo gcig ces bya ba'i nges don gyi dkyil 'khor grub pa 'di la zer /
NK131(do)001:1395: de bas na rtog pas btags pa'i lha bsgom bzlas la mi ltos te /
NK131(do)001:1396: 'khor 'das thams cad sku gsum gyi rol par shar ba'i phyir ro //
NK131(do)001:1397: de ltar yang dpal brtag pa gnyis pa las /
NK131(do)001:1398: spros pa med pa'i rang bzhin la //
NK131(do)001:1399: lha dang sngags ni yang dag gnas //
NK131(do)001:1401: de ni las dang po pas ma yin no snyam na /
NK131(do)001:1402: dkyil chog rdo rje phreng ba las /
NK131(do)001:1403: bri ba'i cho ga 'di yang yid kyi sgrub pas cho ga nyid kyi 'bras bu dang ldan no //
NK131(do)001:1404: zhes bya ba la sogs pas yid kyi cho ga kho na mchog tu gsungs pas /
NK131(do)001:1405: de nyid kyi phyir dkyil 'khor gyi bdag po'i gzugs kyis bzung ba la sogs pa dang /
NK131(do)001:1406: sku gzugs la sogs pa'i rab gnas dang /
NK131(do)001:1407: slob ma la yang dbang bskur ba dang /
NK131(do)001:1409: zhi ba'i sbyin sreg gi mthar thug pa thams cad yid kyi bya'o //
NK131(do)001:1411: de'i phyir las dang po pas kyang sems brtan pas
NK131(do)001:1412: yid kyi sprul pa'i dkyil 'khor du snga ma bzhin
NK131(do)001:1414: skal ba dang ldan pa la dbang bskur bar bya'o //
NK131(do)001:1415: zhes gsungs pas na skyon med cing nges par rung ba yin la /
NK131(do)001:1416: slob ma mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'i tshul dang /
NK131(do)001:1417: des gsol ba gdab pa sogs 'dir bshad pas smyon du med cing /
NK131(do)001:1420: bdun nas nyi shu rtsa lnga'i bar //
NK131(do)001:1421: zung du ma gyur slob ma bzung //
NK131(do)001:1424: bcu'am brgyad dam bdun nam lnga //
NK131(do)001:1425: gcig gnyis bzhi las lhag kyang rung //
NK131(do)001:1426: dpyad mi dgos par bzung bar bya //
