NK131(do)001:1427: zhes tshad bzung mdzad pa gong ma ni bya rgyud pa'i rang lugs yin gyi /
NK131(do)001:1428: rgyud sde gang ma la rgyas 'gebs dgos pa ni ma yin la /
NK131(do)001:1429: rnam snang mngon byang gi lung drangs ma thag pa de dang 'brel chags su /
NK131(do)001:1430: 'di skad ces gsang ba'i bdag po /
NK131(do)001:1431: gang dag gi sngon theg pa chen po gsang sngags
NK131(do)001:1432: spyad pa'i tshul sgo mtha' yas pa sgrub pa la
NK131(do)001:1433: goms par byas pa de dag ni rdo rje sems
NK131(do)001:1434: dpa' yin te / de rnams nyid kyi don gyi phyir grangs kyi tshad 'di byas so //
NK131(do)001:1435: 'on kyang slob dpon snying rje chen po dang ldan
NK131(do)001:1436: pas sems can gyi khams ma lus pa bsgral bar
NK131(do)001:1437: yid dam bca' ba kho na bya ste des byang
NK131(do)001:1438: chub kyi sems kyi rgyur 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK131(do)001:1439: sems can tshad med pa rnams yongs su bzung bar bya'o //
NK131(do)001:1440: zhes gsungs pas spyod rgyud du yang slob ma la grangs nges ma mdzad /
NK131(do)001:1441: de nyid bsdus pa'i rgyud las /
NK131(do)001:1442: dkyil 'khor chen po 'dir 'jug pa la snod du
NK131(do)001:1443: gyur pa dang ma gyur pa brtag mi 'tshal lo
NK131(do)001:1444: // zhes pas rnal 'byor gyi rgyud du yang grangs nges ma gsung zhing /
NK131(do)001:1445: bla med kyi rgyud rnams su grangs can grangs med kyi kha gsal bshad pa ma mthong yang /
NK131(do)001:1446: don la grangs med gzung chog pa nyid yin te /
NK131(do)001:1447: rigs ldan gyi rgyal po 'jam dpal grags pas /
NK131(do)001:1448: drang srong nyi ma'i shing rta la sogs pa bye ba phrag dgu bcu /
NK131(do)001:1449: dus gcig tu dpal dus kyi 'khor lo'i dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur ba dang /
NK131(do)001:1451: dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga rdo rje phreng bar /
NK131(do)001:1452: skal ba dang ldan na stong gi bar du yang bzung bar bya'o //
NK131(do)001:1453: zhes gsungs pas dbang bskur ba'i slob ma la grang nges par dgos pa yang ma yin no //
NK131(do)001:1454: gnas kyi mtshan nyid dben pa dgos pa yang ma nges te /
NK131(do)001:1456: dur khrod dang ni chu 'grum dang //
NK131(do)001:1457: nags tshal 'bab chu grong khyer du //
NK131(do)001:1458: zhes pas 'du 'dzin can gyi skye bo'i grong khyer du yang rung bar bshad cing /
NK131(do)001:1459: slob ma'i skabs su mi'i 'du tshogs gtso bor bzung
NK131(do)001:1460: nas snod la brtag dpyad mi byed pas snod ma
NK131(do)001:1463: dkyil 'khor chen po 'dir 'jug pa la snod du
NK131(do)001:1464: gyur pa dang ma gyur pa brtag mi 'tshal lo
NK131(do)001:1466: dkyil 'khor mthong ba tsam gyi sdig pa 'dag pa'i phyir ro //
NK131(do)001:1467: zhes gsungs pa nyid kyi gsal ba yin la /
NK131(do)001:1468: rgyu mtshan de dag gis ni spyir rnying ma ba
NK131(do)001:1469: dag gi dbang gi lag len ma 'khrul ba bstan
NK131(do)001:1470: pa yin no // da ni yang dgos sgrub chen
NK131(do)001:1471: gyi lag len 'khrul zhes gsung ba la brjod par
NK131(do)001:1472: pa yin no // bya ste / de la sgrub chen zhes pa /
NK131(do)001:1474: bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi rdo rje gsum dang sbyor ba yan lag drug dang sbyar te /
NK131(do)001:1475: thog mar dge ba sku rdo rje bsnyen pa'i yan lag /
NK131(do)001:1476: bar du dge ba gsung rdo rje nyer sgrub kyi yan lag /
NK131(do)001:1477: tha mar dge ba thugs dang ye shes rdo rje
NK131(do)001:1478: sgrub pa dang sgrub chen gyi yan lag ces gsungs
NK131(do)001:1479: pa dang / 'dir gsang ba snying po las /
NK131(do)001:1480: bsnyen pa dang ni nye bsnyen dang //
NK131(do)001:1481: sgrub pa dang ni sgrub chen po //
NK131(do)001:1483: bde ba thugs kyi dkyil 'khor spro //
NK131(do)001:1484: zhes tshig tu mi 'dra yang don la khyad par med pa nyid du yod la /
NK131(do)001:1485: dpal ye shes snying po'i rgyud las /
NK131(do)001:1486: lta ba rang rig ye shes te //
NK131(do)001:1487: ngo sprod rnam bzhis gtan la phabs //
NK131(do)001:1488: rang rig mtshan nyid nyams su myong //
NK131(do)001:1489: de ni bsnyen pa'i don du bshad //
NK131(do)001:1491: lam la gnas pa nye bsnyen yin //
NK131(do)001:1493: lam grol grub pa sgrub pa yin //
NK131(do)001:1495: lam gyi 'bras bu mthar phyin pa //
NK131(do)001:1496: sgrub pa chen por bstan pa'o //
NK131(do)001:1498: rtogs pa rnam bzhi bsnyen sgrub bzhi //
NK131(do)001:1499: gsang sngags mi bzlas don la bzhag /
NK131(do)001:1500: phyag rgya mi bsgom mi bskyed par //
NK131(do)001:1502: zhes pas gsang ba 'dus pa dang gur dang brtag
NK131(do)001:1503: pa gnyis pa dang ri gi a ra li dang
NK131(do)001:1504: dpal dus kyi 'khor lo nas bshad pa'i bsnyen bsgrub
NK131(do)001:1505: bzhi dang tshul khyad par med par yod do //
NK131(do)001:1506: da ltar grags pa'i sgrub chen zhes bya ba 'di
NK131(do)001:1507: ni rnying ma rang lugs kyi dkyil 'khor gyi sgrub
NK131(do)001:1508: mchod chen po zhes pa yin no //
NK131(do)001:1509: de la spyir btang du phun sum tshogs pa snga sngon du 'gro dgos par bshad de /
NK131(do)001:1510: gnas phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK131(do)001:1512: gang na sa skyong chos ldan zhing //
NK131(do)001:1513: gang zhig kho nar skye dgu rnams //
NK131(do)001:1514: bder gnas sa 'dzin rtsod med pa //
NK131(do)001:1515: der ni rnal 'byor brtsoms par bya //
NK131(do)001:1517: ston pa phun sum tshogs pa rdo rje slob dpon la bya ste /
NK131(do)001:1518: rab chos nyid kyi bden pa mthong ba /
NK131(do)001:1519: 'bring yi dam lha'i gnang ba thob pa /
NK131(do)001:1520: tha ma cho ga lag len la mkhas shing byin
NK131(do)001:1521: rlabs kyi brgyud pa sel med cing bar ma chad
NK131(do)001:1523: dus phun sum tshogs pa phyi nang gi 'byung ba cha snyoms shing /
NK131(do)001:1524: dus kyi 'khrug pa dang nad dang mu ge la sogs mi bde ba med pa'i dus su bya /
NK131(do)001:1525: yo byad phun sum tshogs pa rang rang gi gzhung 'byung ba'i gang dgos tshang ba la bya /
NK131(do)001:1526: grogs phun sum tshogs pa dbang rten thabs shes /
NK131(do)001:1538: las kyi rdo rje ste med du mi rung ba dang der 'dus pa dag la bya /
NK131(do)001:1539: de nas dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo gang yin pa
NK131(do)001:1540: de'i don dbang ngam sku gsum thugs kyi byin rlabs
NK131(do)001:1541: brtsal bas / sngar sngags kyi sgor ma zhugs pa
NK131(do)001:1542: der 'dus pa rnams kyi rgyud gsang sngags kyi snod
NK131(do)001:1544: 'di la gsang sngags bka' ma pa dag bsnyen dbang zer /
NK131(do)001:1545: bka' brgyad bde gshegs 'dus pa la sogs pa'i gter ma rnams su snying po rgyud dbang du btags /
NK131(do)001:1546: de nas bsgom bzlas kyi phung po gnas sgrub pa
NK131(do)001:1547: zhugs pas gsang sgrog tu ga la 'gyur te dbang
NK131(do)001:1548: dang lung sbyin grub pas so //
NK131(do)001:1549: de nas grub pa rtags dang mtshan ma mthong gi bar sgrub pa la sgrub pa zer /
NK131(do)001:1550: de ltar grub nas thog mar rdo rje slob dpon gyi dbang dang dngos grub blang /
NK131(do)001:1551: de nas rim gyi slob ma la dbang bskur ba yin te /
NK131(do)001:1552: rgyas par zhi khro dang phur pa dang /
NK131(do)001:1556: sha rim sgrub pa rnams su lha'o //
NK131(do)001:1557: de ltar sgrub pa'i sngon du don dbang dang bzlas
NK131(do)001:1558: lung phog pas bsnyen dbang de nas bsgom bzlas gzhung
NK131(do)001:1560: thun mtshams su dbang dang dngos grub len pa ni
NK131(do)001:1561: sgrub dbang dngos kyi mtshan ma mthong ba ni sgrub
NK131(do)001:1563: thod gar nam mkha' yi ge ni /
NK131(do)001:1564: nye bsnyen yan gong ltar la /
NK131(do)001:1565: dngos grub kyi mtshan ma mthong nas slob dpon gyi dbang bskur te sgrub dbang /
NK131(do)001:1566: de nas phyag rgya chen po mchog gi grub bsgrub pa sgrub pa chen po zhes 'dod do //
NK131(do)001:1567: lung 'di la slob dpon snga ma dag gi bzhed pa mang du yod par grags na yang /
NK131(do)001:1568: bdag gis ni gnyis po 'di la ma mthong ngo //
NK131(do)001:1569: slob dpon gyi dbang bskur ba'i sngon du bdag 'jug
NK131(do)001:1570: blang ba ni nges par bshad cing phyag srol la
NK131(do)001:1572: 'on kyang bla ma de rdzogs pa chen po'i don
NK131(do)001:1573: rgyud la 'phrod pa zhig yin na slob ma la
NK131(do)001:1574: ji ltar bskur ba'i tshul du dbang rdzas phra mo
NK131(do)001:1575: yan chad nas blangs dgos pa ma yin te /
NK131(do)001:1576: ye shes ting nge 'dzin gyi dbang blangs ba nyid mchog yin pas so //
NK131(do)001:1577: des 'jam dpal sgyu 'phrul dra ba las /
NK131(do)001:1578: ye shes dbang bskur co pan can //
NK131(do)001:1579: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rgyan du mthong //
NK131(do)001:1580: sdug bsngal gsum gyi sdug bsngal zhi //
NK131(do)001:1581: gsum sel mtha' yas grol gsum thob //
NK131(do)001:1583: ye shes rngams pa glog gi 'khor lo las //
NK131(do)001:1584: sems kyi chos la dbang thob na //
NK131(do)001:1585: rdzas tshig mtshan ma'i dbang rnams kun //
NK131(do)001:1586: ma bskur par yang thob par 'gyur //
NK131(do)001:1587: zhes pas de thob nas de bzhin gshegs pa'i las rab 'byams la dbang thob pa yin no //
NK131(do)001:1589: dbang chog ji lta ba'i tshul gyi bdag 'jug len pa legs mod kyi /
NK131(do)001:1590: dbang chog gi shar byang tsam yin nam snyam mo //
NK131(do)001:1591: 'on kyang dbang thob la ma nyams pa des bdag
NK131(do)001:1592: nyid 'jug cing dbang len pa mi 'gogs te bdag
NK131(do)001:1593: nyid zhugs shing dbang blangs pas dbang gi chu bo
NK131(do)001:1594: ma nyams pa de gong 'phel du song nas dngos
NK131(do)001:1595: grub myur du thob pa'i rgyud byed pa yin no
NK131(do)001:1596: // don du na dbang bskur ba'i sngon du bdag
NK131(do)001:1597: 'jug len pa bla ma rang gi ma tshor bar
NK131(do)001:1598: dam tshig nyams pa srid pas de gso ba'i ched
NK131(do)001:1599: // du yin gyi / de lta bu'i skyon med
NK131(do)001:1600: na gsar du bdag 'jug len dgos pa'ang ma yin
NK131(do)001:1601: // du yin gyi / te / bla ma rang
NK131(do)001:1602: nyid dbang thob la ma nyams par yod bzhin pa
NK131(do)001:1603: yin pas slar gzhan nas blang mi dgos pa nyid
NK131(do)001:1604: // du yin gyi / te / yin la /
NK131(do)001:1605: bran mo chu len pa ltar gcig nas blangs te
NK131(do)001:1606: gcig tu 'jo ba lta bu ma yin no //
NK131(do)001:1607: slob dpon dkyil 'khor gyi lkog tu 'dug nas sgrubs pa'i lag len kyang ma 'khrul pa yin te /
NK131(do)001:1608: 'di ltar snang grags kyis bsdus pa'i snod kyi 'jig rten gzhal yas khang //
NK131(do)001:1609: bcud rnams lha la grags pa sngags //
NK131(do)001:1610: dran rtogs chos nyid du shes na //
NK131(do)001:1611: gsang sngags pa zhes de la bya //
NK131(do)001:1612: zhes pa 'di gsang sngags kyi don mthar thug yin pas /
NK131(do)001:1613: de lta bu'i don las mi 'bral ba'i skyes bu
NK131(do)001:1614: de gang du gnas kyang bskyed rdzogs kyi rol pa
NK131(do)001:1615: las ma 'das pas na gang du 'dug kyang rung
NK131(do)001:1616: ste / dkyil 'khor gyi drung kho nar gnas dgos pa yang ma yin no //
NK131(do)001:1617: dbang rdzas rgyal tshab kyi thogs kyang dbang slob dpon las thob pa yin te /
NK131(do)001:1618: dper na pho nyas rgyal po'i lung dang bka' rtags khyer te 'bangs kyi tshogs la sgrags pa na /
NK131(do)001:1619: pho nya ba'i ngag de rgyal po'i ngag tu 'dzin pa dang mtshungs pa nyid do //
NK131(do)001:1620: de tsam gyi rgyal tshab dbang brgyud la 'jug dgos na /
NK131(do)001:1621: bde ba myu gu'i rgyud las /
NK131(do)001:1622: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba sras bcas kyi //
NK131(do)001:1623: mkha' mnyam ye shes bdud rtsi ni //
NK131(do)001:1624: rdo rje'i lam nas rab bsdus nas //
NK131(do)001:1625: bde ba bskyed byed rigs kyi yum //
NK131(do)001:1626: sras rnams gsang ba'i dbang bskur bas //
NK131(do)001:1627: rdo rje'i bla ma gnyis pa'o //
NK131(do)001:1630: lhan cig skyes pa dpe bral ba //
NK131(do)001:1631: nam mkha' dang ni mnyam par sbyor //
NK131(do)001:1632: rigs mnyam dpe med bde ster ma //
NK131(do)001:1633: sring mo de nyid bla mar basngagasa //
NK131(do)001:1634: zhes pas gsang ba'i dbang dang shes rab ye shes
NK131(do)001:1635: kyi dbang gnyis rig ma la rten nas thob dgos
NK131(do)001:1636: par gsung na / rig ma de dbang brgyud la 'jug gam ci /
NK131(do)001:1637: las byang tshar gcig gi bdag mdun bum gsum cig char du sgrub sgrub pa'i tshul yang /
NK131(do)001:1638: sngags bla na med pa'i rnal 'byor pa de'i bsam don ni /
NK131(do)001:1639: ji ltar snang ba 'di thams cad ye shes kyi
NK131(do)001:1640: ngo bor dus rtag tu longs spyod pa yin la
NK131(do)001:1642: snang grags kyi chos ji snyed pa thams cad ye
NK131(do)001:1643: gdod ma nas yod ma myong bas gnyis dang gsum
NK131(do)001:1644: du 'dzin pa la sogs pa spros pa'i mtha' thams
NK131(do)001:1645: cad dang bral ba 'di nyid la mi 'dra ba'i
NK131(do)001:1646: dbye ba ci yang yod pa ma yin pas rang
NK131(do)001:1648: mchog gi dang po'i skyes bu dang /
NK131(do)001:1650: sgyu 'phrul dra ba la sogs pa'i ming gis gdags so //
NK131(do)001:1651: de'i lta bu'i chos nyid bsam du med pa de'i rang rtsal las /
NK131(do)001:1652: chu las nya ldang ba ltar du bdag mdun bum
NK131(do)001:1653: gsum skad cig la lha'i 'khor lo ji lta ba
NK131(do)001:1654: bzhin du bskyed nas gzhan nas 'byung ba med pa'i
NK131(do)001:1655: tshul gyis spyan drangs pa dang /
NK131(do)001:1656: rang gi rig rtsal ma 'gags pa las byung ba'i
NK131(do)001:1657: mchod pa'i sprin spungs kyi dmigs pa med pa'i tshul
NK131(do)001:1658: du rang la mchod pa dang /
NK131(do)001:1659: sangs rgyas rnams kyi yon tan lhun gyis grub cing
NK131(do)001:1660: spros pa mtha' dag las grol ba'i tshul gyis bstod
NK131(do)001:1661: pa dang / zag pa med pa'i bde ba chen
NK131(do)001:1662: po'i rang bzhin rnam par rtog pa'i rgyun las 'das
NK131(do)001:1663: pa'i tshogs kyi 'khor lo'i mchod pa 'bul ba la
NK131(do)001:1664: pa dang / sogs pa / so so'i las byang gi tshig gi gsal btab nas khyer te /
NK131(do)001:1665: sngags kyi bzlas pa las so so'i go rim ltar
NK131(do)001:1666: gsal la rtog pa med par 'dzab dgongs dang ma
NK131(do)001:1667: bral bar bzlas pas bdag mdun bum gsum cig char
NK131(do)001:1668: du sgrub zin par ma zad /
NK131(do)001:1669: rgyud sde rgya mtsho'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha thams cad gdan thog gcig tu sgrub zin pa yin te /
NK131(do)001:1670: rigs brgya la sogs pa'i lha thams cad kyang rang
NK131(do)001:1671: gi sems rnam par dag pa'i rol pa yin pas
NK131(do)001:1672: so // de lta bu'i chos nyid kyi rol pa de la bdag bskyed pa dang /
NK131(do)001:1674: bum pa bskyed pa la sogs pa'i 'dzin rtog gang
NK131(do)001:1675: yang med pa ni dkyil 'khor sgrub pa'i mchog ste
NK131(do)001:1676: / spros pa med pa'i rang bzhin la //
NK131(do)001:1677: lha dang sngags ni yang dag gnas //
NK131(do)001:1679: de dag gi lung mang po go rim bzhin du /
NK131(do)001:1680: ji ltar dwangs pa'i chu klungs las //
NK131(do)001:1681: nya dag myur du 'phar ba ltar //
NK131(do)001:1682: de bzhin stong pa'i 'od gsal las //
NK131(do)001:1686: sems can rdzus te skye ba ltar //
NK131(do)001:1687: sa bon med par bskyed par bya //
NK131(do)001:1690: lha nyid rang la rang nyid lha //
NK131(do)001:1691: rang dang lhan cig skyes pa la //
NK131(do)001:1693: rang sems bla ma lha ru gnas //
NK131(do)001:1695: rta mgrin bdud rtsi thig pa las /
NK131(do)001:1696: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod chen po //
NK131(do)001:1697: rang las spros shing rang la mchod //
NK131(do)001:1698: ma 'gag ye shes rol pa'i rgyan //
NK131(do)001:1699: rang byung lhun grub gzhan nas min //
NK131(do)001:1701: mchod pa chen po chags pa che //
NK131(do)001:1702: chags pa thams cad sel bar byed //
NK131(do)001:1705: yid bzhin nor bu dpag bsam shing //
NK131(do)001:1706: ji ltar re ba yongs bskong ba //
NK131(do)001:1707: de bzhin gdul bya'i smon lam gyi //
NK131(do)001:1708: dbang gi rgyal ba'i skur snang ngo //
NK131(do)001:1711: mi 'dzin sgyu ma lta bu la //
NK131(do)001:1712: dgos pa'i tshul gyis rol par mdzad //
NK131(do)001:1714: thugs srog sngags kyi 'od zer spro //
NK131(do)001:1715: bsdus te snang sems gnyis med bsre //
NK131(do)001:1716: rtag tu bzlas brjod ba rtson gyur na //
NK131(do)001:1718: ces rta mgrin sgrub thabs su bshad pa ltar ro //
NK131(do)001:1719: de lta bu'i rnal 'byor pa la snang srid thams
NK131(do)001:1720: cad ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du shar ba yin
NK131(do)001:1722: dza pa zhes pa'i zur chag pa yin la /
NK131(do)001:1723: bod skad du bzlas pa zhes bya ste /
NK131(do)001:1724: gong du smos pa ltar bzlas pa'i lung sbyin pa yin pas gsang sgrog tu mi 'gyur zhing /
NK131(do)001:1726: bung ba tshang tshol ba lta bu'i bzlas pa zhes dang /
NK131(do)001:1727: rdo rje srin po'i ngur sgra zhes rang lugs kyi
NK131(do)001:1728: gzhung nas bshad pas pan grub kyi dgongs pa yang
NK131(do)001:1729: yin no // sngags dbang ngag la bskur ba ni rang rkang gi skabs thob yin la /
NK131(do)001:1732: dang po thabs mchog yab las te //
NK131(do)001:1733: gnyis pa shes rab yum las so //
NK131(do)001:1734: zhes pas bla ma ni slob dpon gyi rig ma yin la /
NK131(do)001:1735: slob ma ni bum dbang sngon du song ba /
NK131(do)001:1736: dbang gong ma la mos pa /
NK131(do)001:1737: gtsang rme'i rtog pa chung ba'o //
NK131(do)001:1738: dkyil 'khor ni rig ma de'i b+ha ga ste /
NK131(do)001:1740: dkyil 'khor lus su gsung pa ste //
NK131(do)001:1741: de ni b+ha gar bstan pa'o //
NK131(do)001:1743: bskur ba'i gnas ni slob ma'i lce la ste /
NK131(do)001:1745: rdo rje'i lam nas byung nas ni //
NK131(do)001:1746: slob ma'i khar ni dbab par bya //
NK131(do)001:1747: 'di ni gsang sngags de kun gyi //
NK131(do)001:1748: dbang bskur ba yi go 'phangs mchog /
NK131(do)001:1750: sgrib pa ngag gi 'dag pa ste //
NK131(do)001:1752: ngag gi sgrib pa des sbyangs nas //
NK131(do)001:1755: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med pa stong pa'i ngang du ro gcig pa ste /
NK131(do)001:1756: shes rab thabs kyi nga rgyal byed //
NK131(do)001:1757: chos kun ro gcig shes rab 'gyur //
NK131(do)001:1758: sangs rgyas sa ni mngon sum thob //
NK131(do)001:1760: 'bras bu ni shes rab dri ma med pa la sogs la thob pa yin te /
NK131(do)001:1761: shes rab dri med 'bras bur bshad //
NK131(do)001:1762: rgyu mthun khu ba'i ngo bo yin //
NK131(do)001:1763: zhes dbang rin chen 'khor lo nas gsungs so //
NK131(do)001:1764: de ltar gsang dbang gi dgos pa ni /
NK131(do)001:1766: sngags bzla ba kho na la gsang dbang nges par bskur dgos pa ma yin /
NK131(do)001:1767: de dag gis ni sgrub chen gyi lag len ma 'khrul pa'i tshul rgyas par bstan pa yin no //
NK131(do)001:1768: u rgyan gyi thugs sngags su rgya skad bod skad 'dres pa la yang skyon ma mchis te /
NK131(do)001:1769: 'di dag sang kri ta'i skad ma shes pas bod skad du bzhag pa ma yin /
NK131(do)001:1770: nus pa myur du 'byung ba'i phyir sdebs pa yin te /
NK131(do)001:1771: jo bo chen po rje'i rta mgrin gyi sngags kyang gzhan rnams legs sbyar du yod pa la /
NK131(do)001:1772: rgyal 'gong rgyal tshe la sha la ngom /
NK131(do)001:1774: zhes bod skad sor bzhag mang po dang /
NK131(do)001:1776: rdo rje lce dbab pa'i rgyud las /
NK131(do)001:1777: sa gdon nag po sod sod /
NK131(do)001:1780: rdo rje bde khros kyi rgyud las /
NK131(do)001:1781: ma ra na myos byings thums ril dza //
NK131(do)001:1783: phyag rdor gsang ba mngon bstan gyi rgyud las /
NK131(do)001:1784: ma ra ya rak+ta rngubs rngubs /
NK131(do)001:1785: ma ra ya kem choms choms /
NK131(do)001:1786: ma h+aa ma nu ma ra ya gtubs gtubs /
NK131(do)001:1788: ha kri khug ha kri khug /
NK131(do)001:1792: lus dul ma ra ya rbad /
NK131(do)001:1801: ngag gram ti tig tig gra tha brag shig /
NK131(do)001:1805: ra tsa tsit+ta rbad nan hur thums dzahdang /
NK131(do)001:1806: gtum po rgyud phyi ma'i phyi mar /
NK131(do)001:1807: kha rag nag po khrag ma ra ya n+ri ma ra dza khug /
NK131(do)001:1809: mgon po gsang ba dngos grub 'byung ba'i rgyud kyi lha mo'i sngags la /
NK131(do)001:1810: rag mo tsit+ta kha rag ma h'u b+h+yo /
NK131(do)001:1812: tshal pa tshal pa ni sha ku ru sa ma ya gtubs gtubs dzah zhes sogs mang po dang /
NK131(do)001:1813: phyag na rdo rje u tsar+ya'i sngags la yang /
NK131(do)001:1814: pu pu dan du nag po bam tsi tsi rgyas
NK131(do)001:1815: drag thur snying la thur nyams rtsa bzhi skums shan
NK131(do)001:1816: shan srog la shan sogs mang po dang /
NK131(do)001:1817: dpal sa skya pa'i bstan bsrung pu tra ming sring gi sngags la yang yang /
NK131(do)001:1820: li shig ste rmugs rmugs spu gri a li ma /
NK131(do)001:1821: zhes sogs mang po snang ngo //
NK131(do)001:1822: 'di dag las kha cig ni ma 'ongs pa'i dus su sngags kyi nus pa mi 'byung bas /
NK131(do)001:1823: sngags 'gro ba gzhan gyi skad du bsgyur nas bzlas
NK131(do)001:1824: na nus pa 'byung ba la dgongs nas rdo rje
NK131(do)001:1825: 'chang nyid kyis gsungs pa yang yod la /
NK131(do)001:1826: kha cig ni bsdus po rnams kyis de ltar bsdus shing /
NK131(do)001:1827: 'ga' zhig ni lo pan grub pa brnyes pa rnams
NK131(do)001:1828: kyi ma 'ongs pa la phan par dgongs nas de
NK131(do)001:1829: ltar du bsgyur ba yang yod de /
NK131(do)001:1830: pu tra'i sngags 'di lo chen rin bzang bon po
NK131(do)001:1831: dang 'gras pa'i dus su pu tra 'gro ma 'dod
NK131(do)001:1832: pa la sngags zhang zhung gi skad du bsgyur bas
NK131(do)001:1833: nus pa thon zhes pa lo rgyus su 'byung zhing
NK131(do)001:1834: / slob dpon pad+mas gter du sbas pa rgya ston
NK131(do)001:1835: pad+ma dbang phyug gi phyung ba la yang de ltar
NK131(do)001:1837: gzhan yang rnying ma'i rgyud rnams na /
NK131(do)001:1838: 'a dang ca cha ja zha sa sogs rgya gar la ma grags pa yod de /
NK131(do)001:1839: de dag kyang 'gro ba mtha' yas pa'i skad du
NK131(do)001:1840: gsungs pa'i don yin pas na yi ge de dag
NK131(do)001:1841: mkha' 'gro ma dang 'gro ba gzhan gyi skad la
NK131(do)001:1842: yod do // yang de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung gcig
NK131(do)001:1843: la so so'i skad dang dbang po dang bsam pa
NK131(do)001:1844: ji lta ba bzhin du so sor go ba yin
NK131(do)001:1845: yod do // te / sangs rgyas phal po che'i mdo las /
NK131(do)001:1846: rgyal ba'i gsung dbyangs gcig la mtha' yas pa'i //
NK131(do)001:1847: chos kyi sgo mo sna tshogs kun kyang 'byung //
NK131(do)001:1850: 'jig rten kun gyi mos pa sna tshogs dang //
NK131(do)001:1851: bsam pa ji bzhin sbyor ba rnam dpyod pa //
NK131(do)001:1852: de dag ji bzhin rgyal ba'i chos ston te //
NK131(do)001:1853: rang byung mos pa mkhyen pa'i stobs ston to //
NK131(do)001:1856: lha yi skad dang klu dang gnod sbyin skad //
NK131(do)001:1857: grul bum dag dang mi yi skad rnams dang //
NK131(do)001:1858: 'gro ba kun gyi sgra rnams ji tsam pa //
NK131(do)001:1859: thams cad skad du bdag gi chos bstan to //
NK131(do)001:1861: bde mchog sdom 'byung la sogs pa ni kla klo'i
NK131(do)001:1862: skad du gsung pa la sogs pa mtha' yas shing
NK131(do)001:1864: 'dir ma 'ongs pa'i dus na byis pa'i skye bo
NK131(do)001:1865: ming tshig yi ge la brten pa de dag gis
NK131(do)001:1866: rgyud thams cad du 'di skad bdag gi zhes sogs
NK131(do)001:1867: sangs rgyas kyi bzhugs gnas nges par bstan par de
NK131(do)001:1868: bzhin gshegs pas gsungs par gang brjod pa de ni
NK131(do)001:1869: ma yin te / gang gi phyir chos ston pa
NK131(do)001:1870: po'i sangs rgyas don la brton pa nyid kyi phyir
NK131(do)001:1871: ma yin te / dang / sdud par byed pa
NK131(do)001:1872: po rnams kyis kyang yul sna tshogs kyi skad kyis
NK131(do)001:1873: yang dag par 'byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK131(do)001:1875: ston pa sangs rgyas kyis 'gro ba mtha' yas pa'i skad du gsungs pa /
NK131(do)001:1876: sdud pa po rnams kyis kyang yul so so'i skad kyis bsdus par gsungs shing /
NK131(do)001:1878: re zhig yul gyi khyad par gzhan lta zhog gi /
NK131(do)001:1879: de bzhin gshegs pa mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa /
NK131(do)001:1880: 'phags yul 'dir bcom ldan 'das yongs su mya ngan las 'das par gyur pa na /
NK131(do)001:1881: sdud par byed pa po dag gi theg pa gsum glegs bam la bris te /
NK131(do)001:1882: de bzhin gshegs pa'i nges pa'i sde snod gsum ma ga ta'i skad kyis so //
NK131(do)001:1883: mdo sde ni sin d+hu'i skad kyis so //
NK131(do)001:1884: pha rol tu phyin pa'i tshul dang sngags kyi tshul ni legs sbyar gyi skad kyis so //
NK131(do)001:1885: rgyud dang rgyud gzhan ni legs sbyar dang tha mal pa'i skad dang /
NK131(do)001:1887: legs sbyar ma yin pa ri khrod pa la sogs pa ka klo'i skad de /
NK131(do)001:1888: de lta bu la sogs pa thams cad mkhyen pas
NK131(do)001:1889: bstan pa'i chos rnams sdud par byed pa pos bris
NK131(do)001:1890: so // de bzhin du theg pa gsum bod kyi yul du bod kyi skad kyis bris te /
NK131(do)001:1891: rgya nag tu rgya nag gi skad kyis so //
NK131(do)001:1892: de bzhin du rgya nag chen po /
NK131(do)001:1897: rug ma su ram ma'i skad kyis so //
NK131(do)001:1898: de ltar grong bye ba'i bdag nyid yul dgu bcu
NK131(do)001:1899: rtsa drug rnams su dgu bcu rtsa drug gi skad
NK131(do)001:1900: kyis so // de bzhin du bum bu bcu gnyis dang /
NK131(do)001:1902: mi'i yul dang sa 'og rnams su sems can sna
NK131(do)001:1903: tshogs kyi skad kyis sdud par byed pa po dag
NK131(do)001:1904: gis theg pa gsum bris te /
NK131(do)001:1905: nyan thos rnams kyi nyan thos kyi theg pa dang /
NK131(do)001:1906: rang sangs rgyas rnams kyi rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa dang /
NK131(do)001:1907: byang sems rnams kyi theg pa chen po phar phyin dang /
NK131(do)001:1908: theg pa chen po gsang sngags rgyu dang 'bras bu'i bdag nyid de /
NK131(do)001:1909: sdud par byed pa po sna tshogs kyis sems can rnams 'dul bar byed pa'i don du'o //
NK131(do)001:1910: sdud par byed pa po sna tshogs kyi yul sna
NK131(do)001:1911: tshogs kyi skad kyi bris pa'i lung dang rigs pa
NK131(do)001:1913: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das thams cad mkhyen pa /
NK131(do)001:1914: thams cad mkhyen pa'i skad kyis chos ston pa po yin gyi /
NK131(do)001:1915: khyab 'jug dang drag po la sogs pa gzhan ni ma yin no //
NK131(do)001:1916: ci ste khyab 'jug dang drag po la sogs pa
NK131(do)001:1917: rnams kyi nang na yon tan 'di dag rdzogs pa
NK131(do)001:1919: de yang bdag cag gis rnam pa thams cad du phyag bya ba dang /
NK131(do)001:1921: bkur stir bya ba yin no //
NK131(do)001:1923: mdo rgyud rnams kyi tshigs dang /
NK131(do)001:1924: sngags kyi sgra rnams sang kri skad kho nar nges
NK131(do)001:1925: pa ma yin pa'i tshul gsal bar bstan zin to
NK131(do)001:1926: // rtsal rtsal mang po sngags dang gsang mtshan la
NK131(do)001:1927: yod pas rnying ma bon dang 'dres pa yang mi
NK131(do)001:1928: // 'grub ste / chos kyi sgo brgyad khri bzhi stong gi cha 'dra ba tsam re /
NK131(do)001:1929: bon brgyad khri bzhi stong la yang yod pas /
NK131(do)001:1930: mthar thug gi skyel so mi gcig kyang /
NK131(do)001:1931: gnas skabs su 'dra ba mang po snang bas ma nges pa yin no //
NK131(do)001:1932: sngags sgra rgya min bod min bklag /
NK131(do)001:1934: rgya skad ma dag par 'don pa rnams la gsungs pa yin la /
NK131(do)001:1935: thod phreng rtsal zhes bod skad sor bzhag rgya min bod min du mi 'grub bo //
NK131(do)001:1936: yang rgyud de dag gi don yin pa ltar bcos
NK131(do)001:1937: pa'i gdams pa rnams kyi gzhi bshad pa'i skabs na
NK131(do)001:1938: / gsar ma lugs ni klu sgrub dpa' bo la
NK131(do)001:1939: sogs 'phags yul gyi mkhas grub phal mo che dang
NK131(do)001:1940: / / khyad par chos kyi grags pa'i bzhed pas /
NK131(do)001:1941: de la kun gzhi'i rnam shes ni //
NK131(do)001:1942: ngo bo ma sgribs lung ma bstan //
NK131(do)001:1943: ces pa ltar me long rang gi ngo bo'i dus na gzugs brnyan gyi stong pa bzhin du /
NK131(do)001:1944: kun gzhi rang gi ngo bo'i dus na tshogs bdun sems byung dang bcas pas stong pa /
NK131(do)001:1945: gzugs brnyan cir yang snang rung gi gsal ba mi 'dor ba bzhin du /
NK131(do)001:1946: 'khor 'das lam gsum gyi bag chags 'jog rung gi nus pa mi 'dor ba /
NK131(do)001:1947: yul rkyen dang ma phrad pa'i me long rang gi
NK131(do)001:1948: dus na lung ma bstan gyi gsal ba yin pa
NK131(do)001:1949: bzhin / kun gzhi 'khrul grol 'du byed ma g.yos
NK131(do)001:1950: pa'i dus na 'khor 'das kyi phyogs su ma lhung
NK131(do)001:1951: ba'i lung ma bstan du bzhed pa la /
NK131(do)001:1952: khyed rnams kyi lugs la gzhi ka dag dang ye grol du 'dod zer ba /
NK131(do)001:1953: khyed rang gi lugs la ka dag dang kun gzhi gcig gam tha dad /
NK131(do)001:1954: gcig na kun gzhi 'khor 'das gnyis kyi spyi gzhi
NK131(do)001:1955: yin pa'i don gyi lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig
NK131(do)001:1956: pa yod la / de ma rig pa thams cad
NK131(do)001:1957: kyi rtsa ba yin pas ka nas dag pa dang
NK131(do)001:1958: ye grol gyi don ma tshang /
NK131(do)001:1959: kun gzhi dang ka dag gnyis mi gcig tha dad na /
NK131(do)001:1960: ka dag dang kun gzhi thog mar gang snga /
NK131(do)001:1962: dang po ka dag la rjes zhi gnas kun gzhi'i
NK131(do)001:1963: gnas lugs su byung ba ni lung rig gi ngos
NK131(do)001:1965: kun gzhi ni 'khor 'das kyi phyogs su ma lhung ba'i gdod ma'i gnas lugs yin la /
NK131(do)001:1966: de'i gong ma gang yod med pas so //
NK131(do)001:1967: kun gzhi snga na ka dag dang ye grol du mi 'gyur bas /
NK131(do)001:1968: de bas na ka dag ces pa ni bon gyi gzhung na /
NK131(do)001:1969: dang po ye med du 'dod pa ka dag dang /
NK131(do)001:1970: de las ye yod cung zad srid pa la ma
NK131(do)001:1971: rtogs pa 'khor ba'i 'khrul gzhi zhes ming 'dogs bsgyur
NK131(do)001:1972: ba yin mod / ces gsungs pa la /
NK131(do)001:1973: kun gzhi zhes pa'i ngo bo ni /
NK131(do)001:1974: 'dus ma byas brjod du med pa'i rang byung phyogs gang du yang ma lhung ba yin la /
NK131(do)001:1975: de la gzhi ka dag dang ye grol ces pa
NK131(do)001:1976: rgyal ba kun tu bzang po gzhi de nyid kyi
NK131(do)001:1977: thog tu rang grol ba la zer ba yin gyi
NK131(do)001:1978: / kun gzhi nyid ka dag dang ye grol du 'dod pa ma yin no //
NK131(do)001:1979: de'i phyir ka nas dag pa zhes bya ba gdod
NK131(do)001:1980: ma nas 'khrul ma myong ba'i dag pa de la
NK131(do)001:1981: zer la / kun tu bzang po zhes pa'i sgra
NK131(do)001:1982: don ni dus kun tu 'khrul pas nam yang gos
NK131(do)001:1983: ma myong ba de'i phyir bzang po zhes bya ba
NK131(do)001:1984: zer la / / 'di'i lugs la 'chad pa yin
NK131(do)001:1985: zhing ye grol zhes pa yang de dang don gcig
NK131(do)001:1986: pa yin pas na gzhan du mi bsam mo //
NK131(do)001:1987: de'i phyir 'dir gzhi ka dag dang ye grol zhes
NK131(do)001:1988: gsungs pa grol gzhi la ngos 'dzin pa yin gyi
NK131(do)001:1989: kun gzhi la 'dod pa ma yin no //
NK131(do)001:1991: grol gzhi rig pa yin pa de'i phyir /
NK131(do)001:1992: kun gzhi dang ka dag gnyis gcig dang tha dad gang yang ma yin no //
NK131(do)001:1993: de ltar yang lang+kara gshegs pa las /
NK131(do)001:1994: blo gros chen po 'di lta ste dper na /
NK131(do)001:1996: 'jim pa'i gong bu ni gcig pa yang ma yin
NK131(do)001:1997: tha dad pa yang ma yin pa dang ji ltar
NK131(do)001:1999: blo gros chen po ci ste 'jim pa'i gong bu
NK131(do)001:2000: 'jim pa'i rdul phra rab dang tha dad pa zhig
NK131(do)001:2001: yin na ni de dag las brtsams pa ma yin
NK131(do)001:2002: par 'gyur na / de ni 'jim pa'i rdul phra
NK131(do)001:2003: rab de dag las brtsams pas na de'i phyir tha
NK131(do)001:2005: de ste tha dad pa ma yin na ni 'jim
NK131(do)001:2006: pa'i gong bu dang rdul phra rab tu bye brag
NK131(do)001:2008: de bzhin du blo gros chen po 'jug pa'i rnam
NK131(do)001:2009: par shes pa rnams kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pa'i
NK131(do)001:2010: rigs kyi mtshan nyid dang gal te tha dad pa
NK131(do)001:2011: yin na ni kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pa'i rgyu
NK131(do)001:2013: de ste tha dad pa ma yin na ni 'jug
NK131(do)001:2014: pa'i rnam par shes pa 'gag na kun gzhi'i rnam
NK131(do)001:2015: par shes pa yang 'gag par 'gyur na /
NK131(do)001:2016: de ltar bdag gi rigs kyi mtshan nyid 'gag par yang mi 'gyur te /
NK131(do)001:2017: de'i phyir blo gros chen mo rnam par shes pa
NK131(do)001:2018: rnams kyi rang gi rigs kyi mtshan nyid 'gag par
NK131(do)001:2019: mi 'gyur gyi las kyi mtshan nyid ni 'gag go
NK131(do)001:2020: // zhes khams las byas pa'i rdzas bum la kham
NK131(do)001:2021: sa'i rigs yod kyang de khams nyid ma yin te
NK131(do)001:2022: // / gal te yin na 'di ni kham sa
NK131(do)001:2023: 'o 'di ni bum pa'o zhes phyed par mi 'gyur
NK131(do)001:2024: // / la / rdza bum la kham sa'i rigs
NK131(do)001:2025: med na de la rigs gzhan ci yang med pa
NK131(do)001:2027: de bzhin du chab ram chu'i rigs can yin kyang
NK131(do)001:2028: chu nyid ma yin te chab rom bzhu ba na
NK131(do)001:2031: sems dang rig pa rnam pa gnyis //
NK131(do)001:2032: gcig dang tha dad ma yin la //
NK131(do)001:2033: dbye na rab tu dka' ba'i chos //
NK131(do)001:2035: kun tu bzang po gzhi thog nas grol kyang gzhi
NK131(do)001:2036: ma yin pas kun gzhi phyogs su lhung ba med
NK131(do)001:2037: cing gang dang ma 'dres pa so so rang rig
NK131(do)001:2038: pa'i lhan cig skyes pa dang kun tu btags pa'i
NK131(do)001:2039: ma rigs pa gnyis ka las grol ba yin pas
NK131(do)001:2040: na gzhi las gzhan du yang ma yin la /
NK131(do)001:2041: gzhi nyid kyang ma yin no //
NK131(do)001:2043: kun tu bzang po nga nyid kyang //
NK131(do)001:2044: rgyu rkyen med pa gzhi yi don //
NK131(do)001:2045: de nyid gzhi la rang byung rig /
NK131(do)001:2046: phyi nang sgro skur skyon ma btags //
NK131(do)001:2047: dran med mun pa'i dri ma gos //
NK131(do)001:2048: de phyir rang snang skyon ma gos //
NK131(do)001:2049: rang rig so la gnas pa la //
NK131(do)001:2050: srid gsum 'jigs kyang sngangs skrag med //
NK131(do)001:2051: rtogs med shes pa rang byung la //
NK131(do)001:2052: gdos pa'i gzugs dang kha dog med //
NK131(do)001:2053: rig pa gsal cha ma 'gag pa //
NK131(do)001:2054: ngo bo gcig la ye shes lnga //
NK131(do)001:2056: ka dag dang kun gzhi la snga phyi med de
NK131(do)001:2057: lhan cig skyes pa yin pas na bya dang sgo
NK131(do)001:2059: bya med na sgo nga mi 'byung zhing /
NK131(do)001:2060: sgo nga med na bya mi 'byung bas na rang bzhin gyi lhan cig skyes pa yin no //
NK131(do)001:2062: dpal mgon 'phags pa klu sgrub kyis /
NK131(do)001:2063: kun gzhi kun gyi gzhi yin te //
NK131(do)001:2064: mya ngan 'das pa'i gzhi ma'ang yin //
NK131(do)001:2066: kun gzhi de nyid rang thog tu rig pa la ni yang dag pa'i sangs rgyas zhes 'dod la /
NK131(do)001:2067: ma rig par 'khrul pa'i dbang du song ba na sems can zhes 'dod pas na /
NK131(do)001:2068: bon gyi gzhung ltar dang po me med stong pa
NK131(do)001:2069: de la ming ka dag tu btags nas des slar
NK131(do)001:2070: 'khrul snang gi 'khor ba'i gzhi byed pa ltar du
NK131(do)001:2072: yang thod rgal dang lhun grub 'od gsal gyi snang
NK131(do)001:2073: ba zhes zab zab mo zhig yin par rlom ste
NK131(do)001:2076: mig la tshos ma bkab pa'i mthong snang dang /
NK131(do)001:2077: rna ba bkag pa'i sgra dang /
NK131(do)001:2079: 'bag chas la sogs ngo sprod cig yod 'dug pa /
NK131(do)001:2080: de dag gi skabs zhig na gsal ba'i rig pa
NK131(do)001:2081: rdo rje lu gu brgyud du grags pa de chos
NK131(do)001:2082: nyid kyi mngon sum yin nam /
NK131(do)001:2083: nyams snang gi mngon sum yin nam /
NK131(do)001:2085: chos nyid kyi mngon sum yin na /
NK131(do)001:2086: chos nyid kyi spyod yul yin phyir rang snang ye
NK131(do)001:2087: shes kyi rol par ngang gi gsal ba las 'du
NK131(do)001:2088: byed kyi rkyen sna tshogs mi dgos la /
NK131(do)001:2089: dbang po dang dbang shes kyi mthong bya'i yul ma yin /
NK131(do)001:2090: nyams kyi mngon sum yin na /
NK131(do)001:2091: du nyams ni bsgom pa la ltos te lam rtags kyi ngor gsal ba zhig yin la /
NK131(do)001:2092: 'di ni de yang ma yin te ma bsgoms kyang rkyen sna tshogs dus na gsal /
NK131(do)001:2093: dbang po'i mngon sum yin na chos nyid mngon sum zhes ming btags su mi rung la /
NK131(do)001:2094: rung na'ang dbang po'i yul du dngos snang bas chos nyid de ni gad mo'i gnas /
NK131(do)001:2095: yang rkyen tshogs pa las byung ba'i kha dog de dag /
NK131(do)001:2096: rang gi snying nang na sems nyid 'od lnga'i rnam
NK131(do)001:2097: par bzhugs pa'i rtsal mdangs phyir shar ba'i rnam pa
NK131(do)001:2098: mthong ba yin / zhes zer nas nyi zer sogs la lta bar byed /
NK131(do)001:2099: snying nang na rang la yod pa'i rtsal yod na
NK131(do)001:2100: nyi zer sogs la ma ltos par rtsol med gsal
NK131(do)001:2102: rkyen gyi bskul dgos zer na /
NK131(do)001:2103: dper na 'char gzhi snying nang na 'od lnga'i rnam par can gyi sems gcig ste /
NK131(do)001:2104: shar ba nyi zer gyi ngog na lu gu brgyud
NK131(do)001:2105: kyi rnam pa'i sems gcig /'dzin pa'i lu gu brgyud
NK131(do)001:2106: mig shes kyi lta ba'i sems gcig ste gsum yod
NK131(do)001:2107: par 'gyur la / de ltar 'dod la na sangs
NK131(do)001:2108: rgyas pa las lkog tu gyur pa'i grub mtha' zhig
NK131(do)001:2109: par 'gyur la / snang ngo // snying nang na
NK131(do)001:2110: sems nyid 'od lnga'i rnam par 'dzin pa 'di dang
NK131(do)001:2111: par 'gyur la / snang ngo // / rtag lta
NK131(do)001:2112: ba bdag lta ba bzang ba po byed pa po
NK131(do)001:2113: rang dbang can gyi sems zhig rnam pa snying nang
NK131(do)001:2114: na 'od che ste sgo nga tsam /
NK131(do)001:2115: chung ste yungs 'bru tsam zhig yod par 'dzin pa ni khyad par cung zad kyang ma mchis /
NK131(do)001:2116: khyad yod na de'i sgrub byed rnam dag kyang smra bar mdzod cig /
NK131(do)001:2117: yang 'od de snying nang na yod nges yin na yang rtsal phyir mthong ba'i nges pa med do //
NK131(do)001:2118: 'od de'i rten gyi snying dang nang khrol dngos su
NK131(do)001:2119: yod nges yin kyang de dag las 'di yin dngos
NK131(do)001:2121: mthong ba'i zer thag sogs de dag mngon sum lta
NK131(do)001:2122: ba na sems 'dzin gyi rten du byas te mnyam
NK131(do)001:2123: bzhag gi lta ba skyong rgyu yin na skyon cher
NK131(do)001:2124: med do // de bas kyang yul rkyen cir snang gi steng du skyong ba ches gnad zab la /
NK131(do)001:2125: zer de mthong ba dang ngan skug gi phung po
NK131(do)001:2126: mthong ba gnyis mnyam bzhag gi lta ba skyong tshul
NK131(do)001:2128: ma shes na 'ching bas rgyur mtshungs so //
NK131(do)001:2129: des na lhun grub mngon sum gyi snang ba la
NK131(do)001:2130: zab gnad ci mchis zhes dri na 'di la rnam
NK131(do)001:2131: dag gi gtan tshig ci smra /
NK131(do)001:2132: yang thig le thig bran gyi snang ba 'di dag
NK131(do)001:2133: longs sku'i zhing khams yin pas zhing khams mthong ba'o
NK131(do)001:2134: zhes khyed kyi gzhung lugs na bshad 'dug pa /
NK131(do)001:2135: zhing khams mi zad pa yin nam ma yin /
NK131(do)001:2136: ma yin na zhing khams bshad pa don med par 'gyur la /
NK131(do)001:2137: yin par ni rgyu mtshan gnyis kyi mi 'thad de /
NK131(do)001:2138: longs sku'i zhing khams lta ba la dbang bas gang
NK131(do)001:2139: zag de sa drug gi rtogs pa yod pa cig
NK131(do)001:2141: khyed kyi zhing khams de mthong ba la ni dang
NK131(do)001:2142: po'i bden pa mthong ba tsam yang mi dgos te
NK131(do)001:2143: / gang zag so skye zhig la bstan pas de
NK131(do)001:2144: ma thag des mthong ba'i phyir zhing khams mthong ba'i
NK131(do)001:2146: longs sku'i zhing khams mtshan nyid pa yin na rgyud
NK131(do)001:2147: tshod mthor song ba bzhin zhing khams rgya cher mthong
NK131(do)001:2148: bas mthar rab bkram chen po gcig dang grangs med
NK131(do)001:2149: sogs mthong bar bshad pa la /
NK131(do)001:2150: khyed rgyud mtho shes su byed pa'i chos nyid zad
NK131(do)001:2151: par zhing khams kyi snang ba ba thag bsdus pa
NK131(do)001:2152: ltar bsdus pa'i mthar mi mthong bar bshad pas /
NK131(do)001:2153: des na lam gyi mthong snang yin gyi zhing khams
NK131(do)001:2154: ma yin pas zhing khams rang gi ngo ma dag
NK131(do)001:2155: pas / zhes lung rigs kyi dngos su gsal na 'di la ci ste /
NK131(do)001:2156: yang nged kyi chos nyid mngon sum dang gzhan nas
NK131(do)001:2157: bshad pa'i du sogs kyi rtags mtshungs te skyon med
NK131(do)001:2158: do snyam na / du sogs mnyam bzhag gi brtan pa'i nyams snang la mig mdangs btsums med pa /
NK131(do)001:2161: rig pa lu gu brgyud mig btsums na mi gsal /
NK131(do)001:2162: nyi ma med na mi gsal /
NK131(do)001:2163: yul rkyen sna tshogs med na mi gsal ba dang /
NK131(do)001:2164: de dag gang nas kyang mi mtshungs shing /
NK131(do)001:2165: mtshungs kyang du sogs kyi rtags med nas du ba
NK131(do)001:2166: 'dren pa lta bu'i lam rtags kyi rnam pa tsam
NK131(do)001:2167: las / de la ting nge 'dzin mchog tu yang mi 'dzin /
NK131(do)001:2168: nyams kyi shun pa yin pas dor nas grol bar thob par bzhed pa dang /
NK131(do)001:2169: chos nyid mngon sum dag pa'i zhing khams yin pa'i
NK131(do)001:2170: mthong bas grol bar 'dod la ting nge 'dzin ni
NK131(do)001:2171: mchog tu 'dzin pa gnyis skyil po mi mtshungs so
NK131(do)001:2172: // des na 'di dag gi bon chos rnams na 'od gsal lta ba'i gdams pa mang zhig dang /
NK131(do)001:2173: rang lus 'od la phar zhugs na lhag med g.yung drung gi sku thob la /
NK131(do)001:2174: 'od rang lus la tshur zhugs nas lhag bcas g.yung
NK131(do)001:2175: drung drug gi sku thob par bzhed pa'i lung snang
NK131(do)001:2176: ba la khyad cung zad kyang ma mchis so //
NK131(do)001:2177: zhes gleng na rnam dag gi khyad par bye ba smra rgyu ci yod /
NK131(do)001:2178: ces gsungs la brjod par bya ste /
NK131(do)001:2179: dpe la sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa'i snying po stong nyid snying rjes yin te /
NK131(do)001:2181: gang zhig phyogs nyams de ni ma nyams pa 'gyur ro //
NK131(do)001:2182: de gang zhe na gang zhig stong nyid snying rje gnyis su med par smra ba po ste /
NK131(do)001:2183: 'dir snying rje dmigs pa med cing rnam par rtog pa dang bral ba dang /
NK131(do)001:2184: stong pa nyid rnam pa thams cad kyi mchog dang
NK131(do)001:2185: ldan pa dus gsum yongs su shes pa'i slad du
NK131(do)001:2187: zhes pa ni sangs rgyas pa'i grub pa'i mtha' nges pa /
NK131(do)001:2188: zhes gsungs pa'i stong nyid snying rje dbyer med pa de yang /
NK131(do)001:2189: khang stong mi'i stong pa nyid lta bu nyi tshe ba'i stong pa nyid dang /
NK131(do)001:2190: cang med du 'dod pa chad lta'i stong pa nyid dang /
NK131(do)001:2191: bem po'i stong pa nyid dang /
NK131(do)001:2192: dngos med kyi stong pa nyid dang /
NK131(do)001:2194: la sogs par rnam par dpyad pa thams cad las 'das pa /
NK131(do)001:2195: bde bar gshegs pa rnams kyi yang dag pa'i ye
NK131(do)001:2196: shes chen po de ni 'od gsal rnam pa thams
NK131(do)001:2197: cad kyi mchog dang ldan pa'i stong pa nyid kyi
NK131(do)001:2199: 'jam pa'i dbyangs kyi rang gi lta bas 'dod pa mdor bstan pa las /
NK131(do)001:2200: phung po rnam dpyod stong pa rnams //
NK131(do)001:2201: chu shing ji bzhin snying po med //
NK131(do)001:2202: rnam pa thams cad mchog ldan pa'i //
NK131(do)001:2203: stong nyid de ltar 'gyur ma yin //
NK131(do)001:2204: skyes pa med pa 'gag med pa //
NK131(do)001:2205: shes bya gang zhig 'dir mthong ba //
NK131(do)001:2206: stong pa'i dngos po stong pa nyid //
NK131(do)001:2207: phung po rnams rnam dpyad pa min //
NK131(do)001:2208: zhes gsungs shing de lta bu'i 'od gsal de ci lta bu zhe na /
NK131(do)001:2210: bcom ldan 'das 'od gsal zhes bgyi ba ji ltar lags /
NK131(do)001:2212: bcom ldan 'das kyi bka' rtsal pa /
NK131(do)001:2213: 'od gsal ni nam mkha'i dbyings su gnas pa'i thig le ste /
NK131(do)001:2214: des na phyag rgya chen po mnyes par 'gyur ba yin no //
NK131(do)001:2216: gsang ba 'dus pa'i rim lnga las /
NK131(do)001:2217: rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas ma ltos pa'i //
NK131(do)001:2218: phyag rgya chen po rtog par ni //
NK131(do)001:2220: nam mkha'i 'ja' tshon dag dang mtshungs //
NK131(do)001:2223: phyag rgya chen po'i gzugs 'chang ba //
NK131(do)001:2224: sgyu ma 'ja' tshon lta bu ru //
NK131(do)001:2225: rang dang gzhan gyi rgyud sbyong ba //
NK131(do)001:2226: yang dag gsal ba zhes bshad do //
NK131(do)001:2227: zhes gsungs pa'i 'od gsal de ni mtshan ma can ltar mthong ba dang /
NK131(do)001:2229: gang rnams kyi blo rten dang bral //
NK131(do)001:2230: yod dang med las rnam par 'das //
NK131(do)001:2231: zab mo dmigs med de rnams kyi //
NK131(do)001:2232: mtshan ma'i don ni rnam par sgom //
NK131(do)001:2235: de kho na nyid kyi 'bras bu'i snga ltas su gyur pa'i phyir mtshan ma'o //
NK131(do)001:2237: 'o na de rnams dngos po ci zhig yin snyam na /
NK131(do)001:2238: sems kyi snang ba tsam ste rang gi yid las
NK131(do)001:2239: skyes pa me long gi gzugs brnyan lta bu nyid
NK131(do)001:2240: / ces gsungs pa'i phyir sems kyi snang ba tsam yin gyi /
NK131(do)001:2241: de las gzhan pa'i dngos po'i chos ni ci yang ma yin no //
NK131(do)001:2242: sems kyang rtog pa dang bral zhing ma 'khrul bas /
NK131(do)001:2244: de'i snang ba tsam yin pas /
NK131(do)001:2245: bag chags kyis bskyed pas rnam par rtog pa'i snang ba yang ma yin la /
NK131(do)001:2246: mig skyon can gyi zla ba gnyis su snang ba
NK131(do)001:2247: sogs dbang po bslad pa'i shes pa'i snang ba yang
NK131(do)001:2248: ma yin zhing / yid kyi shes pa'i bslad pa
NK131(do)001:2249: snang ba yang ma yin dbang po lnga'i rnam par
NK131(do)001:2250: shes pa'i snang ba yang ma yin te /
NK131(do)001:2251: don gyi bzhag pa ma yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK131(do)001:2252: ma bslad pa'i yid kyi shes pa'i snang ba ni yin te /
NK131(do)001:2253: slob dpon ar+ya de wa yid kyi dbang po snang ba gsum la bzhed pas so //
NK131(do)001:2254: yang slob dpon 'gro bzang snying po'i de kho na nyid kyi man ngag gi 'grel bar /
NK131(do)001:2255: 'di ci dngos po ngo bo nyid yin nam 'o na de ma yin zhe na /
NK131(do)001:2256: yi ge med ces bya ba smos te /
NK131(do)001:2257: dngos po med ces ngo bo nyid kun gzhi rnam
NK131(do)001:2258: par shes pas rang bzhin mkha' khyab par snang ngo
NK131(do)001:2259: // de lta bu'i mgon po bsgom pa las ye shes skye bar 'gyur ro //
NK131(do)001:2261: 'di ni don gyi kun gzhi'i snang ba zhes pa de yin gyi /
NK131(do)001:2262: rnam shes tshogs brgyad kyi ya gyal kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pa zhes pa de ma yin te /
NK131(do)001:2263: rje 'bri gung bas phyag chen rtsal du bton te
NK131(do)001:2264: bsgom pa sa stong gzugs mtha' yas pa shar pa
NK131(do)001:2265: la kun gzhi mthong ba yin zhes bzhed par mdzod
NK131(do)001:2266: / 'di dag 'khrul pa'i snang bar yang gsungs pa med kyi /
NK131(do)001:2267: mngon sum gyi snang ba kho na yin gyi /
NK131(do)001:2268: rtag tsam zhig kyang ma yin gyi /
NK131(do)001:2269: zung du 'jug pa zhes rab tu basngagasa pa de'i
NK131(do)001:2270: ngo bo nyid du gyur nas rgyal bas sku chen
NK131(do)001:2273: mtho ris sa steng sa 'og rnams //
NK131(do)001:2274: skad cig las ni sku gcig 'gyur //
NK131(do)001:2276: sngags kyi theg pa las gsar bar gsungs pa'i don gyi gtso bo yang 'di yin pas /
NK131(do)001:2277: dad pa dang shes rab med pa'i gang zag la gtam bya bar daka'o //
NK131(do)001:2278: da ni mngon sum zhes pa'i don brjod par bya ste /
NK131(do)001:2279: 'dir tshad ma dang bral ba'i lam du zhugs pas ni gol zhing /
NK131(do)001:2281: tshad ma gtan la dbab par bya ba ste /
NK131(do)001:2282: tshad ma de yang mngon dang rjes su dpag pa
NK131(do)001:2283: gnyis su nges par slob dpon chos kyi grags pas
NK131(do)001:2284: bshad do // gsang ba'i theg pa 'dir yang tshad ma gnyis kho na ste /
NK131(do)001:2285: dpal dus kyi 'khor lo'i sgrub thabs kyi le'ura /
NK131(do)001:2286: lha yi dmigs pa mngon sum dang ni rjes su dpag pa gnyis su 'gyur ba ste /
NK131(do)001:2287: mngon sum dag ni de nyid sbyor bar mkha' la
NK131(do)001:2288: skar ma bzhin du du ma longs spyod rdzogs pas
NK131(do)001:2289: sku / mngon sum med na rjes su dpag pa
NK131(do)001:2290: shi bas lus bzhin de nyid min pa yis ni
NK131(do)001:2291: sku / brtags pa gang / de nas ri mo
NK131(do)001:2292: la sogs lta bya yongs su ma smin blo can
NK131(do)001:2293: rnal 'byor rnams kyi bsgom pa'i don /
NK131(do)001:2295: de la mngon sum yang tha mal ba'i dbang po'i
NK131(do)001:2296: mngon sum nas nyan thos dang rang sangs rgyas kyi
NK131(do)001:2297: bar gyi mngon sum gyis ni shes pa ma yin
NK131(do)001:2298: pa'i / mngon sum khyad par can dag gi de
NK131(do)001:2299: kho na nyid bsgom pa'i mngon sum gyi gtan la
NK131(do)001:2301: de yang chos rnams la 'khrul pa'i shes pa sna tshogs kyi bslad pa'i snang ba ma yin pa /
NK131(do)001:2302: sems can nas sangs rgyas kyi sa'i bar du rigs
NK131(do)001:2303: mi 'gyur bar gnas pa'i kho na nyid bcas bya
NK131(do)001:2305: chos rnams gzugs la sogs pa nas //
NK131(do)001:2306: kun mkhyen bar gyi rang bzhin ni //
NK131(do)001:2307: nam mkha'i dkyil ltar rnam dag pa //
NK131(do)001:2308: zab gsal gnyis med ye shes te //
NK131(do)001:2309: de ni dngos med sgom dngos med //
NK131(do)001:2310: dngos po thams cad dang bral la //
NK131(do)001:2311: khams dang skye mched kyis ma yin //
NK131(do)001:2312: rang bzhin gyi ni 'od gsal ba //
NK131(do)001:2313: gdod nas dag pa nam mkha' bzhin //
NK131(do)001:2314: med pas chos rnams mtshan nyid spangs //
NK131(do)001:2315: chos dang chos nyid yang med de //
NK131(do)001:2316: dngos po med pa mkha' dang mtshungs //
NK131(do)001:2317: tshig dang yi ge kun las grol //
NK131(do)001:2318: de ni dus dang phyogs rnams dang //
NK131(do)001:2319: chos rnams kun gyi ngo bor song //
NK131(do)001:2320: lus ma yin te ngag dang ni //
NK131(do)001:2321: yid kyang ma yin 'dod khams dang //
NK131(do)001:2322: gzugs dang gzugs med khams ma yin //
NK131(do)001:2323: 'byung chen bzhi yang ma yin te //
NK131(do)001:2324: de bas de nyid gang na yang //
NK131(do)001:2325: mi gnas pas na mnyam pa nyid //
NK131(do)001:2327: chos rnams kun gyi chos nyid chog /
NK131(do)001:2328: thabs kyi sgrub par bya ba'i dngos //
NK131(do)001:2329: brtags pa kun las rab dbyin pa //
NK131(do)001:2330: phun sum tshogs rgyud dpag dka' ba //
NK131(do)001:2331: phyag rgya chen po rab snang ba'i //
NK131(do)001:2332: zer gyi rang bzhin smin byed pa //
NK131(do)001:2333: gnyis su med pa'i rang bzhin mchog /
NK131(do)001:2334: rdo rje 'dzin pa chen pos kyang //
NK131(do)001:2335: brjod du med pa'i sku chen po //
NK131(do)001:2336: zhes pa la sogs pas bstan pa ni nang gi
NK131(do)001:2337: de kho na nyid kyi mthong ba'i mngon sum zhes
NK131(do)001:2338: bya ste zhing / rdo rje snying po'i 'grel pa la /
NK131(do)001:2342: rang rig pa'i mngon sum ste /
NK131(do)001:2346: nyams su myong ba'i mtshan nyid can no //
NK131(do)001:2347: zhes gsungs pas na de la mngon sum gyi ngo bo gang yin zhe na /
NK131(do)001:2348: de kho na nyid stong nyid snying rje'i rnal 'byor
NK131(do)001:2349: bsgom pas sha la sogs mig lngas rnam pa thams
NK131(do)001:2350: cad pa'i gzugs nam mkha' la skar ma bzhin du
NK131(do)001:2351: gsal bar mthong shes pa rtog pa dang bral zhing
NK131(do)001:2352: ma 'khrul ba de la bya ste /
NK131(do)001:2354: 'dir nam mkha' la dngos po bsgom bya ni rmi
NK131(do)001:2355: lam lta bus te rdul phra rab kyi chos nyid
NK131(do)001:2356: las 'das pa'o // de yongs shes pa ni dngos po med pa bsgom par bya ste /
NK131(do)001:2357: rnam par rtog pa dang bral ba'i sems kyi snang brnyan mthong ba'o //
NK131(do)001:2358: rtog pa dang bral zhing ma 'khrul ba ni mngon sum zhes brjod par bya'o //
NK131(do)001:2360: de lta bu thabs gang gis mthong na /
NK131(do)001:2361: bde mchog ri gi a ra li'i rgyud las /
NK131(do)001:2362: dgon pa dben pa'i gnas su ni //
NK131(do)001:2363: gnyis gnyis thams cad rnam par spangs //
NK131(do)001:2364: mig dag steng du bzlog nas ni //
NK131(do)001:2365: smin pa'i dbus su sems byas na //
NK131(do)001:2366: mi zad mun pa'i gzugs su ni //
NK131(do)001:2367: sgrub pos dngos por mthong bar 'gyur //
NK131(do)001:2369: tshul ji ltar mthong ba yang /
NK131(do)001:2371: dang po mun pa mthong bar 'gyur //
NK131(do)001:2372: gnyis pa dkar dang du ma mtshungs //
NK131(do)001:2373: gsum pa me khyer rnam par lta //
NK131(do)001:2374: bzhi pa ya bas me tog bzhin //
NK131(do)001:2375: lnga pa sprin med ye shes ni //
NK131(do)001:2376: rang bzhin yang dag rig pa yang //
NK131(do)001:2377: rtag tu goms pa'i rnal 'byor gyi //
NK131(do)001:2378: rtse gcig sems kyi rig pa 'gyur //
NK131(do)001:2379: zhes gsungs shing rdo rje gur las /
NK131(do)001:2380: dang po sprin dang 'dra bar snang //
NK131(do)001:2381: gnyis pa du ba 'dra ba yin //
NK131(do)001:2382: gsum pa me khyer 'dra ba ste //
NK131(do)001:2383: bzhi pa mar me cher 'bar ba //
NK131(do)001:2384: lnga pa rtag tu snang ba ni //
NK131(do)001:2385: sprin pa nam mkha' lta bu'o //
NK131(do)001:2387: bde mchog mkha' 'gro rgyal po'i rgyud du gsungs shing /
NK131(do)001:2389: dang po smig rgyu 'dra ba ste //
NK131(do)001:2390: gnyis pa du ba 'dra ba yin //
NK131(do)001:2391: gsum pa me khyer rnam pa ste //
NK131(do)001:2392: bzhi pa mar me 'bar ba nyid //
NK131(do)001:2393: lnga pa sprin med nam mkha' 'dra //
NK131(do)001:2395: slob dpon ar+ya de bas spyod bsdus su /
NK131(do)001:2396: dang po smig rgyu lta bu la /
NK131(do)001:2397: 'od zer lnga'i tshogs dang ldan par mthong ngo //
NK131(do)001:2399: snang ba ste zla ba'i 'od zer lta bu'o //
NK131(do)001:2400: gsum pa ni snang ba mched pa ste nyi ma'i 'od zer lta bu'o //
NK131(do)001:2401: bzhi pa ni snang ba thob pa ste mun pa lta bu'o //
NK131(do)001:2402: de nas mun pa dang bral bas skad cig la
NK131(do)001:2403: 'od gsal ba ste shin tu gsal ba rtag tu
NK131(do)001:2405: don dam pa'i bden pa'i rang gi mtshan nyid ye shes kyi mig gi mthong ngo //
NK131(do)001:2406: zhes gsungs pa'i dang po smig rgyu lta bu la
NK131(do)001:2407: 'od zer lnga'i tshogs dang ldan par mthong bas gsungs
NK131(do)001:2408: pa dang / rdzogs chen nas thog mar dbyings rnam
NK131(do)001:2409: par dag pa'i sgron ma dar mthing kha'i mdog lta
NK131(do)001:2410: bu'am rma bya'i mdongs lta bu 'char bar gsungs pa
NK131(do)001:2412: de las gzhan gsungs pa rnams ni /
NK131(do)001:2413: rig pa rdo rje lu gu rgyud dang /
NK131(do)001:2416: de la sogs 'char sgo sna tshogs pa du ma dang /
NK131(do)001:2417: thig ler gsum sbrel nas nyi shu rtsa lnga la
NK131(do)001:2418: sogs pa'i bar du snang ba ni chos nyid mngon
NK131(do)001:2419: sum gyi snang ba zhes pa yin no //
NK131(do)001:2420: de yang sngar gsungs pa rnams kyi steng du nyi
NK131(do)001:2421: ma'i rtag lnga bsnan pas bcu po rdzogs pa phan
NK131(do)001:2423: rtags bcu ni dbang mdor bstan las /
NK131(do)001:2424: du ba smig rgyu mkha' snang dang //
NK131(do)001:2425: sgron me 'bar dang zla nyi ma //
NK131(do)001:2426: mun can cha dang thig le che //
NK131(do)001:2427: sna tshogs gzugs can 'od gsal ba //
NK131(do)001:2429: sna tshogs gzugs can 'od gsal ba ni /
NK131(do)001:2430: nyams gang 'phel gyi snang ba yin te /
NK131(do)001:2431: 'od lnga ma 'dres snam bu lta bu dang /
NK131(do)001:2434: mig mang ris dang za 'og dang /
NK131(do)001:2435: re lde lta bur snang ba tshun chad yin no //
NK131(do)001:2436: de nas 'od kyi snang srid thams cad la khyab pa ma lta kyang gsal la /
NK131(do)001:2437: thig le'i nang du sangs rgyas kyi sku zhi ba
NK131(do)001:2438: dang khro bo gang yang nges pa med pa sna
NK131(do)001:2439: tshogs 'char ba phyin chad ni rig pa tshad la
NK131(do)001:2440: pheb pa'i snang ba yin la /
NK131(do)001:2441: dpal dus kyi 'khor lo ni nam mkhar kun nas
NK131(do)001:2442: zhes pa'i sems dang mig ni mi 'dzum rdo rje'i
NK131(do)001:2443: lam du rab tu zhugs pa yi /
NK131(do)001:2444: stong pa las ni du ba smig rgyu rab gsal
NK131(do)001:2445: dri ma med pa'i mkha' snang nyid dang mar me
NK131(do)001:2446: dang / 'bar ba dang ni zla ba nyi ma
NK131(do)001:2447: rdo rje dang mchog gi cha dang thig le mthong
NK131(do)001:2448: dang / bar 'gyur / de'i dbus su sangs rgyas
NK131(do)001:2449: gzugs ni yul dang rnam par bral ba du ma
NK131(do)001:2452: nam mkha' chu 'dzin bral ba'i dbus su rnal 'byor gyi bgrod pa'i mig gi lta bya ste /
NK131(do)001:2453: re 'ga' nag po dri med 'od zer 'phro ba
NK131(do)001:2454: dus kyi rtsa la mthong bar gyur gyi bar du'o
NK131(do)001:2457: rtag bcu rdzogs par gyur pa dang //
NK131(do)001:2458: thig le chen po'i snang ba 'byung //
NK131(do)001:2459: sna tshogs theg le chen po la //
NK131(do)001:2460: re kha nag po'i ri mo 'byung //
NK131(do)001:2461: de nang 'gro drug la sogs dang //
NK131(do)001:2462: shin tu phra bas sprul sku dang //
NK131(do)001:2463: longs sku du ma mthong 'gyur ba //
NK131(do)001:2464: sna tshogs gzugs na 'od gsal yin //
NK131(do)001:2465: de la sems ni thim pa na //
NK131(do)001:2466: ting 'dzin yan lag mthar phyin pa'o //
NK131(do)001:2467: zhes bshad pa'i don ni rdzogs chen nas chos nyid
NK131(do)001:2468: zab pa'i snang ba zhes gsungs pa dang khyad par
NK131(do)001:2469: med do // 'di dag ni don zhib tu 'chad rigs med kyi /
NK131(do)001:2470: ye shes mang por 'gro phyir bzhag la /
NK131(do)001:2471: bdag gis byas pa'i lam rim thar pa'i sgo gcig tu gsal lo //
NK131(do)001:2472: de dag ni chos nyid kyi mngon sum kyang yin te /
NK131(do)001:2473: ye gdod ma'i chos nyid ye shes kyi rang 'od
NK131(do)001:2474: du ye nas ngang gi gsal ba yin par sngar
NK131(do)001:2475: bshad pa'i lung de rnams kyi sgrubs zin no //
NK131(do)001:2476: dbang po'i yul du snang bas chos nyid de gad mo'i gnas shes gsung ba yang mi rigs te /
NK131(do)001:2477: 'dus pa stong chen po'i gdam yin chen mo rin po che tog las /
NK131(do)001:2478: shes rab za mo tshul bzhin rnam dag pas //
NK131(do)001:2479: ston pa'i rnal 'byor bla med rtag sgrub pa //
NK131(do)001:2480: rdo rje lta bu mig gnyis la mthong ba //
NK131(do)001:2481: ting nge 'dzin dang mnyam pa yod ma yin //
NK131(do)001:2482: de bas 'di ni rin chen mchog tu gsungs //
NK131(do)001:2483: zhes mig gi mthong bar gsungs la /
NK131(do)001:2485: rang yid mtshan ma mtha' dag bral ba yis //
NK131(do)001:2486: mig phyed gyen du lta ba dang bcas pas //
NK131(do)001:2487: gang tshe rlung ni dbu mar bus gyur pa //
NK131(do)001:2488: de tshe rdo rjes me dang du ba mtshungs //
NK131(do)001:2490: nyams kyi mngon sum kyang yin te /
NK131(do)001:2491: rnal 'byor bas lam bsgom pa'i nyams kyi snang ba yin pa'i phyir /
NK131(do)001:2492: bir+wa pas lam 'bras rdo rje'i tshig rkang las /
NK131(do)001:2493: rnal 'byor pa la ting 'dzin la nyams kyi snang ba zhes bshad pa de /
NK131(do)001:2494: dbang po'i mngon sum yin par snying tig rnam gnyis la sogs par bshad kyang /
NK131(do)001:2495: rgyang zhag chu'i sgron ma zhes 'char ba'i sgo mig yin pa la dgongs pa yin te /
NK131(do)001:2496: don du dbang po'i mngon sum ma yin te /
NK131(do)001:2497: sangs rgyas kyi ye shes lnga'i rang 'od du rang gsal ba de nyid /
NK131(do)001:2498: mig gi mthong bya mthong byed kyi yul las 'das pa'i phyir dang /
NK131(do)001:2499: mun khang du rang gi lag pa brkyangs pa mi mthong pa'i tshe na'ang mthong ba'i phyir dang /
NK131(do)001:2500: bar dor mig dang bral bas /
NK131(do)001:2501: dus na'ang mthong ba'i phyir te /
NK131(do)001:2503: rang gi mig gi mi mthong zhing //
NK131(do)001:2504: gzhan gyi mig gis kyang min pa //
NK131(do)001:2505: skye ba med pa mthong ba ni //
NK131(do)001:2506: gzhon nu mi yi bu ji bzhin //
NK131(do)001:2509: gang gi phyir bkab pa dang ma bkab pa'i mig gi rtogs pa de'i phyir gzugs ma yin zhing /
NK131(do)001:2510: gzugs las gzhan pa yang ma yin la /
NK131(do)001:2511: mig gi rtogs pa ni ma yin la /
NK131(do)001:2512: mig med pa rtogs pa yang ma yin no //
NK131(do)001:2513: zhes gsungs pa nyid kyi shes so //
NK131(do)001:2514: yang rdo rje snying po 'grel las gsungs pa ltar gyi mngon sum bzhi po'ang yin te /
NK131(do)001:2515: de'i tshul yang rdzogs pa'i rim pa'i rnal 'byor pas
NK131(do)001:2516: 'jug pa'i yul ni mi bshig pa'i thig le yin
NK131(do)001:2517: pas / de dbang po'i mngon sum mthong ba tsam zhig byas /
NK131(do)001:2518: de nas phyag rgya sgyu ma'i rjes su mthun pa
NK131(do)001:2519: yid dang nam mkha' la ni me long dag la
NK131(do)001:2520: gzugs brnyan bzhin / 'jig rten gsum po snang bar
NK131(do)001:2521: byed cing dri med klog dang mtshungs pa'i 'od zer
NK131(do)001:2524: yid kyi mngon sum mi shig pas thig le de'i
NK131(do)001:2525: nang du yid kyi gzugs brnyan mthong bas nges pa
NK131(do)001:2526: snyed / de nas rig pa tshad la phebs pa'i
NK131(do)001:2527: rnal 'byor gyi mngon sum gyi rang rig pa'i ye
NK131(do)001:2529: chos nyid zad pa'i skabs gzung 'dzin dang /
NK131(do)001:2530: bral bas rang rig pa'i mngon sum gyi 'jug pa'i
NK131(do)001:2531: yul mi bshig pas thig le gnyis su snang ba
NK131(do)001:2532: med pa'i tshul gyis nyams su myong ba yin no
NK131(do)001:2533: // de la tshos ma bkab pas mthong snang dang /
NK131(do)001:2535: nyi zer la rten pa dang /
NK131(do)001:2536: 'bag chas la sogs pa la rten nas ston pa ni /
NK131(do)001:2537: rig pa'i ye shes dngos ma yin te /
NK131(do)001:2538: 'di bas lugs la dpe don rtags gsum gyi ngo sprod ces 'byung bas na /
NK131(do)001:2539: dpe la rten nas don ngo sprad pas na mtshon
NK131(do)001:2540: byed dpe'i ye shes zhes bya ba yin gyi 'di
NK131(do)001:2541: dag mngon sum ye shes su khas mi len no
NK131(do)001:2542: // de lta bu'i ye shes rang rang gi snying
NK131(do)001:2543: nang na stong gsal 'od kyi rang bzhin du yod
NK131(do)001:2544: la de yang rtag lta ba 'dod rtag pa ba
NK131(do)001:2545: la bem po rtag par 'dod pa dang shes pa
NK131(do)001:2546: rtag par 'dod pa gnyis las dang po dbang phyug
NK131(do)001:2547: // gi gzhung las / smyug ma'i tshal na smyug ma skye //
NK131(do)001:2549: mi shi ba ni mi ru skye //
NK131(do)001:2550: zhes rtag pa mi 'gyur ba mi shi ba mi skye ba dang /
NK131(do)001:2551: sems can gcig shi na sems can spyi de la thim shing /
NK131(do)001:2552: sems can gcig skyes na sems rtag pa spyi de las chad pa yin nam zer /
NK131(do)001:2553: shes pa rtag par 'dod pa ni /
NK131(do)001:2554: sems de snying gi dkyil na che ba the bong tsam /
NK131(do)001:2557: dkar la mtsher ba snum la 'gril ba shes rig gi bdag nyid can /
NK131(do)001:2558: rtag pa gcig bu rang dbang can dus thams cad
NK131(do)001:2559: du mi 'gyur ba rjes su grub pa gcig snying
NK131(do)001:2561: phung po nyid mtshams sbyor ba dang //
NK131(do)001:2562: rtag pa the bong yungs 'bru tsam //
NK131(do)001:2563: bdag ces bya ba de yi len //
NK131(do)001:2564: nga ni rtag la blo ni 'gyur //
NK131(do)001:2565: zhes byed pa po des byas nas /
NK131(do)001:2566: da lta'i lus 'di mi rtag kyang sems rtag ste /
NK131(do)001:2567: rdza chag bye'u 'phur ba lta bu yin zer /
NK131(do)001:2568: lus che chung la sems che chung yod de /
NK131(do)001:2569: khang pa dang bum pa lta bu 'dod /
NK131(do)001:2571: pa ltar bdag tu lta ba ma yin te /
NK131(do)001:2573: lus la ye shes chen po gnas //
NK131(do)001:2574: gzhan du gang na'ang sangs rgyas med //
NK131(do)001:2575: mi shes mun pas sgribs pa rnams //
NK131(do)001:2576: lus las gzhan du sangs rgyas 'dod //
NK131(do)001:2579: snying gi nang son pad+ma ni //
NK131(do)001:2580: 'dab ma brgyad pa snying por bcas //
NK131(do)001:2581: de yi nang du son pa'i rtsa //
NK131(do)001:2582: mar me rang gi ngo bo can //
NK131(do)001:2583: chu shing gi ni me tog ltar //
NK131(do)001:2585: de'i nang na dpa' bo ni //
NK131(do)001:2586: yungs dkar gyi ni sbom phra tsam //
NK131(do)001:2588: rtsa yi mdzes spyi las byung ba'i //
NK131(do)001:2589: de ni rdul bral rab tu grags //
NK131(do)001:2590: dag pa shel gyi 'od dang mnyam //
NK131(do)001:2591: byang chub sems ni 'od gsal ba //
NK131(do)001:2592: ye shes lnga yi dngos de nyid //
NK131(do)001:2593: yungs kar gyi ni sbom phra tsam //
NK131(do)001:2596: mkhas pa rnams ni bstan bcos 'chad pa yi //
NK131(do)001:2597: lus la ye shes yod pa ma rtogs so //
NK131(do)001:2599: slob dpon rdo rje dril bu pas //
NK131(do)001:2600: rtag tu snying la gnas pa yi //
NK131(do)001:2601: thig le gcig la 'gyur ba med //
NK131(do)001:2602: de bsgom byed pa'i skye bo la //
NK131(do)001:2603: nges par ye shes skye bar 'gyur //
NK131(do)001:2605: gzhan yang rgyud dang bstan bcos rnams nas rgya cher bshad pa yin no //
NK131(do)001:2606: de la snying nang na 'char gzhi 'od kyi rnam pa'i sems dang /
NK131(do)001:2607: shar ba lu gu rgyud kyi rnam pa'i sems /
NK131(do)001:2608: 'dzin pa mig gi dbang shes kyi lu gu rgyud
NK131(do)001:2609: gsum gyi sems gsum yod par 'gyur gsung ba ni
NK131(do)001:2610: ma nges pa chen po ste /
NK131(do)001:2611: rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad kyi don spyi tsam
NK131(do)001:2612: yang blo yul du ma shar ba'i blun po dag
NK131(do)001:2613: gi tshig dang mtshungs par bsal /
NK131(do)001:2614: de lta na nyi ma dang nyi ma'i 'od zer
NK131(do)001:2615: gyi sgo nas nyi ma gnyis yod par 'gyur te
NK131(do)001:2616: / 'char gzhi nam mkhar gnas pa'i nyi ma gcig dang //
NK131(do)001:2617: shar ba 'od zer gyi tshul du gcig ste gnyis
NK131(do)001:2618: su mi 'gyur ram chos drug pa dag la yang
NK131(do)001:2620: snang ba sgyu mar bsgoms pa'i sgyu lus kyi sems gcig /
NK131(do)001:2621: thams cad kyi rmi lam du bsgoms pa rmi lam
NK131(do)001:2622: gyi sems gcig la sogs pa du mar 'gyur ro
NK131(do)001:2623: // de ltar ma lags de'i phyir /
NK131(do)001:2625: sems nyid lhan cig skyes pa chos kyi sku //
NK131(do)001:2626: snang ba lhan cig skyes pa chos sku'i'o //
NK131(do)001:2627: de phyir snang sems gnyis med lhan cig skyes //
NK131(do)001:2628: yid bzhin nor 'dra'i sems la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK131(do)001:2629: zhes gsungs pa ma yin nam /
NK131(do)001:2630: 'od snang de dag gi steng du mnyam bzhag gi
NK131(do)001:2631: lta ba mi skyong bar byis pa lha khang lta
NK131(do)001:2632: ba lta bu ni ma yin te /
NK131(do)001:2633: de'i tshul ni sbyor drug pa'i bsam gtan gyi yan lag dang /
NK131(do)001:2634: rdzogs chen pa'i thod rgal gyi khrid yig rnams su lta'o //
NK131(do)001:2636: ngan skyug gi phung po mthong ba mnyam bzhag gi
NK131(do)001:2637: skyong tshul shes na mnyam par gsung pa yang mi
NK131(do)001:2638: 'thad de / 'di ni nges pa'i don gyi rgyal
NK131(do)001:2639: ba'i dkyil 'khor yin pas mthong ba tsam gyi grol
NK131(do)001:2640: 'thad de / ba yin te / sangs rgyas rjes su dran pa las /
NK131(do)001:2641: 'di mthong ba la don yod pa /
NK131(do)001:2642: mkhas pa rnams kyi so so rang gi rig par bya ba /
NK131(do)001:2644: so sor sdud pa rtags bcu mthong bas bden pa'i tshig 'grub pa la sogs gsungs shing /
NK131(do)001:2645: ngan skyug gi phung po ni lta ba can la don du ma grub pa yin /
NK131(do)001:2646: mthong ba la de lta bu'i yon tan med pas ngan skyug nyid du zad do //
NK131(do)001:2647: chos nyid mngon sum gyi zab gnad ci zhes gsung ba yang /
NK131(do)001:2648: 'di ni grong khyer rgyun gcod kyi lta ba zhes bya ste /
NK131(do)001:2649: mngal gyi grong khyer rgyun gcod pa na phyis 'khor bar mi 'khyams te /
NK131(do)001:2650: mngon sum gnad 'di sus mthong ba //
NK131(do)001:2651: khams gsum ldog pa ma yin no //
NK131(do)001:2653: rgya gar gyi grub chen rnams kyang lam 'di'i sgo
NK131(do)001:2654: nas bgrod pa gcig pa sha stag yin te rang
NK131(do)001:2655: rang gi mgur rnams na gsal mod kyi /
NK131(do)001:2656: 'dir yi ges 'jigs pas bri bar ma nus la /
NK131(do)001:2659: rma byung nam mkha'i dkyil shar b+hu su ku //
NK131(do)001:2660: dpe med me tog rgyas so b+hu su ku //
NK131(do)001:2661: rin chen rin thang med pa'i me tog long //
NK131(do)001:2662: me tog 'di ni stong nyid dgon par skyes //
NK131(do)001:2663: me tog 'di ni kha dog sna tshogs can //
NK131(do)001:2666: snang ba thob pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK131(do)001:2667: gzhan du rtags ni shes bya ste //
NK131(do)001:2668: grub pa'i 'khrul ba med pa rnams //
NK131(do)001:2669: lam nag gi ni du ba bzhin //
NK131(do)001:2670: mig dag rengs par byed pa dang //
NK131(do)001:2671: mgo bo dud pa nyid dang ni //
NK131(do)001:2672: sems dang sems byung mi g.yo dang //
NK131(do)001:2673: stong nyid mthong ba'i stong ba nyid //
NK131(do)001:2676: gang tshe zla ba nya ba shar gyur pa //
NK131(do)001:2677: de tshe sems kyi rgyal po kun tu nyal //
NK131(do)001:2678: dga' dang snying rje'i da ma ru yi sgra //
NK131(do)001:2679: 'phags pa lha yi dmigs pa med par gsal //
NK131(do)001:2682: zab mo'i chos mthong nas ni lam ngan pa //
NK131(do)001:2683: mun pa'i lam la ci yang mthong ba med //
NK131(do)001:2684: gang tshe nam mkha'i rtse mor me tog rgyas //
NK131(do)001:2685: sh+aan+tisa smras pa de tshe 'khrul pa chad //
NK131(do)001:2687: lta zhing lta bas nam langs kyang //
NK131(do)001:2688: sh+aan+ti sgron mes lam tshol lo //
NK131(do)001:2691: me tog lnga byung de ru thim //
NK131(do)001:2692: dga' ba'i sems nyid nam mkhar 'byin //
NK131(do)001:2695: dri ma med pa'i nam mkha' gang la sprul pa'i mig phye la //
NK131(do)001:2696: thugs rje chen po rgyas pa brlan pa bsam pa'i rten za las //
NK131(do)001:2697: yod dang med dang dngos po dngos med 'byed pa bral //
NK131(do)001:2698: stong pa nyid kyi rjes 'gro du sogs ma lus glo bur shar //
NK131(do)001:2699: zhes sogs rgya cher gsungs pa yin no //
NK131(do)001:2700: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku ni sa bcu'i byang chub
NK131(do)001:2701: sems dpa' kho na la snang ba yin na gnas
NK131(do)001:2702: skabs 'dir ji ltar mthong zhe na /
NK131(do)001:2704: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i gzugs can rnams dang mkha' la rgyal ba'i sras sogs chos sku yi //
NK131(do)001:2705: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir gnas gtsang ma'i gnas na bzhugs
NK131(do)001:2706: pa'i sangs rgyas kyi sku longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku
NK131(do)001:2707: zhes bya zhing / de 'dir mthong ba yin la /
NK131(do)001:2708: longs spyod rdzogs pa chen po ni 'dir chos kyi sku'i ming gi bshad par mngon no //
NK131(do)001:2709: rnam pa gcig tu na thig le'i dbus su mthong
NK131(do)001:2710: ba'i sku gang yin pa de dag la sprul pa'i
NK131(do)001:2712: sna tshogs pa'i sgra skad mang po snang ba la longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku zhes bya'o //
NK131(do)001:2713: zhes sbyor drug pa'i bla ma gong ma rnams kyi bshad cing /
NK131(do)001:2715: rig pa tshad phebs snang ba yi //
NK131(do)001:2716: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku ngos zin //
NK131(do)001:2717: zhes pas rig pa tshad phebs kyi rnal 'byor pa
NK131(do)001:2718: de gar gnas pa'i yul de longs sku'i zhing khams
NK131(do)001:2719: dang / 'khor rnams longs sku'i 'khor du bzhag pa sogs yod kyang /
NK131(do)001:2720: rig pa tshad la ma phebs pa'i gong gi snang
NK131(do)001:2721: ba rnams la longs sku'i zhing du ma bshad cing
NK131(do)001:2722: / rig pa tshad la phebs pa'i rnal 'byor pa
NK131(do)001:2723: de rang gi blo ngo na rang gnas pa'i yul
NK131(do)001:2724: longs sku'i zhing khams dang 'khor rnams kyang de ltar
NK131(do)001:2725: / yin mod / gzhan gyi blo ngo na ni de ltar med do //
NK131(do)001:2726: 'di la slob dpon dus zhabs pas kyang longs sku'i zhing khams mthong ba yin par bshad de /
NK131(do)001:2727: dkar dang ser dang dmar dang ljang //
NK131(do)001:2730: de nang gzugs brnyan yul med pa //
NK131(do)001:2731: longs spyod rdzogs sku du ma mthong //
NK131(do)001:2732: zhes gsungs pas zhing khams kyi ngo bo ma dag pa ma yin no //
NK131(do)001:2733: rig pa lu gu rgyud mig btsum na mi gsal /
NK131(do)001:2734: nyi ma med med na mi gsal /
NK131(do)001:2735: yul can sna tshogs med na mi gsal /
NK131(do)001:2736: zhes pa rnams ni rgyus med kyi 'od tshad 'ba' zhig bris pa nyid du zad do //
NK131(do)001:2737: du sogs kyi rtags la ting nge 'dzin mchog tu yang mi 'dzin /
NK131(do)001:2738: nyams kyi shun pa yin pas der nas grol ba thob par bzhed /
NK131(do)001:2739: ces gsungs pa yang ma yin te /
NK131(do)001:2740: rgya bod gnyis su byon pa'i dus kyi 'khor lo'i
NK131(do)001:2741: mkhas grub thams cad kyis rnam kun mchog ldan gyi
NK131(do)001:2742: stong nyid ces / gces spras su mdzad cing /
NK131(do)001:2743: ye shes de la gzhom zhig med pas na //
NK131(do)001:2744: ji ltar bum pa zhig gyur kyang //
NK131(do)001:2745: nam mkha' la ni 'jig pa med //
NK131(do)001:2746: de bzhin sems ni zhig gyur kyang //
NK131(do)001:2747: ye shes la ni 'jig pa med //
NK131(do)001:2750: ji ltar zangs kyi dri ma ni //
NK131(do)001:2751: bcud kyi sbyor bas nyams par 'gyur //
NK131(do)001:2752: de yi yod nyid nyams pa med //
NK131(do)001:2753: dri med nyid kyi yang dag gnas //
NK131(do)001:2754: de bzhin sems kyi dri ma ni //
NK131(do)001:2755: stong nyid sbyor bas rnam nyams 'gyur //
NK131(do)001:2756: de yi ye shes nyid nyams med //
NK131(do)001:2757: dri med nyid kyi yang dag gnas //
NK131(do)001:2758: zhes gser 'gyur gyi rtsi la dpe mdzad de yang
NK131(do)001:2759: dag pa'i ye shes nyams pa med par gsungs pa
NK131(do)001:2760: yin no // yang la la dag ni thos grol bya ba yin zer /
NK131(do)001:2761: tshe 'das dang ro'i rna bar dpe klog pa dang /
NK131(do)001:2762: de 'bri ba la gtso bor 'dzin la des grol bar rlom /
NK131(do)001:2763: des na de dag gi tshig rna bar thos pa
NK131(do)001:2764: tsam gyi don rgyud la ma skyes kyang grol ba'am
NK131(do)001:2766: thos tsam gyi mi grol bar 'dug pa ni dngos su grub la /
NK131(do)001:2767: don rgyud la skyes na ni gzhan gyis kyis kyang
NK131(do)001:2768: grol bar 'gyur bas thos grol gyi gdams gzhi ma
NK131(do)001:2769: grub la / de'i don rgyud la skye ba la go dgos so //
NK131(do)001:2770: go ba la rtogs dgos so //
NK131(do)001:2771: rtogs pa la de dag gi tshig don la go ba rkang tshugs pa zhig skyes pa /
NK131(do)001:2772: de rjes nyams su blang ba zhig dgos na /
NK131(do)001:2773: lam gzhan nas kyang de ka ltar bgyi bar bstan te thos pas mi grol pa'o //
NK131(do)001:2774: zhes gleng na thos pas grol ba'i sgrub byed smra rgyu ci yod /
NK131(do)001:2776: de ni tshig thos pas don rgyud la skyes te grol ba yin te /
NK131(do)001:2778: bcom ldan 'das kyi chos kyi rnam grangs 'di bshad
NK131(do)001:2779: pa na lha'i bu gang dag stong phrag gcig mchis
NK131(do)001:2780: pa de dag chos rnams la chos kyi mig rdul
NK131(do)001:2781: med cing dri ma dang bral ba thob ste zhes
NK131(do)001:2782: pa dang / byang chub sems dpa' drug stong gis mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa thob ste /
NK131(do)001:2783: zhes thos pa dang don rgyud la skyes te grol
NK131(do)001:2784: bar gsungs pa rnams dang tshul mtshungs pa yin no
NK131(do)001:2785: // de yang sngags gsar ma'i bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i rgyud las /
NK131(do)001:2786: rtogs dang goms pa mthar phyin pa //
NK131(do)001:2787: 'di la yod pa ma yin te //
NK131(do)001:2788: rtogs pa'i skad cig de nyid la //
NK131(do)001:2789: bcu pa'i sa la nges par gnas //
NK131(do)001:2791: 'dir gdams ngag gi don bsgrags pa de thos pa
NK131(do)001:2792: tsam gyi rgyud la ngo 'phrod nas bde blag tu
NK131(do)001:2795: go ba dang ni rtogs pa gnyis //
NK131(do)001:2796: don gcig ming gi rnam grangs yin //
NK131(do)001:2798: sang kri ta la skad dod kyang gcig yin pas /
NK131(do)001:2799: go ba dang rtogs pa don gcig /
NK131(do)001:2800: de ltar rtogs pa de nyid mi brtan po la phrin bskur ba ltar ma brjed par byas pas /
NK131(do)001:2801: bar do'i snang ba sgra 'od zer gsum la sogs pa rang snang du ngo shes pas /
NK131(do)001:2803: zung du 'jug pa'i tshul gyi skad cig de nyid la 'tshang rgya ba /
NK131(do)001:2804: skad cig gcig gi bye brag phyed //
NK131(do)001:2805: skad cig gcig gi rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NK131(do)001:2806: zhes gsungs pa ltar grol ba'o //
NK131(do)001:2807: 'di ni rtogs pa dang grol ba dus mnyam pa'am /
NK131(do)001:2808: shar grol dus mnyam gyi skabs dang 'dra bas gdams
NK131(do)001:2809: pa btab pa ma brjed pa kho nas rang grol
NK131(do)001:2810: ba yin pas na lam gzhan ltar 'bad pas nyams
NK131(do)001:2811: su blang dgos pa ma yin te /
NK131(do)001:2812: slob dpon dga' rab rdo rjes /
NK131(do)001:2813: yin pa grub pa med pa'i rig pa 'di //
NK131(do)001:2814: rang snang 'char tshul cir yang ma 'gag pas //
NK131(do)001:2815: snang srid kun kyang chos sku'i zhing du shar //
NK131(do)001:2816: shar ba de nyid rang gi thog tu grol //
NK131(do)001:2820: gdengs grol thog tu bca' ba'o //
NK131(do)001:2822: de ltar bla ma'i gdams ngag gi 'od gsal ngos
NK131(do)001:2823: zin nas sangs rgyas nyid du grol ba de'i ngang
NK131(do)001:2824: las gzugs sku rnam pa gnyis la sogs pas gdul
NK131(do)001:2825: bya'i don dpag tu med pa mdzad pa'i tshul ni
NK131(do)001:2826: / gnyis med rnam rgyal gyi rgyud las /
NK131(do)001:2827: 'od gsal zin pa'i gang zag la //
NK131(do)001:2828: bar do'i grong khyer des mi mthong //
NK131(do)001:2829: gzhan don gzugs sku'i snang ba 'char //
NK131(do)001:2830: dper na yin bzhin nor bu bzhin //
NK131(do)001:2832: yang thos grol rang gzhung bshad pa'i zhag phyed dang bzhi'i phyi ma tshun chad la /
NK131(do)001:2833: zhi khro'i bar do sgra 'od kyi snang ba dang
NK131(do)001:2834: bcas te 'char bar gsungs pa de dag 'jag mig
NK131(do)001:2835: gi srin bu la sogs pa sems can thams cad
NK131(do)001:2836: la char ba'am / 'on te thos grol nyams su
NK131(do)001:2837: len mkhan gyi gang zag gcig la 'char ba yin
NK131(do)001:2838: la char ba'am / / sems can thams cad la 'char ba ni mi srid de /
NK131(do)001:2839: spyir bar dor 'char ba'i snang ba phal che ba
NK131(do)001:2840: ni bag chags dang las snang kho na 'char bar
NK131(do)001:2841: gsungs la / srin bu dang grog ma lta bu
NK131(do)001:2842: la lha de dag gi bag chags gtan med pa'i
NK131(do)001:2843: gsungs la / phyir / gal te shar na'ang zhi
NK131(do)001:2844: ba'i skabs su 'od bkrag can bkrag med la spangs
NK131(do)001:2846: khro bo'i skabs su de dag la 'jigs par yang mi 'gyur te /
NK131(do)001:2847: mir gyur pa rnams dur khrod kyi ro la shin tu 'jigs na'ang /
NK131(do)001:2848: grog ma la sogs kyi srog chags phra mo dag ro la sa gzhi'i 'du shes yod de /
NK131(do)001:2849: de'i ngos la 'jigs med du rgyu ba dang /
NK131(do)001:2850: tshang 'cha' ba sogs kyang byed pa'i phyir /
NK131(do)001:2851: des na 'gro ba dag gi mig ngor snang ba
NK131(do)001:2852: gcig la mdzes pa dang 'jigs par snang ba de
NK131(do)001:2853: dag thams cad la de ltar mi lta ste /
NK131(do)001:2854: sdig pa ra can khyo shug gnyis la nang mthun par tshad med kyi mdzes snang yod kyang /
NK131(do)001:2855: mis mthong na bred cing sngangs par 'gyur bas /
NK131(do)001:2856: nges par bar dor 'jigs skrag 'ong rgyu yin na'ang
NK131(do)001:2857: rang rang gi gshed mar gyur pa'i gzugs brnyan cig
NK131(do)001:2858: ma shar na / thams cad khro bo'i gzugs la 'jigs pa mi srid de /
NK131(do)001:2859: de ltar gsar rnying gnyis las bar do'i 'char tshul bshad pa ni mi'i rten la 'char ba ste /
NK131(do)001:2860: lam du 'khyer shes pa'i ched du gsungs pa yin
NK131(do)001:2861: pas thams cad la zhi khro 'char bar gsungs pa
NK131(do)001:2862: ma dag / nges par cis kyang 'char na de la brtag pa gsum bya ste /
NK131(do)001:2863: bar dor shar ba'i lha de nyams snang ba la shar ba'i lha yin nam /
NK131(do)001:2864: rtsa yig mthong snang las shar ba'i lha yin nam /
NK131(do)001:2865: rgyud byin gyis barloba par byed pa'i ye shes kyi lha yin /
NK131(do)001:2866: nyams kyi lha yin na sems can rang rgyud pa
NK131(do)001:2867: la lha de dag gi bag chags gtan med pas
NK131(do)001:2869: rtsa yig mthong snang gi lha yin na yid lus la rtsa yig ma mchis /
NK131(do)001:2870: ye shes kyi lha yin na ye shes kyi lha
NK131(do)001:2871: lta ba'i skal ba yod pa la rang rgyud kyi
NK131(do)001:2872: nyon mongs pa dag par bshad pa la /
NK131(do)001:2873: tha na bshad pa lta bu'i gang zag las nyon
NK131(do)001:2874: can gyis kyang mthong ba 'di 'dra'i ye shes kyi
NK131(do)001:2875: lha ci lta bu yin zhes dri na ci smra
NK131(do)001:2877: zhi khro'i bar do sgra 'od zer dang bcas pa
NK131(do)001:2878: de ni 'jag mig gi srin bu la sogs pa
NK131(do)001:2879: sems can thams cad la 'char ba yin te /
NK131(do)001:2880: dpal brtag pa gnyis pa las /
NK131(do)001:2881: sems can rnams ni sangs rgyas nyid de mtshan sum
NK131(do)001:2882: cu rtsa gnyis dang ldan pa yang sems can thams
NK131(do)001:2885: srin bu dang grog ma lta bu la lha de dag gi bag chags med kyang /
NK131(do)001:2886: de dag rang rang gi kun gzhi bde bar gshegs
NK131(do)001:2887: pa'i snying po de la spyan lnga la sogs pa
NK131(do)001:2888: rnams rang chas su yod pas mthong ba yin te
NK131(do)001:2890: nang du 'dus pa kun mkhyen gzugs ni khams gsum
NK131(do)001:2891: po ma lus pa chu la nyi ma lta bu
NK131(do)001:2892: gos pa med pa kha dog sna tshogs te /
NK131(do)001:2893: rnam pa kun ldan rang sems yul dang rnam par
NK131(do)001:2894: bral ba dag go sems ni gzhan pa min pa
NK131(do)001:2895: nyid / gzhan gyi sems ni ma yin te gzhan gyi sems zhes pa med pa'i phyir ro //
NK131(do)001:2896: 'dir ni de bzhin gshegs pa sha'i spyan gyis dang por rang gi sems kyi snang ba mthong zhing /
NK131(do)001:2897: lha la sogs pa'i spyan gyis gzhan gyi sems kyi shes pa mthong ba ste /
NK131(do)001:2898: des na chos yang dag par sdud pa las bcom ldan 'das kyi spyan lnga zhes gsungs so //
NK131(do)001:2900: de dag rang rang gi lus la gnas pa'i ye
NK131(do)001:2901: shes kyi rang rtsal phyir shar ba yin pas bag
NK131(do)001:2902: chags la rag ma lus shing /
NK131(do)001:2903: de ltar nges par du 'char ba yin kyang /
NK131(do)001:2905: khro bo la 'jigs pa'i snang ba 'char bar ni ma bshad do //
NK131(do)001:2906: 'on kyang stong khams shig shig yom yom 'gul ba dang /
NK131(do)001:2907: nam mkha'i khams kun mes gang ba //
NK131(do)001:2908: sgra drag po 'brug stong ldir ba la sogs pa la ni skrag par 'gyur mod /
NK131(do)001:2909: 'dir 'od la spangs blang dang khro bo la 'jigs pa'i snang ba dang /
NK131(do)001:2910: de dag ngo shes na grol ba dang /
NK131(do)001:2911: ma shes na 'ching ba'i tshul bshad pa rnams ni spyir mi'i rten can dang /
NK131(do)001:2912: khyad par du lam pa'i rnal 'byor pa rnams la 'char ba nyid du gsungs pa yin te /
NK131(do)001:2913: de yang da lta lus la ye shes kyi lha gnas te /
NK131(do)001:2914: snying nang na zhi ba'i lha tshogs /
NK131(do)001:2915: klad pa dung khang na khro bo'i lha tshogs rnams
