NK131(do)001:2916: ye shes kyi rang 'od rang gsal bar bzhugs pa'i
NK131(do)001:2917: don gyi lam gyi rnal 'byor pa rnams la bsgom
NK131(do)001:2918: pa'i tshe na cung zad gsal la /
NK131(do)001:2919: skye bo phal pa rnams la mi gsal kyang /
NK131(do)001:2920: lus sems bral bar gyur pa de'i tshe /
NK131(do)001:2921: ye shes de dag phyir thon pas nam mkhas khyab tshad du 'char ba yin no //
NK131(do)001:2923: rang gi lus la sangs rgyas bzhugs //
NK131(do)001:2924: gzhan du gang na'ang sangs rgyas med //
NK131(do)001:2925: mi shes mun pas sgribs pa rnams //
NK131(do)001:2926: lus las gzhan du sangs rgyas 'dod //
NK131(do)001:2927: rtog pa thams cad rnam spangs pa'i //
NK131(do)001:2928: ye shes chen po lus la gnas //
NK131(do)001:2930: brtag pa lus gnyis pa las /
NK131(do)001:2931: 'di nyid ye shes chen po nyid //
NK131(do)001:2932: thams cad lus la rnam par gnas //
NK131(do)001:2933: gnyis dang gnyis su med pa'i tshul //
NK131(do)001:2934: dngos dang dngos med bdag nyid gtso //
NK131(do)001:2935: brtan dang g.yo ba khyab gnas pa //
NK131(do)001:2936: sgyu ma'i gzugs can nyid du gnas //
NK131(do)001:2937: zhes pas kyang lus la lha dang ye shes gnas par gsungs shing /
NK131(do)001:2938: gzhan yang phung khams rigs lnga yab yum dang /
NK131(do)001:2939: dbang po la sogs pa sems dpa' sems ma /
NK131(do)001:2940: lhu tshigs khro bo bcu la sogs pa lus kyi
NK131(do)001:2941: dkyil 'khor gdan gsum tshang ba zhes bshad pa'i don
NK131(do)001:2942: gyis kyang lus la lha gnas par gsungs so //
NK131(do)001:2943: de las thams cad la zhi khro 'char bar gsungs pa ni /
NK131(do)001:2944: rang rang gi nyams su gang blang pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK131(do)001:2945: gyi lha rnams bag chags kyi dbang gi 'char ba
NK131(do)001:2946: ma yin / 'dir sems can thams cad la mtshungs par /
NK131(do)001:2947: phung po lnga rgyal ba rigs lnga 'byung ba lnga yum lnga /
NK131(do)001:2948: shes pa bzhi dang dbang po bzhi sems dpa' brgyad /
NK131(do)001:2949: yul bzhi dus bzhi sems ma brgyad /
NK131(do)001:2950: dug lnga ser sna thub pa drug /
NK131(do)001:2951: sa chu me rlung gi sgo bzhi rnams sgo ba yab yum ste /
NK131(do)001:2952: zhi ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi lha tshogs dang /
NK131(do)001:2953: de'i rtsal las khro bo khrag 'thung lnga bcu rtsa brgyad du shar ba ni /
NK131(do)001:2954: phung po lnga dang 'byung ba lnga he ru ka yab yum bcu /
NK131(do)001:2955: rnam shes tshogs brgyad ma mo brgyad /
NK131(do)001:2956: phung po brgyad phra men ma brgyad /
NK131(do)001:2957: byams snying rje dga' ba btang snyoms bzhi sgo ma bzhi /
NK131(do)001:2958: sgal tshigs sam nyon mongs pa nyi shu rtsa brgyad
NK131(do)001:2959: gnas su dag pa las dbang phyug ma nyi shu
NK131(do)001:2960: rtsa brgyad de / de ltar du rang rang gi
NK131(do)001:2961: phung khams skye mched la ye gdod ma nas gnas
NK131(do)001:2962: pa'i zhi khro 'char bar gsungs pa yin no //
NK131(do)001:2963: de dag nyams snang las shar ba'i lha yang yin te /
NK131(do)001:2964: bar do'i snang ba thams cad nyams kyi snang ba yin pas so //
NK131(do)001:2965: rtsa yig mthong snang las shar ba'i lha khang yin te /
NK131(do)001:2966: de ltar srog 'gag nas 'tsho ba'i rlung 'byung 'jug
NK131(do)001:2967: gi rgyu ba chad de lus sems barjesa pa'i rkyen
NK131(do)001:2968: gyi / lus la gnas pa'i rtsa'i yi ge dang
NK131(do)001:2969: khams kyi dngas cha dang rlung ngo bo nyid la
NK131(do)001:2970: sogs pa phyir 'thon pa'i snang ba yin par slob
NK131(do)001:2972: bcom ldan srog gi lhag pa'i bdag po /
NK131(do)001:2973: rje bo bdag nyid la ni thim gyur cing /
NK131(do)001:2974: 'tsho ba'i rlung gi rgyu ba 'byung dang 'jug pa'i tshogs rab zhi bar gyur pa na /
NK131(do)001:2975: gang zhig rnal 'byor dbang phyug rnams kyi 'od gsal skar ma'i snang ba rab 'byams ni /
NK131(do)001:2976: rang lus nyid las nges thon mun pa bcom nas 'jig rten gsum po gnon par byed /
NK131(do)001:2978: yid lus la rtsa yig med kyang /
NK131(do)001:2979: lus snga ma'i rtsa yig yin phyir shar ba yin no //
NK131(do)001:2980: rgyud byin gyis brlabs pa'i ye shes kyi lha yang yin te /
NK131(do)001:2981: dus der ngo shes pa tsam gyi sangs rgyas kyi 'bras bu ster bas so //
NK131(do)001:2982: 'o na ngo ma shes na slar 'khor bar 'khrul pa bskyed par byed pa ci snyam na /
NK131(do)001:2983: de ni sngon gnas brtan lha sbyin dang legs skar
NK131(do)001:2984: gyi bcom ldan 'das thams cad mkhyen pa nyid du
NK131(do)001:2985: ma shes pas lus ma spangs pas dmyal bar song
NK131(do)001:2986: ba bzhin no // spyir na khams gsum pa'i sems
NK131(do)001:2987: can rnams kyi rang la gnas pa'i ye shes ngo
NK131(do)001:2988: ma shes pa kho na sa zo chun gyi 'khyud
NK131(do)001:2989: mo bzhin du 'khor bar 'khor ba'i tshul yang khongs
NK131(do)001:2991: bar dor las snang kho na 'char ba yang ma yin te /
NK131(do)001:2993: ba lang 'tsho dang ngang pa dang //
NK131(do)001:2994: rta yi rnal 'byor snang ba dang //
NK131(do)001:2996: shar dang nub tu rim bzhin 'jug /
NK131(do)001:2997: chags sdang phrag dog spel bar 'gyur //
NK131(do)001:2998: 'dzam gling khang bzang nyams dga' bo //
NK131(do)001:2999: lha min nags tshal stug po ste //
NK131(do)001:3000: lha la rin chen gzhal med khang //
NK131(do)001:3001: dud 'gro sa phug skyil por mthong //
NK131(do)001:3002: yi dwags rang gi lus kyi cha //
NK131(do)001:3003: sdang dum phyar ba lta bu'o //
NK131(do)001:3004: dmyal bar 'gro na spyi tshugs so //
NK131(do)001:3005: zhes rigs drug tu skye ba'i snang ba sna tshogs pa de ltar 'char bar gsungs na /
NK131(do)001:3006: grog sbur la sogs pa dag la de dag gi
NK131(do)001:3007: bag chags med pas las snang de ltar 'char ba
NK131(do)001:3008: mi srid par 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK131(do)001:3009: yang ye shes kyi lha sgrub pa la yang sngon bsag gi las 'phro yod pa /
NK131(do)001:3012: bsnyen sogs dag par byas pa la sogs pa rgyu
NK131(do)001:3013: rkyen rten 'brel mang du tshogs dgos par gsungs pa
NK131(do)001:3014: la / bar dor rgyu ma mchis rkyen ma mchis
NK131(do)001:3015: par ye shes kyi lha de tsam zhig gi zhal
NK131(do)001:3016: mthong bar gsungs pa yang ci lta bu yin zhes
NK131(do)001:3018: sgrub thabs zab mo gcig la brten nas 'bad rtsol gyis sgrub pas /
NK131(do)001:3019: lha 'grub cing zhal mthong ba'i tshe tshe rabs kyi sgrib pa 'dag /
NK131(do)001:3021: mkha' spyod du 'dren par bshad pa la /
NK131(do)001:3022: zhi khro'i lha de dag mthong ba la mthong thos dran reg gi yon tan med par /
NK131(do)001:3023: slar gnyis 'dzin skye ba'i 'od bkrag can bkrag med
NK131(do)001:3024: thugs kha nas 'gyed par mdzad de 'khrul nas 'khor
NK131(do)001:3025: bar 'khyams par byed pa'i yi dam gyi lha de
NK131(do)001:3026: 'dra ci lta bu zhes dri na 'di la ci
NK131(do)001:3027: smra / yang zhi khro nyams su len pa po'i gang zag gcig la 'char na /
NK131(do)001:3028: des na 'gro ba thams cad kyi thos grol nyams su ma blangs /
NK131(do)001:3030: ma shar bas 'gro ba gzhan la thos grol bklag
NK131(do)001:3031: pa don med de ngo 'phrod pa'i rten ma mchis
NK131(do)001:3032: pas so // zhes dri ba gsum gsungs pa'i dang
NK131(do)001:3033: po gnyis ni gang zag rim gyis pa bskyed rim
NK131(do)001:3034: la brten nas lus kyi bag chags sbyong /
NK131(do)001:3035: bzlas pa la rten nas ngag gi bag chags sbyong /
NK131(do)001:3036: rdzogs rim la rten nas yid kyi bag chags sbyangs
NK131(do)001:3037: pas lhag pa'i lha'i zhal mthong ste bskyed rim gyi
NK131(do)001:3038: sgo nas lha grub pa yin la de dang 'di
NK131(do)001:3039: mi mtshungs te 'di ni gong du smos pa bzhin
NK131(do)001:3040: du ye nas gnas pa'i lha rang gi lus las
NK131(do)001:3041: thon pa'i snang ba yin no //
NK131(do)001:3042: 'o na 'di dag ye shes kyi lha yin nam ma yin ce na /
NK131(do)001:3043: yin te 'di las gzhan pa'i ye shes kyi lha gang yang med de /
NK131(do)001:3045: rang 'od ye shes ldan pa'i sku //
NK131(do)001:3046: 'ja' tshon bzhin du gsal ba'i bdag /
NK131(do)001:3047: stong pa gsum las 'das pa po //
NK131(do)001:3048: thogs pa med pa'i ye shes 'phro //
NK131(do)001:3050: sems can 'khor bar 'khyams par bya ba'i slad du
NK131(do)001:3051: thugs kha nas 'od bkrag can bkrag med 'gyed par
NK131(do)001:3052: mdzad pa ga la zhig ste /
NK131(do)001:3053: sems can rnams kyi ni rang ma rig pa kho
NK131(do)001:3054: na'i skyon yin pa de'i phyir bcom ldan 'das kyis
NK131(do)001:3055: / gang dag nga la gzugs su mthong //
NK131(do)001:3056: gang dag nga la sgrar shes pa //
NK131(do)001:3057: log pa'i lam du zhugs pa ste //
NK131(do)001:3058: skye bo dag gi nga mi mthong //
NK131(do)001:3059: sangs rgyas rnams ni chos nyid lta //
NK131(do)001:3060: 'dren pa rnams ni chos kyi sku //
NK131(do)001:3061: chos nyid shes par bya min pas //
NK131(do)001:3062: de ni rnam par shes mi nus //
NK131(do)001:3063: shes pas sangs rgyas rnams ni yang dag pa'i chos
NK131(do)001:3064: nyid dmigs su med pa nam mkha' lta bu rtog
NK131(do)001:3065: pa thams cad las rnam par grol ba dri ma
NK131(do)001:3066: med pa'i chos kyi sku can yin pa de'i phyir
NK131(do)001:3067: / byis pa'i skye bo bdag dang gzhan du smra
NK131(do)001:3068: ba gzugs dang mtshan mar 'dzin pa rnams kyi de
NK131(do)001:3069: lta bu'i chos nyid de ni shes par bya ba'i
NK131(do)001:3070: yul ma yin pas 'khor bar 'khor ba nyid du
NK131(do)001:3071: / gsungs so // dri ba gsum pa'i don ni /
NK131(do)001:3072: sems can thams cad la zhi khro 'char bar khas blangs pas khegs pa yin mod /
NK131(do)001:3073: gal te lha ma shar kyang thos grol bklag pa
NK131(do)001:3074: don med pa dang ngo 'phrod pa'i rten ma mchis
NK131(do)001:3076: zhi khro'i lha de dag gi mtshan lan gcig thos
NK131(do)001:3077: pas kyang na rag chen por mi lhung ba'i dgos
NK131(do)001:3078: pa chen po yod par bshad la /
NK131(do)001:3079: de'i sems rgyud de ka ngo sprod pa'i rten yin
NK131(do)001:3080: pas ngo sprod 'khor 'das rang grol ltar du phyag
NK131(do)001:3081: rgya chen po'i gdams pa btab pas grol bar 'gyur
NK131(do)001:3082: bas so // yang thos grol nyams su len pa
NK131(do)001:3083: la zhi khro 'char na gzhan la'ang nyams su gang
NK131(do)001:3085: bde mchog pa la bde mchog dang /
NK131(do)001:3086: dgyes rdor ba la dgyes rdor lha dgu sogs 'char dgos te /
NK131(do)001:3087: gsar ma'i rgyud lung phal che ba las /
NK131(do)001:3088: rang lus las de dag thon nas 'char ba'i bshad pa gtan nas med la /
NK131(do)001:3089: bde mchog lta bu nyams su blang pas /
NK131(do)001:3090: rab tshe 'dir phung khams 'khor lo sdom pa'i ngo bor grol te lhag med 'grub pa dang /
NK131(do)001:3091: 'bring 'chi ba chos sku mkha' khyab kyi 'od gsal
NK131(do)001:3092: ba'i rang bzhin 'khrul na yid lus su ldang rgyu
NK131(do)001:3093: de 'khor lo sdom pa rten brten pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK131(do)001:3094: du bzhengs nas sangs rgyas par 'gyur ba'i bshad pa
NK131(do)001:3095: yod na / de dang bar do'i 'khrul ngo la
NK131(do)001:3096: yi dam gyi lha 'char ba gnyis khyad shin tu
NK131(do)001:3097: yod na / che / des na bar dor las snang gi gshin rje'i skyes bu dang /
NK131(do)001:3098: 'byung ba dgrar langs kyi 'khrul snang nges pa dang
NK131(do)001:3099: ma nges pa dang ma nges pa sna tshogs 'char
NK131(do)001:3100: bar gsungs pa las zhi khro zhal phyag nges pa
NK131(do)001:3101: can de kho na 'char ba tshad ldan gyi gzhung
NK131(do)001:3103: 'khrul ngo'i las snang yin pa'i rtags su sdig can
NK131(do)001:3104: dang skye bo phal pa la dbugs chad kha nyid
NK131(do)001:3106: de nas shin tu rags par 'char bas sngangs skrag che /
NK131(do)001:3108: lam pa la las snang cung zad las med pas 'jigs skrag chung /
NK131(do)001:3110: 'khrul snang zhig pa'i gang zag lta bas thebs pa rnams la bar do mi 'byung bar gsungs so //
NK131(do)001:3111: des na las snang gi 'khrul ngor ye shes kyi
NK131(do)001:3112: lha 'char bar gsungs pa yang sngags btsun skye bo
NK131(do)001:3113: dag gi blo bzo yin no //
NK131(do)001:3114: zhes smra na 'di la gtan tshig smra rgyu ci yod /
NK131(do)001:3116: gsang sngags gsar ma'i rgyud lung rnams nas /
NK131(do)001:3117: bde mchog la sogs pa'i lha rnams lus las thon te 'char bar ma gsung ba de bzhin du /
NK131(do)001:3118: 'dir yang nyams su gang blang ba'i lha de dag 'char bar bshad pa med mod /
NK131(do)001:3119: bde mchog pa dag gi grol lugs rab 'bring gi
NK131(do)001:3120: rnam dbye gsung pa ni ji skad bka' stsal pa
NK131(do)001:3122: 'dir ni theg pa'i go rim gyi dbye bas de dag dang mthun dgos pa'i nges pa med pas /
NK131(do)001:3123: de bas na 'dir gsungs pa'i zhi khro'i snang ba
NK131(do)001:3124: rnams bar do'i 'khrul ngo kho na la shar ba
NK131(do)001:3125: ma yin / lus can rnams la bar do drug
NK131(do)001:3126: tu phye ba'i 'chi kha'i bar do la sdig pa
NK131(do)001:3127: can gyi skye bo la gnad gcod kyi sdug bsngal
NK131(do)001:3129: de'i tshe 'od khug pa lnga 'char mod kyi /
NK131(do)001:3130: gdams ngag dang mi ldan pas sam /
NK131(do)001:3131: ldan kyang rung ste las kyi sgrib pas ngo mi shes /
NK131(do)001:3132: de nas chos nyid kyi bar do zhi khro dag
NK131(do)001:3133: sgra 'od zer gsum la sogs pa'i snang ba de
NK131(do)001:3134: dag 'byung yang bsam gtan gyi zhag lnga las yun
NK131(do)001:3135: ring bar mi gnas pa yin /
NK131(do)001:3136: de la bsam gtan gyi zhag ces pa ting nge
NK131(do)001:3137: 'dzin dang mi ldan pa'i skye bo tha ma la
NK131(do)001:3138: pa dag la se gol gcig gi yun tshad yin
NK131(do)001:3139: cing / rnal 'byor pa rnams kyi ting nge 'dzin
NK131(do)001:3140: yun ji tsam thub pa de nyid kyi yun tshad
NK131(do)001:3142: de nas skye bo phal pa dag la srid pa
NK131(do)001:3143: bar do'i snang ba rang rang gi bsags pa dang
NK131(do)001:3144: mthun pa'i las snang nges pa dang ma nges pa
NK131(do)001:3146: zhi khro sgra 'od zer dang bcas pa'i snang ba
NK131(do)001:3147: de dag gi go chod nas las snang gzhan gtan
NK131(do)001:3148: nas mi 'char bar gsungs pa ma yin /
NK131(do)001:3149: lam pa'i rnal 'byor pa la yang 'chi kha'i bar
NK131(do)001:3150: do'i thim rim dang 'od khug pa lnga dang de
NK131(do)001:3151: rjes chos nyid kyi bar dor rang so ma zin
NK131(do)001:3152: na / bsag pa dang mthun pa'i las snang nges ma nges sna tshogs 'char bas /
NK131(do)001:3153: de'i dus su yur ba skongs chag pa la wa
NK131(do)001:3154: 'dzugs pa lta bu'i srid pa bar do'i gdams pa
NK131(do)001:3155: bshad pa yin / zhi khro'i snang ba de dag
NK131(do)001:3156: chos nyid don gyi rang snang yin pas ming yang
NK131(do)001:3157: chos nyid kyi bar do zhes btags pa yin /
NK131(do)001:3159: rim lnga pa dag gi 'chi kha'i 'od gsal 'dzin pa don gcig /
NK131(do)001:3160: de dag srid pa bar ma do'i las snang gi
NK131(do)001:3161: 'khrul ngo yin par mdzad 'dug pa 'di ni dgongs
NK131(do)001:3162: pa can los yin ma yin na nan ltar ma
NK131(do)001:3163: nges pa chen po nyid do //
NK131(do)001:3164: yang la la dag ni myong grol bya ba yin
NK131(do)001:3165: zer nas ril bu zhig zos pas thar pa thob
NK131(do)001:3166: par rlom ste / de la skye bdun ril bu'i khungs ma dag par bstan pa /
NK131(do)001:3167: skye bdun rang gi ngo bo ma dag par bstan pa'o //
NK131(do)001:3168: de la skye bdun ril bu'i khungs ma dag pa ni /
NK131(do)001:3169: za hor rgyal po gtsug lag 'dzin zhes bya ba
NK131(do)001:3170: 'khor los bsgyur ba'i rgyal po lta bu zhig gi
NK131(do)001:3171: bu mo man+da ra ba bya ba zhig yod pa
NK131(do)001:3172: la / rgya dkar nag la sogs pa phyogs kyi
NK131(do)001:3173: rgyal pos btsun mor bslong ba'i snye bo mang ste
NK131(do)001:3174: la / / yab yum gyi byin ngo ma shes
NK131(do)001:3175: par man+d+ha ra ba nyid su la gtong pho brang
NK131(do)001:3176: gi yang rtser bsam gzhigs gtong bcug pa las /
NK131(do)001:3177: lan cig rgyal po'i skrums sha thogs te man+d+ha ra
NK131(do)001:3178: ba la rin du 'bras bskur te tshong 'dus su
NK131(do)001:3179: sha nyor btang ba na char ches nas tshong 'dus
NK131(do)001:3180: ma 'dzom / log pa'i lam na byis pa shi
NK131(do)001:3181: ba'i ro zhig 'dug pa las sha bregs te rgyal
NK131(do)001:3182: po la zhus pas skye bdun du rig ces smra
NK131(do)001:3183: ma 'dzom / / de la mi 'thad pa'i rgyu mtshan gsum ste /
NK131(do)001:3184: za hor rgyal po 'khor los sgyur ba lta bu'i
NK131(do)001:3185: mnga' thang yod par bstan nas gsol ba'i krum sha
NK131(do)001:3187: gal te thogs srid kyang bran g.yog dpag tu med par bstan nas /
NK131(do)001:3188: lha lcam mig 'bras ltar gces pa de la 'bras
NK131(do)001:3189: kyi sgye'u zhig rgyab tu sbrags te tshong 'dus su
NK131(do)001:3191: gal te btang du zin na'ang spyir za hor ba
NK131(do)001:3192: kun la mi sha ba'i srol dang mi ldan zhing
NK131(do)001:3193: / khyad par rgyal po la gzhan gyi mi za ba'i sha 'dren pa mi srid /
NK131(do)001:3194: des na skye bdun snyed pa'i khungs ma dag ste /
NK131(do)001:3195: 'di yang sngags btsun skye bo dag gi blo bzor rig par bya'o //
NK131(do)001:3196: de dag skyon med du 'gro ba'i sgrub byed yod na smra bar rigs so //
NK131(do)001:3197: yang skye bdun gyi ngo bo ma dag ste /
NK131(do)001:3200: da lta'i sangs rgyas dpag tu med pa'i mdzad pa
NK131(do)001:3201: ni byang chub kyi spyod pa spyad pas grol ba
NK131(do)001:3202: las / skye bdun zos pas grol ba'i sangs rgyas 'adi'o bya ba med /
NK131(do)001:3203: de bas grub pa brnyes pa tsam yang med de /
NK131(do)001:3204: rgya bod kyi grub thob 'di tsam gyi nang na
NK131(do)001:3205: lam rgyud la bsten nas grol ba las skye bdun
NK131(do)001:3206: zos pa'i grub thob 'adi'o bya ba med /
NK131(do)001:3207: yang de dag gi gdams pa la skye bdun gyi
NK131(do)001:3208: sgrub thabs zab mo 'di med de nged cag gi
NK131(do)001:3210: da lta khyed rang rnying ma ba yod do cog
NK131(do)001:3211: rnams kyang gdams pa las byung ba ltar sgrub ste
NK131(do)001:3212: skye bo'i tshogs la sbyin pa ltar byed na /
NK131(do)001:3213: de dag gi dbus na grol ba thob pa lta zhog gi /
NK131(do)001:3214: mthong snang gi yon tan skyes pa tsam yang mi snang la /
NK131(do)001:3215: sems can gyi khams rgyud rang rgyud du khregs se
NK131(do)001:3216: lus nas sangs rgyas par brtags su ni mi rung
NK131(do)001:3217: / des na skye bdun gyi sha zos pas grol
NK131(do)001:3218: bar rlom pa yang sngags btsun skye bo dag gi
NK131(do)001:3220: gsum pa nus pa ma dag pa ni gal te skye bdun des nges par grol rgyu yin na'ang /
NK131(do)001:3221: de la grol byed kyi rdzas skye bdun de mi nas mir brgyud kyi skye bdun des chog gam /
NK131(do)001:3222: gang zag chos ldan gyi skye bdun zhig dgos /
NK131(do)001:3223: chos ldan dgos na shas grol ba ma yin /
NK131(do)001:3224: chos kyi grol ba yin no //
NK131(do)001:3225: mi brgyud bdun tsam gyi chog na /
NK131(do)001:3226: mi de chos dang mi ldan pas skye ba bdun
NK131(do)001:3227: blangs kyang kho rang gi shes rgyud ma grol bar
NK131(do)001:3228: tha mal du khres se lus nas /
NK131(do)001:3229: de'i sha cung zad zos pas nged rang grol bar ci la 'gyur /
NK131(do)001:3230: des na gsang sngags gsar ma'i rgyun 'ga' zhig nas
NK131(do)001:3231: kyang skye bdun gyi dam rdzas bsten pa tsam ni
NK131(do)001:3233: rgyal mtshan dang ni mtshon snun dang //
NK131(do)001:3234: lan bdun pa yang bza' bar bya //
NK131(do)001:3236: bde mchog nges brjod bla ma las kyang gsungs la /
NK131(do)001:3237: de'i dgongs pa ni rdo rje'i lus la gnad du
NK131(do)001:3238: bsnun pas bde stong ye shes chen pos lam sgrod
NK131(do)001:3240: don dam byang chub sems kyi rten du gyur pa'i kun rdzob kun+da 'phel ba'i rgyur /
NK131(do)001:3241: rgyal mtshan rigs kyi dregs pa'i sha dang /
NK131(do)001:3242: mtshon snun g.yul du bsad pa'i sha chen /
NK131(do)001:3243: lan bdun pa mi skye ba bdun blangs pa'i gang
NK131(do)001:3244: zag las dbang gi shi ba'i sha rnams gang snyed
NK131(do)001:3245: kun+da'i rim gror 'gyur te dngos su grol ba ma
NK131(do)001:3246: yin na'ang / brgyud nas grol bar gsungs pa ltar go ba chags dgos te /
NK131(do)001:3247: de zos pas sdig can kyang grol bar 'dod pa log rtog chen po'o //
NK131(do)001:3248: zhes dri na grol nges kyi sgrub byed rnam dag smra rgyu ci yod /
NK131(do)001:3250: de la skye bdun gyi sha zos pas mkha' la
NK131(do)001:3251: spyod pa nyid du 'gyur bar mdo rgyud rnams su
NK131(do)001:3252: mang du gsungs pas khungs ma dag pa ma yin
NK131(do)001:3253: zhing / lo rgyus de la yang ma dag pa'i skyon yod pa yin te /
NK131(do)001:3254: rgyal po dpag par dka' ba'i dge ba'i blo can
NK131(do)001:3255: de nyid skye bdun gyi sha la rten te grol
NK131(do)001:3256: ba thob par 'gyur ba'i skal ba dang ldan pa
NK131(do)001:3258: de dus kyi bram ze'i sha de yang 'phags pa
NK131(do)001:3259: spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug bsam bzhin du 'gro ba'i
NK131(do)001:3260: don du skye ba lan bdun bzhes pa'i sha yin
NK131(do)001:3261: pas lha lcam rang bzhin gyi mkha' 'gro ma de
NK131(do)001:3262: yi lag tu 'ong ba las gzhan dag la len
NK131(do)001:3263: pa'i skal ba med pa'i phyir dang /
NK131(do)001:3264: za hor rgyal po 'khor dang longs spyod rab tu rgyas pa yin mod kyi /
NK131(do)001:3265: rgya gar gyi rgyal po rnams nang nub kyi gsol
NK131(do)001:3266: zas btsun mo rnams kyi gan du rim gyi gsol
NK131(do)001:3268: rgyu mtshan gsum gyi byung khungs dag pa yin no //
NK131(do)001:3270: rgyal po rkang khra btsun mo chung ba ngan shos kyi bsnyan bkur res la bab pa na /
NK131(do)001:3271: sha gzhan ma rnyed pas dur khrod na byis pa
NK131(do)001:3272: shi ba'i ro zhig 'dug pa las sha bregs te
NK131(do)001:3274: de'i rlangs pa byad bzhin la phog pas mo rkang pa sa la mi reg par 'agro'o //
NK131(do)001:3275: de khos mthong nas ngo mtshar te /
NK131(do)001:3276: mo la sdigs pas skrag ste /
NK131(do)001:3277: mchog byin nas bshad pa dang /
NK131(do)001:3278: lhag ma kun yang khyer shog zer te zos pas kho nam mkha' la 'agro'o //
NK131(do)001:3280: gsang sngags kyi rgyud sde rin po che rnams su ni skye bdun gyi shas grol ba'i tshul dang /
NK131(do)001:3281: de la rten pa'i sgrub thabs mang po gsungs pa yin te /
NK131(do)001:3282: bde mchog sdom pa 'byung ba'i rgyud las /
NK131(do)001:3283: skyes bu gang gi rdul dri zhim par gyur pa dang /
NK131(do)001:3285: yun ring por mig mi 'dzum pa dang /
NK131(do)001:3286: khro ba med par gyur pa dang /
NK131(do)001:3287: kha nas dbugs dri zhim po 'byung ba de ni skye ba bdun du mir gyur pa yin te /
NK131(do)001:3288: de bsnams na de'i snying kha la bsten pa'i go ro tsa na yod de /
NK131(do)001:3289: de blangs pa la dpal he ru ka'i sngags brgya
NK131(do)001:3290: rtsa brgyad bzlas nas thig le byas na steng du
NK131(do)001:3291: lding bar 'gyur zhing dpag tshad bye bar 'gro bar
NK131(do)001:3292: 'gyur ro // de zos pa tsam gyi dus gsum gyi ye shes can du 'gyur ro //
NK131(do)001:3294: de nyid kyi le'u bzhi bcu rtsa dgu par /
NK131(do)001:3295: gang gi kha yi dri zhim shing //
NK131(do)001:3296: mig gi 'dzum par rnam par lta //
NK131(do)001:3297: bden par smra zhing mthong na dga' //
NK131(do)001:3298: rtag tu dam chos dga' 'gyur zhing //
NK131(do)001:3299: rang gi skye ba shes pa dang //
NK131(do)001:3300: lus kyi dri ni rtag tu zhim //
NK131(do)001:3301: mtshan nyid 'di dang ldan pa ni //
NK131(do)001:3302: skye ba bdun du byung ba yin //
NK131(do)001:3303: de ni zos pa tsam gyi ni //
NK131(do)001:3305: bsnams pa'am reg pa tsam gyis ni //
NK131(do)001:3306: gang zhig thig le byas pa de //
NK131(do)001:3307: mod la grub par 'gyur ba ste //
NK131(do)001:3310: dpal brtag pa gnyis pa las kyang /
NK131(do)001:3311: skye ba bdun pa'ang de nas mtshon //
NK131(do)001:3312: dga' bral dga' ba la smod pa //
NK131(do)001:3314: dri lus gzi brjid chen po dang //
NK131(do)001:3315: skad snyan mig dang ldan pa dang //
NK131(do)001:3316: de yi grib ma bdun du 'gyur //
NK131(do)001:3317: mthong nas rnal 'byor pa yi mtshon //
NK131(do)001:3318: de ni zos pa tsam gyi ni //
NK131(do)001:3319: skad cig nyid la mkha' spyod 'gyur //
NK131(do)001:3321: gzhan rgyud sde rnams su mang du gsungs kyang 'dir
NK131(do)001:3322: yi ge mang por 'gro phyir de tsam gyi chog
NK131(do)001:3323: go // rgyas par bde mchog gi rgyud le'u lnga bcu rtsa gcig pa'i le'u bcu gcig pa dang /
NK131(do)001:3324: bde mchog nges brjod bla ma'i le'u drug cu re drug pa dang /
NK131(do)001:3325: bde mchog mkha' 'gro rgya mtsho'i rab byed gnyis pa dang /
NK131(do)001:3326: he ru ka mngon 'byung gi le'u bzhi bcu zhe gnyis pa dang /
NK131(do)001:3327: sam+bu ti'i le'u bcu bdun pa dang /
NK131(do)001:3328: phyag rgya chen po'i thig le'i le'u nyi shu rtsa bzhi pa dang /
NK131(do)001:3329: sgyu 'phrul chen mo'i rgyud kyi le'u dang po dang /
NK131(do)001:3330: de la sogs pa rnams su lta bar bya'o //
NK131(do)001:3331: 'di dag las mkha' 'gro rgya mtsho'i rab byed gnyis
NK131(do)001:3332: par bde mchog bong bu'i rnam pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi
NK131(do)001:3333: skye bdun sgrub pa gsungs pa'i tshul ni sa skya
NK131(do)001:3334: pa bdag chen thams cad mkhyen pas phyag len mdzad
NK131(do)001:3335: pa yin no // bstan bcos rnams su yang 'byung ba yin te /
NK131(do)001:3337: rgyal po grags pa mtha' yas mnga' 'bangs dang bcas
NK131(do)001:3338: pa skye bdun gyi sha zos pas mkha' spyod du
NK131(do)001:3339: song ste grong khyer stong pa bshad pa dang /
NK131(do)001:3340: lo ts+aa ba chen po shong ston gyis mdzad pa'i mtshan brjod kyi 'grel pa las /
NK131(do)001:3341: byang chub yan lag me tog spos zhes pa lan bdun pa ste /
NK131(do)001:3342: de zos pa las dga' ba zhes pa bde ba chen po 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NK131(do)001:3344: rje dam pa rgya gar gyi /
NK131(do)001:3345: chu bo ne rany+dza na'i 'gram na grub thob cig
NK131(do)001:3346: ting nge 'dzin la bzhugs pa la nya bo che
NK131(do)001:3347: cig gi khyur mid byas song bas lo bcu gnyis
NK131(do)001:3348: kyi bar du nya'i lto bar ma zhu bar ting
NK131(do)001:3350: bram ze'i sha kham gcig zos pas de mkha' spyod du song ba mthong /
NK131(do)001:3352: ces 'khor rnams kyi ya mtshan pa ci 'dra gzigs zhes zhus pa'i lan du gsungs shing /
NK131(do)001:3354: sha kham gcig zos pas dag pa'i zhing la 'gro ba'i gang zag de 'dra mthong /
NK131(do)001:3356: phyis dam pa'i gdung gzhu ba na /
NK131(do)001:3357: rgya gar nas dam pa'i slob ma grol ba thob pa'i pan+di ta gsum byung ste /
NK131(do)001:3358: bod kyi phung thal chen po byas zhes mya ngan du gyur pa na /
NK131(do)001:3359: deng ri ba dag gi rgyu mtshan dris pas de gsum na re /
NK131(do)001:3360: chos ma byas par sangs rgya ba'i thabs gsum yod de /
NK131(do)001:3361: de la phyag rgya mtshan dang ldan pa khrag 'o mar 'bab pa zhig yod /
NK131(do)001:3362: de la thabs kyi sbyor shes na sangs rgya ba yin /
NK131(do)001:3363: gnyis pa ni 'pho ba'i gnad shes na sangs rgya ba yin /
NK131(do)001:3364: gsum pa ni bram ze gtsang ma skye ba bdun
NK131(do)001:3365: brgyud pa'i sha khrag su'i ltor song yang sangs rgya
NK131(do)001:3366: ba yin / dam pa de yang skye ba bdun
NK131(do)001:3367: pa yin pa la da ni gdung thal tsam yang
NK131(do)001:3369: zhes pa zhi byed pa dag gi lo rgyus su 'byung ngo //
NK131(do)001:3370: de la skye ba bdun blangs kyang mi de chos
NK131(do)001:3371: dang mi ldan pas kho rang ma grol bas nged
NK131(do)001:3372: rang de'i shas mi grol gsung ba yang ma yin
NK131(do)001:3373: te / rdo khab len la sogs pa'i rdzas kyi
NK131(do)001:3374: 'pho ba'i nus pa mngon sum du gsal ba bla
NK131(do)001:3375: ma rnams phyag len du mdzad pa dang /
NK131(do)001:3376: dngul chu dul mas lcags kyi khams rnams gser du bsgyur ba bzhin du /
NK131(do)001:3377: 'dir yang rdzas kyi nus pas mkha' spyod nyid 'grub par byed pa yin no //
NK131(do)001:3378: de ltar skye bdun gyi sha kho nas kyang mkha' spyod kyi 'bras bu ster ba nyid na /
NK131(do)001:3379: rgyud lung las byung ba'i sgrub thabs bzhin du tshul
NK131(do)001:3380: bzhin sgrub pas grol ba thob par ci ste mi
NK131(do)001:3382: yang la la dag ni btags pas grol ba yin zer nas glegs bam 'dra dang /
NK131(do)001:3385: de yang 'gro don rgya che zer nas spar ma mang du byas nas mgrin pa dang /
NK131(do)001:3387: dpung par bcangs pas grol bar rlom /
NK131(do)001:3388: de ni 'thad pa ma yin te /
NK131(do)001:3389: btags grol bstan pa spyi dang mi mthun par bstan pa /
NK131(do)001:3390: btags pas mi grol ba'i shes byed bstan pa'o //
NK131(do)001:3391: spyi dang mi mthun pa ni /
NK131(do)001:3392: sh+aakya'i rgyal po'i gzungs 'ga' zhig na gdul bya drangs
NK131(do)001:3393: pa'i don du bris pa dang bklag pa dang bcangs
NK131(do)001:3394: pa dang / kun chub par byas pa la phan yon mang du gsungs kyang /
NK131(do)001:3395: nges don gyi chos 'khor rnams na de dag kyang
NK131(do)001:3396: bshad pa med de lam nyams su blang pas grol
NK131(do)001:3398: btags grol gyi mdo zur pa mi bzhugs /
NK131(do)001:3399: gsar ma'i rgyud phal cher na rgyud de'i glegs bam bri thabs dang /
NK131(do)001:3400: bcangs thabs re gsungs kyang de ni mi 'bral ba'i
NK131(do)001:3401: dam tshig gi rten du bcangs ba yin gyi grol
NK131(do)001:3403: des na rnying ma'i snying thig tu grags pa rnams
NK131(do)001:3404: na btags grol rgyud drug tu grags pa sogs 'dug
NK131(do)001:3405: kyang brtsams rgyud sha stag las rgyud mtshan nyid pa
NK131(do)001:3406: ma yin no // zhes dri na 'di la lan ci smra /
NK131(do)001:3407: de yang nges par glegs gcig bcangs pas grol nges yin na /
NK131(do)001:3408: mnyam med sh+aakya'i rgyal po chu bo ne ran dza
NK131(do)001:3409: nar dka' thub lo drug spyod par mdzad pa bas
NK131(do)001:3410: 'khor lo spar ma zhig mchan khung du bcangs pa
NK131(do)001:3411: mdzad rgyur snang / de ni gdul bya'i snang ngor mdzad pa yin /
NK131(do)001:3412: don la dka' ba spyod mi dgos so zhe na /
NK131(do)001:3413: gdul bya lam pa'i ngor dka' ba spyod pa mdzad
NK131(do)001:3414: pa de ka rjes 'jug gis lam la dka' ba
NK131(do)001:3415: spyad pas grol bar bstan pa yin gyi /
NK131(do)001:3416: btags pas grol ba sogs kyi sangs rgyas las sla bar bstan dgongs pa ma yin no //
NK131(do)001:3417: de ltar rgya bod kyi grub thob rnams kyang chos
NK131(do)001:3418: phyir de tsam gyi ngal ba mdzad pa las btags
NK131(do)001:3420: des mi grol bar mkhyen pas lam la 'bad pa kho na mdzad pa yin no //
NK131(do)001:3421: zhes dri na btags pas grol ba'i gtan tshig smra rgyu ci yod /
NK131(do)001:3422: yang btags pas mi grol ba'i shes byed ni /
NK131(do)001:3423: khyed rang rnying ma ba'i lugs la btags grol bcangs
NK131(do)001:3424: pas grol ba'i byin rlabs de lus 'di dang ldan
NK131(do)001:3427: ldan dus na 'byung na btags grol bcangs pa'i gang zag 'di tsam mang ba'i nang na /
NK131(do)001:3428: lam dang mi ldan par btags grol bcangs tsam gyi grol ba ni gcig kyang ma mthong zhing /
NK131(do)001:3429: grol ba lta zhog gi 'khrul snang cung zad kha bri ba tsam dang /
NK131(do)001:3430: 'khor ba la cung zad zhen pa chung ba tsam dang /
NK131(do)001:3431: shes bya la cung zad blo kha yang sa tsam 'gro ba su byung /
NK131(do)001:3432: ma byung bas mi grol bar dngos su grub bo zhe na ci smra /
NK131(do)001:3434: btags grol lus la 'bral med du yod dus gang zag rang rgyud du khres se lus nas /
NK131(do)001:3435: lus sems btags grol gsum tha dad du gyes tshe
NK131(do)001:3436: byin rlabs 'byung ba ni shes bya la mi srid
NK131(do)001:3437: / gal te srid na'ang btags grol dang bral nas
NK131(do)001:3438: grol ba de btags grol gyi byin brlabs su mi
NK131(do)001:3439: rung zhes dri na ci smra /
NK131(do)001:3440: yang btags grol rgyud don ngo 'phrod dgos /
NK131(do)001:3441: 'phrod pa'i don nyams su len pa na dam tshig gi rten tsam du dang /
NK131(do)001:3442: dran 'dzin gyi rten tsam du glegs bam bcang ba yang yin zer ba snang bas /
NK131(do)001:3443: des na bsgoms grol yin gyi btags grol gyi mtshan nyid mi ldan /
NK131(do)001:3444: des na btags pas grol bar 'dod pa yang sngags
NK131(do)001:3445: btsun skye bo dag gi blo bzor rig par bya'o
NK131(do)001:3446: // yang la la dag ni btags grol lus la bcangs pa dang /
NK131(do)001:3447: 'chi khar skye bdun ril bu khar song ba rnams grol ba ni rtags kyi bslu ba med de /
NK131(do)001:3449: rus pa la gdung rigs 'byung ba sogs yod pa'o zhe na /
NK131(do)001:3450: de la yang nges pa med de /
NK131(do)001:3451: 'byung ba rten 'brel tshogs pa'i 'ja' ni ma nges par skabs 'ga' rer snang /
NK131(do)001:3452: la la de dang 'grig pa yin /
NK131(do)001:3453: 'dra min bdud kyi byas pa'i 'ja' ni sdig can bshan pa la'ang 'char /
NK131(do)001:3454: de ni gang zag chos dang mi ldan snyam par
NK131(do)001:3455: lta ba'i log rtog bskyed de 'gro ba chos la
NK131(do)001:3456: mi 'jug pa'i don du bdud kyi bskul ba'i rdzu
NK131(do)001:3457: 'phrul yin / de sogs 'ja' rtags la nor ba mang ste brtag mi thub /
NK131(do)001:3458: ring bsrel la'ang ji skad du /
NK131(do)001:3459: ring bsrel phal cher bdud kyi byas //
NK131(do)001:3460: gzhan dag la yang dbye ba yod //
NK131(do)001:3461: 'byung bas grub pa'i ring bsrel dang //
NK131(do)001:3462: rdzas kyi bcos pa'i ring bsrel dang //
NK131(do)001:3463: sngags kyis sgrubs pa'i ring bsrel dang //
NK131(do)001:3464: bden pa mthong ba'i ring bsrel dang //
NK131(do)001:3465: de bzhin gshegs pa'i ring bsrel dang //
NK131(do)001:3466: 'dra min mang po nor sa yod //
NK131(do)001:3467: ces pa ltar de dag gang yin mi shes la /
NK131(do)001:3468: btags grol dang skye bdun tshad ldan la ni 'ja'
NK131(do)001:3469: dang ring bsrel 'byung nges su mi 'dug ste mi
NK131(do)001:3471: la la dag la rtags nges pa can byung ba ltar snang na yang /
NK131(do)001:3472: brul thub min pa'i rtags su rjes nas gshin 'dre
NK131(do)001:3473: gzhan pas thu ba sogs kyang 'dug pas 'di dag
NK131(do)001:3475: des na gang zag blo mig dang ldan pa rnams kyi ji skad du /
NK131(do)001:3476: chos ni khyi yi zas bzhin du //
NK131(do)001:3477: gang phrad de la chog mi bzung //
NK131(do)001:3479: rgyud rtsod pa can de lta bu la bsten par mi bya'o //
NK131(do)001:3480: gang la bsten na rgyal ba'i bka' yin nges pa /
NK131(do)001:3481: pan+di ta mkhas pas bdag gir bzung ba /
NK131(do)001:3482: lo ts+aa ba mkhas pas bsgyur ba /
NK131(do)001:3483: tshig 'brel dang don 'grel gyi bshad bka' ma nub pa rnams la 'jug par bya /
NK131(do)001:3484: chos kyang rtsod pa can btags grol dang thos grol
NK131(do)001:3485: dang myong grol dang zhag bdun gyi sangs rgyas 'grub
NK131(do)001:3486: par grags pa'i zab zab mo dag la blo mi
NK131(do)001:3488: smin grol gyi lam cha lag tshang ba /
NK131(do)001:3490: rtsod pa med par grub pa rnam dag gi rgyud sde zhig la bstan pa /
NK131(do)001:3491: ngo bo snyan brgyud kyi phyag bzhes ma chad pa zhig la 'jug par bya /
NK131(do)001:3492: lam nyams su blang ba'i rtags kyang 'ja' dang ring bsrel lta bu la bskyel so mi bya ste /
NK131(do)001:3493: gang la bskyel so byed na lam rtags sems la rdzogs pa /
NK131(do)001:3494: spangs bya nyon mongs dri ba /
NK131(do)001:3495: thob bya zad par dang sa lam gyi rtags rim
NK131(do)001:3496: pa can du shar ba rnams kyi mtshams phyed par
NK131(do)001:3497: bya'o // zhes bka' stsal ba la /
NK131(do)001:3498: pan chen thams cad mkhyen pa bus gsang ba 'dus pa'i bshad thabs las /
NK131(do)001:3499: rnal 'byor gyi rgyud nas gsungs pa'i de nyid bcu
NK131(do)001:3500: la phyi'i de nyid bcu ru bshad pa'i rigs pas
NK131(do)001:3501: rnal 'byor gyi rgyud man chad phyi yin la /
NK131(do)001:3502: khro bo bcu lta bu bsrung 'khor bsgom pas phyir bzlog pa dang /
NK131(do)001:3503: bris pa'i bsrung 'khor gyi phyir bzlog pa dang /
NK131(do)001:3505: shes rab ye shes kyi dbang bskur dang /
NK131(do)001:3506: kha sbyor dbye ba'i cho gas dgra bsad pa dang /
NK131(do)001:3509: ma grub na spog pa'i cho ga drag shul lam
NK131(do)001:3510: btsan thabs kyi sgrub pa ste de rnams gsang ba'i
NK131(do)001:3511: de kho na nyid bcur bshad pa'i rig pas /
NK131(do)001:3512: de rnams ston pa'i rgyud ni gsang ba'am nang yin
NK131(do)001:3513: pas rnal 'byor bla med kyi rgyud ni nang yin
NK131(do)001:3514: no // zhes gsang ba'i de nyid bcu bris pa'i
NK131(do)001:3515: bsrung ba'i 'khor los phyir bzlog pa sogs kyi khyad
NK131(do)001:3516: par 'phags pa'i dbye bas rnal 'byor bla med du
NK131(do)001:3518: gsang ba'i theg pa 'dir yang bris pa'i 'khor lo
NK131(do)001:3519: dang glegs bam la sogs pa bcangs pas grol bar
NK131(do)001:3520: 'gyur bas rgyud sde gzhan dag las khyad par du
NK131(do)001:3522: de la gsang sngags gsar ma na btags grol med pa yang ma yin te /
NK131(do)001:3524: bram ze chen po gang la la zhig gi rig
NK131(do)001:3525: pa'i rgyal mo so sor 'brangs ma chen mo 'di
NK131(do)001:3526: cho ga bzhin du bris te /
NK131(do)001:3527: lag pa'am mgul du btags na /
NK131(do)001:3528: de de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi byin gyis brlabs par rig par bya'o //
NK131(do)001:3529: de de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi skur rig par bya'o //
NK131(do)001:3530: de de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi ring bsrel gyi snying po can yin par rig par bya'o //
NK131(do)001:3531: de de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi spyan yin par rig par bya'o //
NK131(do)001:3532: de rdo rje chen po'i lus su rig par bya'o //
NK131(do)001:3533: de 'bar ba 'od 'phro ba'i lus dang ldan par rig par bya'o //
NK131(do)001:3534: de mi bshig pa'i go cha can du rig par bya'o //
NK131(do)001:3535: de dgra thams cad rab tu 'joms par rig par bya'o //
NK131(do)001:3536: sgrib pa thams cad rab tu 'joms par rig par bya'o //
NK131(do)001:3537: de sems can dmyal ba'i 'gro ba rnam par sbyong bar rig par bya'o //
NK131(do)001:3538: zhes btags pas grol ba'i tshul gsungs nas /
NK131(do)001:3539: de brtags pas ji ltar grol ba yang /
NK131(do)001:3540: dge slong sdig to can de bzhin gshegs pa'i bslabs
NK131(do)001:3541: pa dang bral zhing dge 'dun gyi dkor 'phrog pa
NK131(do)001:3542: zhig nad tshabs chen pos btab sdug bsngal chen po'i
NK131(do)001:3544: mgon skyabs dang dpung gnyen med de ku co'i sgra 'byin pa zhig la /
NK131(do)001:3545: dge bsnyen zhig gis so sor 'brangs mi bris te de'i mgul du btags pas /
NK131(do)001:3546: de ma thag tu sdug bsngal thams cad rab tu zhi ste /
NK131(do)001:3547: de'i mtshan mo zad pa dang dran pa shin tu
NK131(do)001:3548: nye bar bzhag pas shi ste mnar med pa'i dmyal
NK131(do)001:3549: bar skyes so // de'i ro de dge slong dag
NK131(do)001:3550: gi sgang bu zhig la bzhag nas so sor 'brangs
NK131(do)001:3551: ma yang de'i mgul na btags bzhin par yod do
NK131(do)001:3552: bar skyes so // // dge slong med par skyes
NK131(do)001:3553: ma thag tu dmyal ba'i sems can thams cad kyi
NK131(do)001:3554: sdug bsngal thams cad rab tu zhi nas bde ba
NK131(do)001:3555: thams cad kyi tshim par gyur /
NK131(do)001:3556: me'i phung po thams cad kyang zhi zhing /
NK131(do)001:3559: ral gri lo ma'i nags kyi bcad gtubs la sogs pa yang zhi /
NK131(do)001:3560: shal ma ri yang chag pa dang /
NK131(do)001:3561: dmyal srung rnams ngo mtshar nas chos kyi rgyal po gshin rje la dris pa dang /
NK131(do)001:3563: de yi tshe rabs lnga lus che //
NK131(do)001:3564: ji ltar sku gdung rgyan mang pos //
NK131(do)001:3565: ston pa'i mchod rten mdzes pa ltar //
NK131(do)001:3566: so sor 'brangs ma mgul btags pas //
NK131(do)001:3567: de yi lus ni de bzhin mdzes //
NK131(do)001:3569: so sor 'brangs ma'i don bris pas /
NK131(do)001:3570: gang gi tshig rnams so sor dran //
NK131(do)001:3572: so sor 'brangs ma bsgom pa ni //
NK131(do)001:3574: sems can dmyal ba'i srung ma khyed //
NK131(do)001:3575: rab tu rgyan dang ldan par deng //
NK131(do)001:3576: der ni sgang bu mthon po la //
NK131(do)001:3577: lha rnams kyis ni bskor ba ltos //
NK131(do)001:3578: de mthong sems can thams cad la //
NK131(do)001:3579: byams pa'i sems su 'gyur bar gyis //
NK131(do)001:3580: de nas gshin rje'i mi de dag /
NK131(do)001:3581: de nub rgyas dang ldan par song //
NK131(do)001:3582: de tshe der ni de dag gi //
NK131(do)001:3583: rgyal po'i pho brang nye ba na //
NK131(do)001:3584: sgang bu de yi khor yug na //
NK131(do)001:3585: 'bar ba yi ni gang bar mthong //
NK131(do)001:3586: mi ro gcig gi mgul pa na //
NK131(do)001:3587: so sor 'brangs ma btags pa mthong //
NK131(do)001:3588: lha dang klu dang dri za dang //
NK131(do)001:3589: gnod sbyin srin po mi'am ci //
NK131(do)001:3590: kun nas 'khor bar bskor nas ni //
NK131(do)001:3591: bla na med pa'i mchod pa byed //
NK131(do)001:3592: de la gnod sbyin de dag gi //
NK131(do)001:3593: so sor 'brangs ma'i sgong zhes btags //
NK131(do)001:3594: de nas gnod sbyin de dag gi chos kyi rgyal
NK131(do)001:3595: po gshin rje'i nges pa de rtogs te slar log
NK131(do)001:3596: nas / lha khyod kyi bka' stsal pa zhes pa nas rgyas par brjod do //
NK131(do)001:3597: de nas smras ma thag tu tshig de skad smras
NK131(do)001:3598: pa'i tha ma la sems can chen po de sems
NK131(do)001:3599: can dmyal ba'i lus bor nas sum cu rtsa gsum
NK131(do)001:3600: pa'i lha rnams kyi nang du skyes so //
NK131(do)001:3601: zhes rgya cher gsungs pas na ming btags grol du ma btags kyang /
NK131(do)001:3602: don la mtshungs pa nyid do //
NK131(do)001:3603: gzhan yang 'khor lo lus la rtag tu bcangs pas grol ba nyid du ma zad /
NK131(do)001:3604: pad+mo sh+nisha'i gzungs kyi 'og tu lan cig 'dzul bas
NK131(do)001:3605: tshe rabs 'bum du bsags pa'i las kyi sgrib pa
NK131(do)001:3606: 'byang bar gsungs pa la sogs pa mtha' yas shing
NK131(do)001:3607: / so sor 'brangs ma btags pa'i dge slong de
NK131(do)001:3608: sdug bsngal las grol te 'chi ba'i dus byas nas
NK131(do)001:3609: / / dmyal ba'i gnas kyi sems can rnams kyi
NK131(do)001:3610: sdug bsngal thams cad kyang zhi bar byas nas slar
NK131(do)001:3611: lha ru skyes par gsungs pa'i rig pa 'dis /
NK131(do)001:3612: btags grol gyi byin rlabs lus 'di dang lhan dus su'ang 'byung la /
NK131(do)001:3613: lus bor ba'i rjes su'ang 'byung ba nyid du gsal bar bstan to //
NK131(do)001:3614: gzhan yang jo bo chen po rje'i lugs kyi ngan song sgo gcod kyi 'khor lo dang /
NK131(do)001:3615: rdo rje gdan dang gnas chen brgyad kyi bkod pa'i
NK131(do)001:3616: khyad par de gang gi lus la bcangs pa de
NK131(do)001:3617: nyid kyi byang chub nges par thob pa'i tshul dang
NK131(do)001:3618: / grong khyer sgrol 'khor zhes pa grong khyer gcig
NK131(do)001:3619: na 'khor lo de yod na grong khyer ba thams
NK131(do)001:3620: cad 'khor ba las bsgral te thar pa thob par
NK131(do)001:3622: rje dam pa rgya gar gyi lugs kyi zhi byed
NK131(do)001:3623: du'ang 'khor lo de nyid mthong thos dran reg tu
NK131(do)001:3624: gyur pa'am / gang gi bcangs de'i lus la rlung
NK131(do)001:3625: phog pa'i ser bus phog pa dang khrus byas pa'i
NK131(do)001:3626: chu 'thung pa thams cad kyang grol bar gsungs pa
NK131(do)001:3627: gyur pa'am / yod do // gzhan yang gtsug gtor rnam rgyal gyi gzungs las /
NK131(do)001:3628: lha'i dbang po dge slong ngam /
NK131(do)001:3632: de las gzhan pa gang la la dag gi gzungs
NK131(do)001:3633: 'di bris te rgyal mtshan gyi rtse mor btags na
NK131(do)001:3635: de dang nye bar gnas par gyur tam /
NK131(do)001:3636: tha na de'i grib mas phog gam /
NK131(do)001:3637: de'i rdul rlung gi khyer ba phog na yang /
NK131(do)001:3639: sems can de dag la sdig pa thams cad dang
NK131(do)001:3640: ngan 'gror 'gro ba'i 'jig pa mtha' dag mi 'byung
NK131(do)001:3641: ngo // sems can dmyal ba dang /
NK131(do)001:3644: yi dwags dang lha ma yin gyi rigs thams cad du mi skye bar rig par bya'o //
NK131(do)001:3645: lha'i dbang po sems can de dag ni de bzhin
NK131(do)001:3646: gshegs pas lung bstan zhing bla na med pa yang
NK131(do)001:3647: dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub las phyir mi bzlog
NK131(do)001:3650: ngan song thams cad yongs su sbyong ba'i brtag pa las kyang de ltar du gsungs so //
NK131(do)001:3651: de ltar de rnams nas bcangs pa'am btags pas grol bar gsungs pas na /
NK131(do)001:3652: btags pas mi grol ba'i shes byed ma grub pa yin no //
NK131(do)001:3653: yang bcom ldan 'das ni dang po nyid du sangs rgyas pa yin kyang /
NK131(do)001:3654: bye ba brgyad cur rgyal ba nyid //
NK131(do)001:3655: sangs rgyas nyid du bstan gyur kyang //
NK131(do)001:3656: da dung chog pa'i 'du shes bsal //
NK131(do)001:3657: byang chub mchog tu thugs kyang 'jug /
NK131(do)001:3658: ces pa la sogs pas gdul bya'i ngor mdzad pa
NK131(do)001:3659: sna tshogs pa ston pas na la lar dka' ba
NK131(do)001:3660: spyod pa dang / la lar grangs med gsum du tshogs bsag pa'i tshul dang /
NK131(do)001:3664: 'khor ba spangs nas gzhan du ni //
NK131(do)001:3665: mya ngan 'das pa yod ma yin //
NK131(do)001:3666: zhes 'khor 'das gnyis su med pa'i don gyis sangs
NK131(do)001:3667: rgyas pa nyid dka' ba med par ston pa la
NK131(do)001:3668: sogs pa sangs rgyas kyi rnam par rol pa mtha'
NK131(do)001:3669: yas pa ston pa'i thabs la mkhas pa de'i phyir
NK131(do)001:3670: rang nyid btags grol 'chad pa la ma ltos mod
NK131(do)001:3671: kyang / sems can rnam par grol ba'i drung du
NK131(do)001:3672: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi btags grol la
NK131(do)001:3673: sogs pa'i rigs sngags zab cing rgya che ba mtha'
NK131(do)001:3674: yas pa nyid ston par mdzad pa yin no //
NK131(do)001:3675: 'phags pa dkon mchog brtsegs pa las /
NK131(do)001:3679: rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba'i mthu ni bsam gyis mi khyab bo //
NK131(do)001:3680: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi thabs dang ting 'dzin dang /
NK131(do)001:3681: rdzu 'phrul gyi spyod yul ni bsam gyis mi khyab pa'o //
NK131(do)001:3683: de ltar grol ba'i ltas su 'ja' dang ring bsrel
NK131(do)001:3684: la sogs pa 'byung bar 'di'i rgyud rnams na bshad
NK131(do)001:3685: cing jo bo chen po'i bka' gdams glegs bam du
NK131(do)001:3686: yang / phyi ltas nam mkha' dang ba yin //
NK131(do)001:3687: tshul khrims gtsang ba me tog 'bab //
NK131(do)001:3688: byang chub sems dpa' la ring bsrel 'dzag /
NK131(do)001:3689: bskyed rim can la lha sku 'byon //
NK131(do)001:3690: khrims gtsang phung po gtsang ma ste //
NK131(do)001:3691: lha rnams kun gyis bsu bar byed //
NK131(do)001:3692: phyir mi'i sdom pa dung 'khyil te //
NK131(do)001:3693: 'khor ba mi spong sems dpa' la //
NK131(do)001:3694: thugs dang ljag ni 'byon par bshad //
NK131(do)001:3695: spyir ni dam pa gshegs pa la //
NK131(do)001:3697: gnas lugs snga ltas sprin med yin //
NK131(do)001:3698: de ni thun mongs snga ltas tsam //
NK131(do)001:3700: btags grol la sogs pa'i byin rlabs kyi mthu las
NK131(do)001:3701: byung bas 'di dag /'byung ba rkyen tshogs pa la
NK131(do)001:3702: sogs pa las byung ba'i 'ja' dang /
NK131(do)001:3703: bdud kyi cho 'phrul las byung ba'i 'ja' dang ring bsrel ma yin no //
NK131(do)001:3704: btags grol la gdungs dang ring bsrel nges par 'byung ba yang /
NK131(do)001:3705: sha ri ram chu ri ram /
NK131(do)001:3706: ba ri ram dang nya ri ram /
NK131(do)001:3707: pan tsa ram dang lnga ldan gsungs //
NK131(do)001:3708: rig lnga'i gdung ste sku yang 'byung //
NK131(do)001:3709: 'di rnams sku thob rtags yin nam //
NK131(do)001:3710: gsungs thob rtag tu me 'od sgra //
NK131(do)001:3711: 'ja' tshon nam mkha' dang gsal ba //
NK131(do)001:3712: nges pa thugs thob rtags yin no //
NK131(do)001:3714: 'di'i grol tshul gang zag phal ba dag la yang /
NK131(do)001:3715: dbang po rnams lnga 'on gyur cig /
NK131(do)001:3716: rgan gzhon pho mo dge sdig med //
NK131(do)001:3717: bag chags bzang ngan med pa ru //
NK131(do)001:3719: zhes bya ba ni rgyud mtha' drug tshul bzhis sbas pas don yin la /
NK131(do)001:3720: man ngag ltar na rang rang gi bsags pa dang mthun pa'i grol lugs tha dad pa yin te /
NK131(do)001:3721: myong grol la sogs pa la yang mtshungs so //
NK131(do)001:3723: e ma rang byung ye shes 'di //
NK131(do)001:3724: sems can gzhan gyi don byed na //
NK131(do)001:3726: mgul du btags te bsregs na ni //
NK131(do)001:3727: 'di yi grol bar smos ci dgos //
NK131(do)001:3728: mtshams med lnga po spyad pa yang //
NK131(do)001:3729: nyan thos rnams dang skal ba mnyam //
NK131(do)001:3730: yid dpyod 'dzin pa'i lta ba yang //
NK131(do)001:3731: rdo rje 'chang dang mnyam par nges //
NK131(do)001:3732: 'di nyid bcangs pa'i skyes bu ni //
NK131(do)001:3733: gang na 'dug pa'i sa phyogs kyang //
NK131(do)001:3734: ngan song dag las grol bar 'gyur //
NK131(do)001:3735: mchog dang thun mong dngos grub thob //
NK131(do)001:3736: rig pa dngos kyi rtags yod pa'i //
NK131(do)001:3737: skyes bu de la bsreg mi dgos //
NK131(do)001:3739: zhes pas gang zag rab rnams grol gzhi chos sku'i dbyings su grol /
NK131(do)001:3740: 'bring rnams rang snang longs sku'i zhing du grol /
NK131(do)001:3741: tha ma rang bzhin sprul pa sku'i zhing du grol
NK131(do)001:3742: ba gsum ni lam dang lam dang ldan pa'i rnal
NK131(do)001:3743: 'byor pa rnams kyi grol tshul yin la /
NK131(do)001:3744: skye bo phal pa rnams ni ngan 'gro'i skye gnas
NK131(do)001:3745: las grol nas mir skyes te chos kyi sgor zhugs
NK131(do)001:3746: nas rim gyi grol bar bshad pa yin te /
NK131(do)001:3747: mtshams med lnga byas pa nyan thos su skye bar len pa la sogs pa gsungs shing /
NK131(do)001:3749: sgrib pa thams cad rab tu bcom par rig par bya'o //
NK131(do)001:3750: zhes sgrib bral du bstan pa ni gang zag rab rnams la dgongs pa yin la /
NK131(do)001:3751: de sems can dmyal ba'i 'gro ba rnam par sbyang bar rig par bya'o //
NK131(do)001:3753: cho ga bzhin du lus la btags nas bcang bar bya ste /
NK131(do)001:3754: de rtag tu sdug bsngal shing nyams thag pa thams cad las yongs su thar bar 'gyur /
NK131(do)001:3755: ngan 'gror 'gro ba'i 'jigs shing skrag pa thams cad las brgal bar 'gyur /
NK131(do)001:3756: zhes pa gsungs pa nyid kyi shes so //
NK131(do)001:3757: de ltar btags nas dge sdig gnyis ka 'phel che bas sdig pa phra mo yang spangs dgos te /
NK131(do)001:3759: tshes brgyad nya rgyal 'dzoms pa la //
NK131(do)001:3760: rab gnas byas te btags par bya //
NK131(do)001:3761: des na dge sdig gnyis ka ni //
NK131(do)001:3763: dge ba grub tshad sems can don //
NK131(do)001:3764: 'bad pas skye med sgrub par bya //
NK131(do)001:3765: sdig pa shin tu phra yang 'dzem //
NK131(do)001:3766: 'di phrad ngan song ltung mi srid //
NK131(do)001:3768: 'di btags pas grol ba thob ste rtags dang mtshan
NK131(do)001:3769: ma byung ba'i lo rgyus mang du yod na yang
NK131(do)001:3770: yi ges 'jigs pas ma bris so //
NK131(do)001:3771: tshong 'dus phag rin bshan pa mgyogs pa'i phul du phyin pas ri dwags la sbar zin thongs pa /
NK131(do)001:3773: mi dge ba 'ba' zhig spyod pa zhig yod pa de nam zhig 'chi ba'i nad kyi thebs nas /
NK131(do)001:3774: zhag nyi shu rtsa bzhi'i bar du chu yang khar mi 'gro /
NK131(do)001:3775: zung rngu drag pos rkang lag dang lus sa la rdeb cing /
NK131(do)001:3776: gnod gcod kyi 'jig skrag gi snang bas skad ngan 'don pa zhig la /
NK131(do)001:3777: phyogs kyi bla ma mkhas btsun bzang gsum dang /
NK131(do)001:3778: rnal 'byor pa bzang zer tshad der byung ba rnams kyi ma phan /
NK131(do)001:3779: bla ma mthu chen rgya mtshos skye bdun byin /
NK131(do)001:3780: btags grol btags pas de ma thag shi ste ro la 'ja' zug /
NK131(do)001:3781: phung po sregs pas me tog gi char dang gdung ring bsrel mang po byung /
NK131(do)001:3782: rje btsun tsong kha pas sne gdong rtser btags grol dang myong grol la dgag pa mdzad pas /
NK131(do)001:3783: kun mkhyen sangs rgyas rong pas zhol gyi khyi 'chi la nye ba zhig la mthong grol bstan /
NK131(do)001:3785: btags grol btags te shi ba dang sregs pas 'ja'
NK131(do)001:3786: dang khyi'i rus pa phal cher gdung ring bsrel du
NK131(do)001:3787: mang po byung / kar+m+aa pa chos grags rgya mtsho'i
NK131(do)001:3788: dngos slob kong po dpal ldan rgya mtsho'i dbon po
NK131(do)001:3789: dug gi shi dus bla ma 'brug grags pas dgongs
NK131(do)001:3790: pa zang thal dang kun bzang dgongs 'dus kyi btags
NK131(do)001:3791: grol gyi dbang ro la bskur nas sreg pas 'ja'
NK131(do)001:3792: 'od dang gdung rigs lnga byung ba sogs /
NK131(do)001:3793: lo rgyus shin tu mang ba yod pa yin no //
NK131(do)001:3795: srid pa'i rtsa ba bdag 'dzin nyid //
NK131(do)001:3796: phyi nang kun brtags ye stong grol //
NK131(do)001:3797: stong gsal mdangs lnga'i sgo phye ste //
NK131(do)001:3798: ti la gsal stong mtha' bral nyid //
NK131(do)001:3799: rkyen med rtsol bral lhug par bzhag /
NK131(do)001:3800: ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje gsum //
NK131(do)001:3801: btags grol nyid du sangs rgya'o //
NK131(do)001:3803: 'khor ba 'di bdag tu 'dzin pa las byung zhing /
NK131(do)001:3804: de'i ngo bo la phyi nang kun tu legs par brtags pa na /
NK131(do)001:3805: gang du yang ma grub pa'i ye stong blo bral chen po'i ngo bor grol ba yin la /
NK131(do)001:3806: de'i ngang nas btags grol don khrid du bshad pa ltar snang ba bzhi la rtsal sbyangs te /
NK131(do)001:3807: khregs chod dang thod rgal zung 'jug tu nyams su
NK131(do)001:3808: blangs pas ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje gsum dbyer
NK131(do)001:3809: med pa'i sangs rgyas su grol ba yang bshad pa
NK131(do)001:3811: de la ni glegs bam ma bcangs kyang don rtogs
NK131(do)001:3812: pas grol bar mkha' 'gro'i snying thig la sogs par
NK131(do)001:3813: bshad do // chos rtsod pa can thos grol dang /
NK131(do)001:3814: zhag bdun gyi sangs rgyas 'grub par grags pa dag la blo mi 'gel ces pa yang /
NK131(do)001:3815: gang zag gi phye ba yin la /
NK131(do)001:3816: chos kyi phye ba ma yin te /
NK131(do)001:3817: phyag rgya chen po pa'i gang zag dam pa bram
NK131(do)001:3818: ze chen po lta bu mda' mkhan ma'i snyugs ma'i
NK131(do)001:3819: brdas / skad cig grol ba dang /
NK131(do)001:3820: rgyal po sa ka ra gdams ngag thos pa tsam gyi mod la grol ba sogs mang zhing /
NK131(do)001:3821: gtum mo zhag bdun ma dang /
NK131(do)001:3822: snyan brgyud zhag bdun ma dang /
NK131(do)001:3823: mthu zhag bdun ma la sogs pa gsang sngags gsar
NK131(do)001:3824: ma pa dag la yang grags pas mtshungs pa nyid
NK131(do)001:3825: do // sa lam gyi rtags rim pa can du shar bas mtshams phyed par bya zhes pa yang /
NK131(do)001:3826: ye shes snang ba rgyan gyi mdo las /
NK131(do)001:3827: rgyu rkyen 'brel par bshad pa dang //
NK131(do)001:3828: rim pas 'jug par bstan pa yang //
NK131(do)001:3829: rmongs pa rnams la thabs su gsungs //
NK131(do)001:3830: lhun gyis grub pa'i chos 'di la //
NK131(do)001:3831: rim pas sbyangs su ci zhig yod //
NK131(do)001:3834: phyag rgya chen po chig chod la //
NK131(do)001:3835: sa lam brtsi ba rmongs pa 'khrul //
NK131(do)001:3836: ces pa la sogs pa'i don gyis ma nges pa yin no //
NK131(do)001:3838: brgyud pa yang dpe brgyud dang gter brgyud sogs la ngo mtshar bar mi bzung ste /
NK131(do)001:3839: rdo rje 'chang nas rim par pha nor bu la
NK131(do)001:3840: gtad pas bka' brgyud kyi chu bo ma nub pa
NK131(do)001:3841: / byin rlabs kyi brgyud pa ma chad pa zhig la gtugs par bya'o //
NK131(do)001:3843: de la gter zhes bya ba rnying ma ba kho
NK131(do)001:3844: na las gzhan du mi 'byung ba ma yin te
NK131(do)001:3845: / bsod nams thams cad sdud pa ting nge 'dzin gyi mdo las /
NK131(do)001:3846: dri ma med pa'i gzi brjid /
NK131(do)001:3847: chos 'dod pa'i byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen
NK131(do)001:3848: po bsam pa phun sum tshogs pa gus pa dang
NK131(do)001:3849: bcas pa rnams ni 'jig rten gyi khams gzhan na
NK131(do)001:3850: 'dug kyang sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams kyi zhal
NK131(do)001:3851: ston cing chos kyang thos par mdzad la /
NK131(do)001:3852: dri ma med pa'i gzi brjid chos 'dod pa'i byang
NK131(do)001:3853: chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po rnams kyi chos
NK131(do)001:3854: kyi gter ri dang ri sul dang shing gi nang
NK131(do)001:3855: na bzhugs pa dag yod do //
NK131(do)001:3856: gzungs dang chos kyi sgo mtha' yas pa glegs bam
NK131(do)001:3857: du byas pa dag kyang lag tu 'ong bar gyur
NK131(do)001:3858: ro // zhes gsungs pas las dang skal bar ldan
NK131(do)001:3859: pa'i gang zag la gnas nges pa med pa dag
NK131(do)001:3860: las chos kyi bdud rtsi 'byung ba yin no //
NK131(do)001:3861: de ltar gsar ma pa rnams la gter gyi rnam grangs kyang /
NK131(do)001:3862: theg chen gyi mdo mang po rgya gar yul na
NK131(do)001:3863: sbas pa dge slong nir ban rak+shi tas phyungs pa
NK131(do)001:3864: dang / ma h+aa ma ya'i rgyud nub phyogs u rgyan nas ku ku ri pas phyungs pa dang /
NK131(do)001:3865: gtsug gtor gdugs dkar la sogs pa'i rgyal mtshan bya
NK131(do)001:3866: ba'i cho ga'i rim pa rgya gar lho phyogs b+he
NK131(do)001:3867: ta pad+mo can gyi gtsug lag khang nas jo bo
NK131(do)001:3868: chen po rjes phyungs pa dang /
NK131(do)001:3869: rdzogs rims rlung sems dbyer med rdo rje gdan nas rje btsun mar pas phyungs pa dang /
NK131(do)001:3870: mkha' 'gro ma seng+ge'i gdong can gyi sgrub sgor rdo
NK131(do)001:3871: rje gdan gyi shar phyogs pha bong g.yag 'dra ba'i
NK131(do)001:3872: 'og nas bla ma rdo rje gdan pa dang /
NK131(do)001:3873: ba ri lo ts+aa bas phyungs pa dang /
NK131(do)001:3874: ku ru kul+le'i sgrub thabs thun mong ma yin pa
NK131(do)001:3875: rdo rje gdan gyi byang phyogs lha mo dud sol
NK131(do)001:3876: ma'i nu 'bur na yod pa sgrol mas lung bstan
NK131(do)001:3877: te bla ma gnyan lo ts+aa bas gter nas phyungs
NK131(do)001:3878: pa yin te / de'i lo rgyus las /
NK131(do)001:3879: bla ma gnyan lo ts+aa ba 'di snyam du //
NK131(do)001:3880: lo ts+aa ba mang yang nga lta bu'i mkhas pa med /
NK131(do)001:3881: pan+di ta mang yang 'bum phrag gsum pa lta bu'i mkhas pa med /
NK131(do)001:3882: ngas rgya mtsho matha'i skad shes pas /
NK131(do)001:3883: de'i mgo 'don du 'bum phrag gsum pa bod du gdan 'dren dgos te /
NK131(do)001:3885: nga yo byad chung ba dang /
NK131(do)001:3886: rgya bod gnyis lam thag ring ba dang /
NK131(do)001:3887: de'i stobs kyi zhu 'bul dka' bas ngas sngags kyis
NK131(do)001:3888: dbang du bsdus la bod du gdan 'drongs par bya'o
NK131(do)001:3889: snyam ste sgrol ma la gsol ba btab pas rmi
NK131(do)001:3890: lam du bud med gzhon nu ma gcig byung nas
NK131(do)001:3891: / rdo rje gdan gyi byang phyogs kyi lha mo
NK131(do)001:3892: ku ru kal+le'i lder bzo'i 'og na de'i sgrub thabs
NK131(do)001:3893: yod pas de thon la nyams su longs shig gsung
NK131(do)001:3894: / / de ltar byas pas bud med dbang du bsdus thabs gcig las ma byung /
NK131(do)001:3895: pan+di ta dbang du bsdu dgos pa la 'dis mi phan snyam nas yang gsol ba btab pas /
NK131(do)001:3896: yang rnal lam du sgrol ma'i zhal nas /
NK131(do)001:3897: de bas kyang gting ring du brus dang /
NK131(do)001:3898: de na ral gcig ma'i ldir gzo so phag las byas pa'i khru gang ba zhig yod /
NK131(do)001:3900: yang de bzhin du byas pas dul gyi ga'u kha
NK131(do)001:3901: sbyar gcig nang dngul gyi bris pa'i rgyal po dang
NK131(do)001:3902: btsun mor bcas pa dbang du sdud pa'i thabs byung
NK131(do)001:3904: pan+di ta dbang du bsdu dgos snyam nas gsol ba btab pas /
NK131(do)001:3906: nub gsum nga la gsol ba thob la /
NK131(do)001:3907: sngar gyi de'i 'og na mar gting ring du brus dang /
NK131(do)001:3908: lha mo dul sol ma srin mo mche ba gtsigs pa 'dra ba zhig yod kyi /
NK131(do)001:3909: de la 'jigs pa med par nga la gsol ba thob /
NK131(do)001:3911: sangs rgyas chos dbyings rnam par gshegs //
NK131(do)001:3912: bde sdug rtog pa mi mnga' bas //
NK131(do)001:3913: gang yang khyod la gos pa med //
NK131(do)001:3914: slar yang gzugs skus 'gro don mdzod //
NK131(do)001:3916: mi rkang gi tsha tshal pa dri bzangs kyi chus
NK131(do)001:3917: byug pa la lha mo'i nu ma g.yon pa'i steng
NK131(do)001:3918: na yi ge h+r+aihzhiga yod kyi de ma chag par
NK131(do)001:3919: brkos la de lha mo'i spyi bor zhog /
NK131(do)001:3920: de'i shul du bskos la de nas byung ba ltar gyis /
NK131(do)001:3921: de thon pa dang ltas dang cho 'phrul sna tshogs
NK131(do)001:3922: yong bas nga la de'i dus su mos gus gyis
NK131(do)001:3925: gos mgo mjug bzlog la phyir nur byed cing ngag tu hring hring zhes zer gyin shog /
NK131(do)001:3926: de ltar byas na 'khor lo lus la bcangs pa tsam gyi dbang du 'du /
NK131(do)001:3928: de dus lha 'dres par chod 'ong bas /
NK131(do)001:3929: pan+di ta phrag dog can rnams kyi ngan sngags byas bsad du 'ong bas zon bya dgos /
NK131(do)001:3930: de ltar gyis gsung pa ltar byas pas /
NK131(do)001:3931: dpal mo gser gyi snying thag can gyi sgrub thabs gter nas thon /
NK131(do)001:3932: bsnyen sgrub byas pas pan+di ta 'bum phrag gsum pa
NK131(do)001:3933: dbang du gyur nas bod du gdan drangs pa'i lo
NK131(do)001:3934: rgyus snang zhing / bod du yang chos rgyal srong btsan sgam po'i bka' chems shog dril ma /
NK131(do)001:3935: blon po'i bka' chems zla ba 'dod 'jo /
NK131(do)001:3936: btsun mo'i bka' chems dar dkar gsal ba la sogs dang /
NK131(do)001:3937: lha sa'i dkar chag rnams ka ba bum pa can du sbas nas yod pa la /
NK131(do)001:3938: jo bo'i dgongs pa la gtsug lag khang 'di ji
NK131(do)001:3939: ltar bzhengs pa'i lo rgyus cig 'ong thang ba la
NK131(do)001:3940: dgongs pa'i tshe / lha sa mi'i rten can gyi
NK131(do)001:3941: mkha' 'gro ma zhig yod pa des jo bo la
NK131(do)001:3942: dgongs pa'i tshe / lung bstan te / spyan snga
NK131(do)001:3943: rnal 'byor pas lag cha thogs te gter nas phyungs
NK131(do)001:3944: dgongs pa'i tshe / lung bstan te / / 'di
NK131(do)001:3945: la bdag po shin tu gnyan pa cig 'dug pas
NK131(do)001:3947: gung thang lo ts+aa ba tshul khrims rgyal ba la
NK131(do)001:3948: sogs pa mi gsum gyi bris nas slar yang ka
NK131(do)001:3949: ba'i khong seng du phyi mo rnams sbas so zhes
NK131(do)001:3950: rnam thar chen mo na snang zhing /
NK131(do)001:3951: 'brom gyi mdzad pa'i bstod par yang /
NK131(do)001:3952: gang du rgyal po'i bka' chems gter du sbas //
NK131(do)001:3953: mkha' 'gro'i gter khungs khyed la bstan pa las //
NK131(do)001:3955: kha che'i pan+di ta chen po sh+aakya sh+r+ai b+ha dras
NK131(do)001:3956: kyang chos rgyal gyi bka' chems skor 'ga' zhig gter
NK131(do)001:3958: phan gnod las tshogs kyi skor rnams ka ba shing lo can /
NK131(do)001:3961: seng mgo can rnams na yod pa /
NK131(do)001:3963: jo gdan dkon mchog grags gnyis kyi 'ga' re phyungs shing /
NK131(do)001:3964: shas che ni gter na bzhugs pa nyid do //
NK131(do)001:3965: gzhan yang ro snyoms skor drug ni /
NK131(do)001:3966: ti bu bas rgya gar 'o ma'i rgya mtsho na /
NK131(do)001:3967: gdam ngag mar gyi snying po 'di //
NK131(do)001:3968: rgyud sde rnams na gab nas yod //
NK131(do)001:3969: pan+di ta yi long gtam byas //
NK131(do)001:3970: grub thob rnams kyi khong snying yin //
NK131(do)001:3971: dur khrod 'grims pa'i go cha yin //
NK131(do)001:3972: ku su lu pa'i sman sbyor yin //
NK131(do)001:3973: n+aa ro pan chen gyi rtogs pa yin //
NK131(do)001:3974: pan+di ta dang ku su lu //
NK131(do)001:3976: snod ldan khyod la bstan pa yin //
NK131(do)001:3977: gdams ngag bshad la dus tshod dgos //
NK131(do)001:3978: da lta bstan pa'i dus min pas //
NK131(do)001:3980: gtad gnyer gyis la gter du sbos //
NK131(do)001:3981: skye ba gsum gyi 'og rol du //
NK131(do)001:3982: snod ldan gang zag lan du 'ong //
NK131(do)001:3983: de'i lag tu gtad cig gyis //
NK131(do)001:3984: smon lam thob la sbos shig gsungs //
NK131(do)001:3985: zhes pa ltar ras chung bas lho brag mkhar chur sbas pa /
NK131(do)001:3986: phyis 'gro mgon gtsangs pa rgya ras kyi gter nas phyungs pa dang /
NK131(do)001:3987: sems khrid yid bzhin nor bu rje sgom po pa
NK131(do)001:3988: dang skyes bu ye shes rdo rjes mtsho man+dala nag
NK131(do)001:3989: po la gter du sbas pa /
NK131(do)001:3990: dung mtsho ras pas gter nas phyungs pa dang /
NK131(do)001:3991: rje mar pa lo ts+aa ba chen po'i chos drug
NK131(do)001:3992: sras mkhar ma nyid kyi phyag gi srin lag las
NK131(do)001:3993: khrag phyungs te bris nas mkhar gyi bya phug la
NK131(do)001:3994: sbas pa mi rab bdun nas 'don pa'i kha byang
NK131(do)001:3995: yod pa / mar pa'i sras dge 'dun gyi seng 'bro rin chen dbang phyug la gtad /
NK131(do)001:3996: de nas bla ma gyang gsar pa la byung ste /
NK131(do)001:3997: de'i sras rgyal tsha'i lag nas gu ru chos dbang
NK131(do)001:3998: gi phyag tu byung ste gter nas phyung pa dang
NK131(do)001:3999: / chos rgyal gyi blon po lha bzang skyid dpal
NK131(do)001:4000: gyi rnam thos sras drag po'i sgrub skor bya rgod
NK131(do)001:4001: gshongs kyi gtsug lag khang du sbas pa gnyal ba
NK131(do)001:4002: nyi ma shes rab kyi gter nas phyungs pa dang
NK131(do)001:4003: / / pu tra ming sring sgrub skor bsam yas
NK131(do)001:4004: su sbas pa lha btsun byang chub 'od kyi phyungs
NK131(do)001:4005: pa la sogs gsar ma ba dag la yang gter
NK131(do)001:4006: chos kyi rnam grangs rgya cher yod pas na /
NK131(do)001:4007: dpe brgyud dang gter brgyud gsar rnying gnyis ga la khyad par ma mchis par yod do //
NK131(do)001:4008: gter ma 'di gsar rnying gnyis ga la khyad par med par yod kyang /
NK131(do)001:4009: deng sang bod kyi dge ba'i bshes gnyen rnams gter
NK131(do)001:4010: chos la btsigs cher mi mdzad pa nas yi ge
NK131(do)001:4011: cung zad zhib par byas so //
NK131(do)001:4012: khyab bdag rgyal ba'i dbang po karma pa //
NK131(do)001:4013: thams cad mkhyen pa sangs rgyas dngos kyi gsungs //
NK131(do)001:4014: sdebs legs don snying 'brel chags rdo rje'i tshig /
NK131(do)001:4015: so skye'i blo yi nam yang bzlog dka' ba //
NK131(do)001:4016: deng 'dir me dang spra ba ji bzhin du //
NK131(do)001:4017: phrad pa tsam gyi gzhom par byas pa yang //
NK131(do)001:4018: phan bde'i lam ston rje btsun sa skya pa //
NK131(do)001:4019: brgyud par bcas pa'i mkhas grub bla ma'i tshogs //
NK131(do)001:4020: de bzhin bstan pa'i srog shing zhal lu pa //
NK131(do)001:4021: rjes 'brangs bcas pa'i bla ma'i tshogs rnams dang //
NK131(do)001:4022: kun bzang gnyis pa yongs 'dzin ngag dbang grags //
NK131(do)001:4023: sangs rgyas kun dngos bla ma de rnams kyi //
NK131(do)001:4024: drin las byung phyir bdag blo'i nus pas min //
NK131(do)001:4025: de phyir legs par bshad gang bla ma'i drin //
NK131(do)001:4026: bka' drin dran pas rtag par phyag 'tshal lo //
NK131(do)001:4027: nongs par bshad gang bdag blo'i nyes pa ste //
NK131(do)001:4028: mkhas pa'i skye bo rnams la bzod par gsol /
NK131(do)001:4030: karma pa'i sku skye'i gong ma dga' rab rdo rje'i slob ma tog tse rang grol dang /
NK131(do)001:4031: de rjes 'phags pa klu sgrub tu gyur pa ni pad+ma gsung gi rig 'dzin yin la /
NK131(do)001:4032: bod du lo ts+aa ba rgyal ba mchog dbyangs o
NK131(do)001:4033: rgyan chen po'i dngos slob yin zhing rta mgrin gyi
NK131(do)001:4034: sgrub lung byin pas grub pa brnyes /
NK131(do)001:4035: ma 'ongs pa'i dus su kar+m+aa pa zhes 'gro ba mtha' yas pa 'dul bar lung bstan pa thob /
NK131(do)001:4036: de'i 'og tu jo bo chen po rje u rgyan
NK131(do)001:4037: gyi gsung gi sprul pa de'i slob ma pu to
NK131(do)001:4038: bar 'khrungs / de nas rje dwags po lha rje
NK131(do)001:4039: u rgyan gyi sprul pa de'i slob ma karma dus
NK131(do)001:4041: karma pag shi ni u rgyan chen po'i sprul par yang zhal gyi bzhes te /
NK131(do)001:4043: re 'ga' sa ra ha pa yin //
NK131(do)001:4044: zhes sogs gsungs nas rgya nag gi rgyal po grub rtags kyi sgo nas btul /
NK131(do)001:4045: khams kahthoga pa byams pa 'bum las bsnyen par rdzogs /
NK131(do)001:4049: rnying ma ba rnams kyi 'dod pa so sor 'byed
NK131(do)001:4050: pa la lung a nu yo ga la rten nas
NK131(do)001:4051: dgongs 'dus kyi don so sor dbye ba dang /
NK131(do)001:4052: a nu yo ga'i chings dang /
NK131(do)001:4053: sku lnga yongs su rdzogs pa dang /
NK131(do)001:4054: rdzogs pa chen po'i dbang gi chu bo dang /
NK131(do)001:4055: kun tu bzang po'i byung tshul dang /
NK131(do)001:4056: gzhan yang rnying ma la yig cha mang du mdzad do //
NK131(do)001:4057: de rjes thams cad mkhyen pa rang byung rdo rje ni /
NK131(do)001:4058: gnyan ras dge 'dun 'bum gu ru jo 'ber gyi dngos slob dang /
NK131(do)001:4061: snye mdo ba kun dga' don grub /
NK131(do)001:4064: rig 'dzin ku m+aa r+aa dza sogs rnying ma'i bla ma mang du bsten /
NK131(do)001:4065: rnying ma la yig cha mang du mdzad /
NK131(do)001:4066: snying thig gi khrid yig mdzad par yang /
NK131(do)001:4067: gu ru jo 'ber sang g+ha lak+sha dang //
NK131(do)001:4068: dpal ldan rang byung rdo rje yan chad du //
NK131(do)001:4069: rig 'dzin brgyud pa bcu bdun nyid las thos //
NK131(do)001:4070: thung brgyud kun bzang rdo rje sems dpa' dang //
NK131(do)001:4071: dga' rab rdo rje sh+r+ai seng ha dang //
NK131(do)001:4072: bi ma mi tra man ngag gnad dang bcas //
NK131(do)001:4073: dag pa'i snang bas mngon sum gzigs gyur te //
NK131(do)001:4074: rnal 'byor dbang phyug rang byung rdo rje yi //
NK131(do)001:4075: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs tshul du nos pa'i phyir //
NK131(do)001:4076: byin brlabs brgyud pa drug tu 'dus pa yin //
NK131(do)001:4078: rgyal bas gsungs pa'i dam chos kun gyi bcud //
NK131(do)001:4079: lung dang rtogs par 'grel pa gsang sngags don //
NK131(do)001:4080: rdzogs rim snying phyungs mngon sum lta ba'i gnad //
NK131(do)001:4081: man ngag thems dang mthun par bdag gi sdebs //
NK131(do)001:4083: thugs dam gyi gtso bo rdzogs chen la mdzad /
NK131(do)001:4084: rje nyid kong yul na bzhugs dus /
NK131(do)001:4085: rdzogs chen snying thig 'di la pad+ma 'byung gnas nas
NK131(do)001:4086: brgyud pa zhig 'ong thang ba la dgongs nas gsol
NK131(do)001:4087: ba btab pas sprul sku las 'brel rtsal gyi gter
NK131(do)001:4088: gyi mkha' 'gro snying thig gi shog ser phyag tu
NK131(do)001:4089: byung / dag pa'i snang ba la u rgyan dngos las dbang dang gdams pa thob /
NK131(do)001:4090: 'brong ngur ba mkhan po rgyan dang /
NK131(do)001:4091: g.yung ston pa sogs la gnang nas dar bar mdzad do //
NK131(do)001:4092: de rjes rje rol pa'i rdo rjes kyang sprul sku
NK131(do)001:4093: sangs rgyas gling pa la de'i gter chos rnams gsan
NK131(do)001:4094: zhing thugs nyams su bzhes so //
NK131(do)001:4095: rje de bzhin gshegs pas kyang /
NK131(do)001:4097: bla ma dgongs 'dus rnams gsan zhing thugs nyams su bzhes /
NK131(do)001:4098: de rjes rje mthong ba don ldan gyis kyang /
NK131(do)001:4099: dka' bzhi pa rin chen bzang po la snying thig dang dgongs 'dus gsan cing /
NK131(do)001:4100: nyang lugs kyi rta nag la thugs dam gtso bor mdzad /
NK131(do)001:4101: de rjes rje chos grags rgya mtshos kyang /
NK131(do)001:4102: gu sh+ri dpal 'byor don grub sogs la dgongs 'dus
NK131(do)001:4103: dang snying thig la sogs bka' gter mang du gsan
NK131(do)001:4104: / de ltar rje gong ma rnams kyi brnog chos
NK131(do)001:4105: yang dag pa yin par rang rang gi rnam thar
NK131(do)001:4106: / du 'byung zhing / rje nyid kyis kyang rtses thang bsgom pa la /
NK131(do)001:4107: u rgyan chen po'i skur ston par mdzad pa nyid kyis na /
NK131(do)001:4108: karma pa rang lugs kyi grub mtha' nas gzhal na
NK131(do)001:4109: yang sngags rnying ma la ma dag pa'i cha ci
NK131(do)001:4110: yang yod pa ma yin no //
NK131(do)001:4111: de bas na rgyal dbang thams cad mkhyen pa mi bskyod rdo rje nyid kyis /
NK131(do)001:4112: til sgro'i bla ma rdzogs chen pa la bzlo ba /
NK131(do)001:4113: zhes pa'i chab shog na bka' lung dgongs pa can sna tshogs pa dang /
NK131(do)001:4114: chab shog sne'u gdong rtser gnang ba zhig na //
NK131(do)001:4115: ding sang dbu ru byang phyogs rgyud 'di na //
NK131(do)001:4116: gter ston lcang lo can sogs bdud sprul gyi //
NK131(do)001:4117: zhes sogs lta dgongs kyi drod tshad ci 'dra'am ma snyam gzigs pa'i tshig dang /
NK131(do)001:4118: dri ba'i tshul 'di dag ni sngags rnying ma'i dogs
NK131(do)001:4119: pa thams cad sel zhing drung 'byin par byed pa
NK131(do)001:4120: zab cing rgya che la gting dpag dka' ba'i tshul
NK131(do)001:4122: rnying ma ba dag thos bsam bsgom gsum la 'bad pa 'don phyir bstsal ba yin pas na /
NK131(do)001:4123: 'di dag gi don spyis phyin par rgyud la 'byor
NK131(do)001:4124: na gsang sngags snga 'gyur gyi dka' ba'i gnas mtha'
NK131(do)001:4125: dag gtan la phebs par 'gyur ba'i phyir nges par
NK131(do)001:4126: bka' drin chen po'i sgo nas mdzad pa yin na
NK131(do)001:4127: yang / de lta bur ma go ba'i rig can shin tu mang ba zhig snang la /
NK131(do)001:4128: sngags btsun lha dgongs mthar phyin pa rnams la ni /
NK131(do)001:4129: sangs rgyas stong byon te khyod kyi de chos min no zhes gsungs kyang bzlog par mi nus te /
NK131(do)001:4130: blo gros rab brtan gyi zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK131(do)001:4131: gang la dad cing mos pa rtse gcig pa de la gang gi mi bardzi ba ste /
NK131(do)001:4132: de'i drung du bdud kyi sangs rgyas su bsgyur nas
NK131(do)001:4133: 'ong ste de ni khyod kyi ma yin no zhes
NK131(do)001:4134: bzlog par byed bsgyur bar byed kyang de ni de
NK131(do)001:4135: las g.yo bar mi byed do //
NK131(do)001:4136: de yang 'byung ba chen po gzhan du 'gyur ba yang srid kyi /
NK131(do)001:4137: dad pa'i stobs la mos pa de ni stobs de las 'bral bar mi byed do //
NK131(do)001:4139: bdag lta bu'i rnying ma ba'i gzugs brnyan tshig don
NK131(do)001:4140: gyi go gzhi ma chags lha re'i las byang bu
NK131(do)001:4141: tsam re blo 'dzin byas nas rang gzhan gyi don
NK131(do)001:4142: byed blo dang / gzhan dag 'dra ba'i snying ma
NK131(do)001:4143: ba phran bu dag gi bka' shog 'di mthong thos
NK131(do)001:4144: byung na dog pa'i gnas mi chod par yul khyad
NK131(do)001:4145: par can la skur ba btab pa dang /
NK131(do)001:4146: chos spongs ba'i las bsags te /
NK131(do)001:4147: gsar ma'i chos rnams kyang 'chal ba dang /
NK131(do)001:4148: bslab pa dang rang gzo can gyi rang gzo byas pa'i mang ngo skur 'debs byed pa dang /
NK131(do)001:4149: de dag gi rjes su 'brangs nas chos spongs las bsags par 'gyur to //
NK131(do)001:4151: gsang 'dus la sogs pa'i rgyud dang phyag rgya chen
NK131(do)001:4152: po gzhob rdog pas rdzis pa dang 'dra zer ba'ang
NK131(do)001:4153: rdzogs chen pa rnal 'byor bla med kyi rgyud sde
NK131(do)001:4154: dang phyag chen gyi lam khyad du gsod pa yin
NK131(do)001:4155: pa'i rdzogs pa chen po chos min du sgrub pa
NK131(do)001:4157: zhes bya ba'i nyes pa dang ldan pa de'i phyir smras pa yin no //
NK131(do)001:4158: de la chos spongs pa'i las ni shin tu lci
NK131(do)001:4159: ba ste 'di dag ni rang bzor byas pa yin
NK131(do)001:4160: no // zhes zer ba dag 'byung bar 'gyur ro //
NK131(do)001:4161: rnam snang mngon byang gi rgyud phyi ma la bdag
NK131(do)001:4162: gi sems kyi gnas bstan la ma pheb par rnam
NK131(do)001:4163: par 'khrul nas 'di skad du 'di ni sangs rgyas
NK131(do)001:4165: ro gsang ba'i bdag po'i mi blun po de dag
NK131(do)001:4166: ni 'gro ba gnyis su 'gro ba rig par bya
NK131(do)001:4169: sems can dmyal ba dang dud 'agro'o //
NK131(do)001:4172: gang zhig chos mchog gtso bo ste //
NK131(do)001:4173: rgyal ba'i gsungs pa chos kyi mdzod //
NK131(do)001:4174: sa steng mis ni spong byed pa //
NK131(do)001:4175: de ni mnar med dmyal ba 'gro //
NK131(do)001:4176: bskal ba chen po de mtshe bcas //
NK131(do)001:4177: rnam pa du mar dbye ba bstan //
NK131(do)001:4178: nam zhig gang du 'byung ba ni //
NK131(do)001:4179: mi'i lus ni skye na yang //
NK131(do)001:4180: dbul zhing nad mang blun pa dang //
NK131(do)001:4181: kla klo dag tu skye bar 'gyur //
NK131(do)001:4183: de ni mdze can nad par 'gyur //
NK131(do)001:4184: lkug cing 'on pa yan lag nyams //
NK131(do)001:4185: blo nyams long ba nyid dang ni //
NK131(do)001:4186: rtsub cing rtag tu 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
NK131(do)001:4187: sa steng yi dwags lta bur snang //
NK131(do)001:4188: gos ngan sems ni ngan pa dang //
NK131(do)001:4189: sen mo dang ni lus kyang ngan //
NK131(do)001:4190: srin bu rnams ni zos pa dang //
NK131(do)001:4191: shu ba g.yan pa yan lag ldan //
NK131(do)001:4192: mdo sde 'di dag spang bar na //
NK131(do)001:4194: de dang der ni skye ba ni //
NK131(do)001:4195: blo ngan rmong pa skye bar 'gyur //
NK131(do)001:4197: bdog po nyung ngu rgyud las kyang //
NK131(do)001:4198: mos pa du ma'i sems can la //
NK131(do)001:4199: spyod pa sna tshogs ston mdzad de //
NK131(do)001:4200: sna tshogs yul gyi gdul bya la //
NK131(do)001:4201: thabs ni sna tshogs ston pa yin //
NK131(do)001:4202: zab mos chos 'di bston pa la //
NK131(do)001:4203: gal te mos pa ma gyur kyang //
NK131(do)001:4204: smad pa dag tu mi bya ste //
NK131(do)001:4205: chos nyid bsam mi khyab dran bya //
NK131(do)001:4208: rdo rje theg pa la smod pa //
NK131(do)001:4210: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun la //
NK131(do)001:4211: ma gus par ni byed pa gang //
NK131(do)001:4212: bder gshegs mtshan ma la bsten bya //
NK131(do)001:4213: de ni nges par mnar med 'gro //
NK131(do)001:4215: brten pa gzhi dang brtags pa gsum gyi legs par
NK131(do)001:4216: ma rtags shing don ma rtogs par sgra tsam la
NK131(do)001:4217: rten pa chos ma yin zhes spongs ba ma yin
NK131(do)001:4218: no // de bas na snod dang mi ldan pa
NK131(do)001:4219: la gsang sngags kyi bstan na rang gi dam tshig
NK131(do)001:4220: nyams shing gzhan yang chos spong gi las la sbyor
NK131(do)001:4222: de nyid bsdus pa'i rgyud las khyod kyi phyag rgya
NK131(do)001:4223: la mi mkhas pa gzhan du su yang rung ba
NK131(do)001:4224: la phyag rgya gang yang rung ba bstan par ma
NK131(do)001:4225: byed cing / de cis phyir zhe na /
NK131(do)001:4226: de ni 'di ltar dkyil 'khor chen po ma mthong
NK131(do)001:4227: ba'i sems can de dag gi phyag rgya bcing ba
NK131(do)001:4228: byas na de'i tshe de dag grub par mi 'gyur
NK131(do)001:4229: ro // de nas de dag the tshom du gyur te /
NK131(do)001:4230: gnod pa ma spangs ba myur ba nyid du dus
NK131(do)001:4231: byas te dmyal ba chen po mnar med pa zhes
NK131(do)001:4233: khyod kyi kyang ngan song du 'gro bar 'gyur ro //
NK131(do)001:4235: tshul 'di la pan chen thams cad mkhyen pa bu
NK131(do)001:4236: ston gyi rgyud sde spyi'i rnam bzhag las don 'di
NK131(do)001:4237: nyid thugs la bzhag nas sngon gyi slob dpon gyi
NK131(do)001:4238: dbang po dang / de'i slob ma slob dpon mtho btsun tso yags kyis kyang /
NK131(do)001:4239: skal ba ngan pa la gsang sngags kyi tshul ston pa la dgag pa mdzad cing /
NK131(do)001:4240: bod kyi rgyal blon sa chen po la bzhugs pa dag gis kyang /
NK131(do)001:4242: ldems por dgongs pa'i don zab mo ma rtogs par /
NK131(do)001:4243: sgra ji bzhin pa la tshad mar bzung ste /
NK131(do)001:4244: thabs shes rab kyi rnal 'byor cung zad kyang med cing /
NK131(do)001:4245: spangs bsrung gi dam tshig sna gcig kyang mi sdom par /
NK131(do)001:4246: gsang sngags la bsnyad btags nas /
NK131(do)001:4247: mu stegs 'chol ba'i rgyud ltar bag med pa'i spyod
NK131(do)001:4248: pas sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa nyams smas par byed
NK131(do)001:4249: pa / rang gzhan phung ba'i tshul la 'jug par gzigs nas /
NK131(do)001:4250: smad nas bka' stsal pa ma gtogs rnal 'byor chen
NK131(do)001:4251: po'i rgyud bsgyur du med par bkas bcad pa yin
NK131(do)001:4253: gsang sngags zab mo'i don blor mi shong ba'i rigs can rnams dang /
NK131(do)001:4254: don ma go ba rnams ni chos spong ba'i las bsog pa sha stag tu nges pas /
NK131(do)001:4255: mkhas pa'i skye bo skal pa can blo gros dang
NK131(do)001:4256: ldan pa rnams kyi de lta bu'i sgor nam yang
NK131(do)001:4258: bka' gsang rmad byung bla med rdzogs pa che //
NK131(do)001:4259: sangs rgyas ye shes mngon sum ston pa'i chos //
NK131(do)001:4260: tha snyad tshig gi dug chus yid dkrugs pa'i //
NK131(do)001:4261: rtog ge smra ba'i spyod yul ma yin mod //
NK131(do)001:4262: gang dag 'di la log par lta ba'i tshogs //
NK131(do)001:4263: bdud sde dpung dang bcas te ltar snang gi //
NK131(do)001:4264: lung rigs bskal pa brgya ru smra na yang //
NK131(do)001:4265: skal bzang su zhig ba spu g.yo nus sam //
NK131(do)001:4266: sbyangs dang skyes stobs yon tan dman na yang //
NK131(do)001:4267: rje btsun bla ma rnams kyi bka' drin las //
NK131(do)001:4268: zab mo'i don la dge ba'i spobs pa thob //
NK131(do)001:4269: log lta can rnams da dung gzhom par bya //
NK131(do)001:4270: chab shog 'di la sngon chad dri ba'i lan //
NK131(do)001:4271: rim pa gsum tsam mdzad pa mthong mod kyi //
NK131(do)001:4272: dri ba'i dgongs don tshul bzhin ma lon pas //
NK131(do)001:4273: dris lan dgos med tshig dang zur za'i gtam //
NK131(do)001:4274: kho na nyid las don gzhan ma bstan pas //
NK131(do)001:4275: rang dang rang 'dra'i 'gro la phan phyir du //
NK131(do)001:4276: smras kyi mkhas gzhan dgyes snyam rlom pa'ang med //
NK131(do)001:4277: bde gshegs dgongs spyod zab mo lhur len pa'i //
NK131(do)001:4278: sngags ban chen po rnams la'ang 'dis ci 'tshal //
NK131(do)001:4279: de lta'ang rmangs zhen rdzun gyi ma sbags par //
NK131(do)001:4280: rgyal ba'i lung la brten nas bkod pa yi //
NK131(do)001:4281: dge ba de yis bdag dang 'gro ba rnams //
NK131(do)001:4282: bde gshegs chos tshul bsam mi khyab pa'i sgo //
NK131(do)001:4283: gang la'ang log rtog nam yang mi skye bar //
NK131(do)001:4284: rang rang blo dang 'tshams pa'i lam zhugs te //
NK131(do)001:4285: dag snang mi zad rgyan gyi 'khor lo la //
NK131(do)001:4286: yongs su spyod pa'i thub dbang de mtshungs shog /
NK131(do)001:4287: ces rgyal ba'i dbang po thams cad mkhyen pa mi
NK131(do)001:4288: bskyod rdo rje'i chab shog gi dri ba'i lan du
NK131(do)001:4289: gsol ba lung dang rigs pa'i 'brug sgra zhes bya
NK131(do)001:4290: ba / dpal u rgyan gyi slob dpon chen po
NK131(do)001:4291: pad+ma 'byung gnas kyi gdul bya tsam du gtogs pa
NK131(do)001:4292: lha rje blo gros bzang pos 'dzin byed kyi lo
NK131(do)001:4293: sa ga zla ba'i tshes bcu la mon yul bum
NK131(do)001:4294: thang bsam gtan gling du rdzogs par bkod pa'o //
NK131(do)001:4295: 'dis kyang 'khor ba sdug bsngal gyi rgya mtsho chen po myur du skems par gyur cig /
NK131(do)001:4298: mi 'jigs bzhi brnyes bden gsung seng ge'i sgras //
NK131(do)001:4299: phas brgol glang po stong gi klad 'gem pa //
NK131(do)001:4300: thub dbang rdo rje 'chang dang dbyer med pa'i //
NK131(do)001:4301: dpal mgon bla ma'i zhabs la phyag bagyi'o //
NK131(do)001:4302: gdod ma'i mgon po kun tu bzang po de //
NK131(do)001:4303: 'khor 'das kun gyi sngon rol byang chub nas //
NK131(do)001:4304: phyir gsal lhan grub thugs rje bkod pa'i sprin //
NK131(do)001:4305: chos kyi dbyings mnyam pha mtha' su yis dpog /
NK131(do)001:4306: don dam dbyings su spros mtshan kun bral yang //
NK131(do)001:4307: kun rdzob snang ngor gdul bya'i blo rim bzhin //
NK131(do)001:4308: gang 'dul theg pa'i dbye sgo bgrangs yas kyang //
NK131(do)001:4309: mthar thug skyel so theg gcig 'bras bu'i rtse //
NK131(do)001:4310: ye shes mngon byed dbang rab cig car lam //
NK131(do)001:4311: grol ba drug ldan rdo rje rtse mo'i srol //
NK131(do)001:4312: grub thob bye ba'i gshegs shul zla med phul //
NK131(do)001:4313: sngon byon dam pa'i drin las deng yang gnas //
NK131(do)001:4314: 'di ni skal pa mchog 'ag'i spyod yul las //
NK131(do)001:4315: phal gyis rtogs dka' yid bzhin nor bu yang //
NK131(do)001:4316: dman pas mi rnyed rnyed kyang mi mgu ste //
NK131(do)001:4317: glang rdzis phul gsum sbyin zhes zer ba bzhin //
NK131(do)001:4318: de slad phyogs 'dir sngon chad rtsod pa'i khul //
NK131(do)001:4319: rmad du byung yang smag la nyi zla bzhin //
NK131(do)001:4320: log rtog skyon gyis nam yang sgrib pa med //
NK131(do)001:4321: bsreg bcad brdar ba'i gser bzhin lhag par mngon //
NK131(do)001:4322: 'jig rten dbang phyug rgyal dbang sarba dz+ny+aar //
NK131(do)001:4324: sngon med legs bshad sgo brgya 'byed slad du //
NK131(do)001:4325: dri ba 'di yang thabs mkhas mdzad par nges //
NK131(do)001:4326: 'jig rten mig gcig snang mdzad sgyu ma'i gar //
NK131(do)001:4327: sog bzlog mkhas pa'i legs bshad spar gyi 'phrul //
NK131(do)001:4328: 'jam pa'i rdo rje'i bka' lung rjes sgrub phyir //
NK131(do)001:4329: bstan gnyis dar rgyas gling gi chos grwar spel //
NK131(do)001:4330: dge bas bstan 'dzin zhabs brtan mdzad phrin 'phel //
NK131(do)001:4331: dge 'dun sde rgyas bshad sgrub bstan pa dar //
NK131(do)001:4332: bod khams bde skyid mtha' dmag dus 'khrugs zhi //
NK131(do)001:4333: rdzogs ldan nyi ma gsar du 'char gyur cig //
NK131(do)001:4334: ces pa'ang rnam dkar 'du byed pa po gzhan phan
